\id MAT - Uare
\h Mataio
\toc3 Mat
\toc2 Mataio
\toc1 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Mataioꞌa Mirihiro
\mt1 Mataio
\mt2 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Mataioꞌa Mirihiro
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Buka ꞌahiꞌe Mataioꞌa mirihiro. Aniꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga. Ani ni ꞌahogaꞌe Levi. Aniꞌe ꞌizema Iesu tahiꞌa rougano takesi ufiroteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe ane nabuga Iuda azaḡa veize Iesu hari manoḡa mirihiro. Buka ꞌahi zamaḡano peroveta azaḡaniꞌa ibite Keriso moneo irina ḡoeriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ḡehaḡa mae fare mirihadu ze ḡoere niduꞌa hugano furerarotaꞌaꞌe ihoziro, ebu Iesuꞌe Iuda azaḡaniꞌa guhine arinuteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso(Mesia) rae ihoziro. Aꞌe mene Iuda azaḡa veize daꞌo, rehano raha azaḡa niduꞌa veize ḡoeriro. Mataioꞌe buka ꞌada Iesu ḡabone niduꞌa, aniꞌa fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo onamo rudanadu bare ḡabodiroteꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa mirihiro.
\c 1
\s1 Iesu Keriso Vouḡa Nize
\r (Luka 3:23-38)
\p 
\v 1 Iesu Keriso vouḡa nizeꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe. Aniꞌe Aberahamo mariga ebu Davida mariga.
\li1 
\v 2 Aberahamoꞌe Isako moga,
\li1 Isakoꞌe Iakobo moga, Iakoboꞌe Iuda zu ani negoḡa duḡuru moze.
\li1 
\v 3 Iudaꞌe Pereze zu Zera moze ebu Tamaraꞌe zeḡe vize. Perezeꞌe Hezarona moga, Hezaronaꞌe Ramo moga.
\li1 
\v 4 Ramoꞌe Aminadaba moga, Aminadabaꞌe Nasona moga, Nasonaꞌe Salamona moga.
\li1 
\v 5 Salamonaꞌe Boazi moga ebu Rahabaꞌe Boazi viꞌa. Boaziꞌe Obeda moga ebu Rutaꞌe Obeda viꞌa. Obedaꞌe Iese moga.
\li1 
\v 6 Ieseꞌe kini Davida moga.
\li1 Davidaꞌe Solomona moga ebu Basebaꞌe Solomona viꞌa. Basebaꞌe ibite Uria inuga.
\li1 
\v 7 Solomonaꞌe Rehoboama moga, Rehoboamaꞌe Abia moga, Abiaꞌe Asa moga.
\li1 
\v 8 Asaꞌe Iehosafata moga, Iehosafataꞌe Iehorama moga, Iehoramaꞌe Uzia moga.
\li1 
\v 9 Uziaꞌe Iotama moga, Iotamaꞌe Ahasi moga, Ahasiꞌe Hezekia moga.
\li1 
\v 10 Hezekiaꞌe Manase moga, Manaseꞌe Amona moga, Amonaꞌe Iosia moga.
\li1 
\v 11 Iosiaꞌe Iekonia zu ani negoḡa duḡuru moze.
\li1 Eꞌe madaḡano Babulonia azaḡaniꞌa Isaraela azaḡa teite utitadu Isaraela azaḡa Babulonia habaꞌano obozi onamiro.
\li1 
\v 12 Babulonia habaꞌano obozi onamiroteꞌe ḡarugano,
\li1 Iekoniaꞌe Sealetiele moga, Sealetieleꞌe Zerubabele moga.
\li1 
\v 13 Zerubabeleꞌe Abiuda moga, Abiudaꞌe Eliakimi moga, Eliakimiꞌe Azora moga.
\li1 
\v 14 Azoraꞌe Zadoka moga, Zadokaꞌe Akimi moga, Akimiꞌe Eliuda moga.
\li1 
\v 15 Eliudaꞌe Eleazara moga, Eleazaraꞌe Matana moga, Matanaꞌe Iakobo moga.
\li1 
\v 16 Iakoboꞌe Iosefa moga ebu Iosefa inugaꞌe Maria.
\li1 Mariaonoꞌo Keriso rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Iesuꞌa fureraro.
\p 
\v 17 Eꞌanoꞌo Aberahamonoꞌo onao Davida madaḡano zeḡe ega niduꞌaꞌe 14, zu Davidaonoꞌo onao Isaraela azaḡa Babulonia habaꞌano obozi onamiroteꞌe madaḡano zeḡe ega niduꞌaꞌe 14, ebu Babulonia habaꞌano obozi onamiroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo onao Keriso\f + \fr 1:17 \fqa Mesia \f* madaḡano zeḡe ega niduꞌaꞌe 14.
\s1 Iesu Kerisoꞌa Fureraro
\r (Luka 2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Iesu Kerisoꞌe ꞌahige fureraro. Ani viꞌa Mariaꞌe Iosefa iraꞌauḡa. Anianine ꞌizema hahurogano Mariaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡanonoꞌo ahiꞌeta reiroteꞌe ederiro.
\v 19 Maria iꞌa Iosefaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa vazeḡa, eꞌanoꞌo hunihunio Maria mene mae mazagaronifine ani sifu tuḡune modiꞌuma rae zamariro.
\p 
\v 20 Ani ꞌouge rae zamarirotene, Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa iḡunao fureranadu ꞌahige rae niro, “Davida mariga Iosefa, Maria teite hahuroga ago rihanoꞌi. Mazaḡa Mariaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡanonoꞌo ahiꞌeta.
\v 21 Aniꞌe ubuga ꞌahoga furenoꞌidene, niḡaꞌe Iesu rae turahoꞌi, mazaḡa aniꞌe ane mone azaḡa haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡaboziꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 22 ꞌOugadu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa peroveta vazeḡanonoꞌo rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 
\v 23 “Ḡianoꞌi, ohoze ꞌize mene edereꞌeteꞌe nogobaḡaniꞌa ahiꞌeta reꞌuma,
\q2 ebu ubuga ꞌahoga fureniꞌuma.
\q1 Ubuga niḡaꞌe Imanuela rae huniꞌuma.”\x + \xo 1:23 \xt Isaia 7:14\x*
\m Imanuela hugaꞌe, “Badiꞌaꞌe emeḡe teite radiuꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 24 Iosefaꞌa bazunanoꞌo evatirotene, Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viganiꞌa niroteꞌe idunaḡano haḡairo, ebu Mariaꞌe ani inuga radu zamaharo.
\v 25 Rehano Iosefaꞌe Maria teite tibano mene baziro, onamo ubuga fureniro, ebu ubuga niḡaꞌe Iesu rae turahiro.
\c 2
\s1 Edeḡa Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Vaḡe Ariro
\p 
\v 1 Herodaꞌe Iudea habaꞌa kiniḡa reiroteꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌe Iudea habaꞌano ne ꞌahoga, Betelehemao fureraro. Eꞌe enogano edeḡa azaḡa nuꞌe madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo Ierusalemao feuri ariro.
\v 2 Ebu ze vaze ḡadiziro, “Iuda azaḡa kini raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe nouma fureraneha? Mazaḡa eme madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneo ani buzuva horoniro ebu ani mazao kuranoga veize areha.”
\v 3 Kini Herodaꞌa ḡoereze igirotene, zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro ebu Ierusalema azaḡa niduꞌa zuni zamazeꞌa adudaro.
\v 4 Eꞌanoꞌo Herodaꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa nuꞌozadu ḡadiziro, “Kerisoꞌe nouma fureraꞌuma?”
\v 5 Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aniꞌe Iudea habaꞌano Betelehema neḡano fureraꞌuma. Mazaḡa peroveta vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahige rae mirihiro,
\q1 
\v 6 'O Iudea habaꞌano ne ꞌahoga Betelehema,
\q2 ḡaꞌe Iudea habaꞌano ne boroboro boꞌaḡano mene zuhuꞌa.
\q1 Mazaḡa ḡae mazaonoꞌo vaze niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ariꞌuma.
\q2 Aniꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa teige, eḡe none azaḡa, Isaraela azaḡa taufiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 2:6 \xt Mika 5:2\x*”
\p 
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo Herodaꞌa edeḡa azaḡa sifu huzadu zeḡe mazaonoꞌo noꞌe madaḡano buzuva eꞌeꞌa agararotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.
\v 8 Ebu edeḡa azaḡa Betelehema neḡano tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae ziro, “Onamadu ene guraḡa eꞌe faine vaḡoꞌi ebu horonoꞌidene ihohoꞌi. Eḡe zuni ani vaḡe onamadu ani mazao kuraꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 9-10 Ze Heroda ḡoere igi hauḡirotene, ibionoꞌo onamiro. Ze ibio onameꞌenogano, ibite madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano horoniroteꞌe buzuvaḡaniꞌa bare fureraro. Ze eꞌe horonadu matuꞌe rudaro. Ebu buzuva eꞌeꞌa ze ibitozeadu ene guraḡaniꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa ragano tue radiro.
\v 11 Ze ne zamaḡa diuḡadu ene guraḡaꞌe viꞌa Maria teite radiuꞌenoga horoniro. ꞌOugirotene, ze ani mazao ḡuḡuradu kuraro. Ebu ꞌumiroteꞌe ḡauḡa naeḡa boroboro fuhiꞌadu ḡahuno haro. Aꞌe golo zu ꞌuvahu hohoḡa manoḡa ebu murava hohoḡa manoḡa.
\v 12 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa iḡunao edeḡa azaḡa ihoziro, “Heroda vaḡe ago bare onamoꞌi.” ꞌOugadu zeꞌe ibi ꞌahoganonoꞌo zeḡe haba bare onamiro. \fig Edeḡa azaḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao kuraro|src="CN01632b.tif" size="col" ref="2:11"\fig*
\s1 Ferau Izipi Habaꞌa Onamiro
\p 
\v 13 Edeḡa azaḡaniꞌa iḡuniroteꞌe enogano, Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viganiꞌa iḡunao Iosefa mazao fureranadu niro, “Herodaꞌa ene guraḡa vaḡadu matihi raꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo iḡunoꞌi ebu ene guraḡa viꞌeta zamazadu Izipi habaꞌa ferau onamoꞌi. Ebu eꞌea radoꞌi onamo eḡeꞌa ḡeꞌuma.”
\v 14 ꞌOugadu Iosefaꞌe ene guraḡa viꞌeta zamazadu ohere ferau Izipi habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 15 Ebu ze eꞌea radiro onamo Herodaꞌa rudaro. ꞌOugadu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa peroveta vazeḡanonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro, “Eḡeꞌa Izipi habaꞌanonoꞌo ubudehe hune ariro.”\x + \xo 2:15 \xt Hosea 11:1 \x*
\s1 Herodaꞌa Tahiꞌa Komeꞌa Zimi Hauḡiro
\p 
\v 16 Herodaꞌe edeḡa azaḡaniꞌa soꞌoniroteꞌe ederirotene, maḡune rudaro. Aniꞌe edeḡa azaḡaniꞌa ihoniroteꞌe madaḡa idunaḡano mada meꞌodadu ene aꞌe muri aheu heuḡa rae zamariro. Eꞌanoꞌo ane uti azaḡa tuḡuzadu Betelehema neḡa zu uhiḡa neḡa niduꞌa zamaḡano ohoze komeꞌa muri aheuonoꞌo onamo ene guraḡa ḡonaga niduꞌa zimi hauḡiro.
\v 17 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Ieremiaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 
\v 18 “Rama neḡano roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa
\q2 kuau niauꞌeteꞌe agoḡa igiro.
\q1 Rahelaꞌa ubugaubuga uꞌano niaro,
\q2 ebu ani vazeꞌa naminoga hezahoziniro,
\q2 mazaḡa ubugaubuganiꞌa rudaro.”\x + \xo 2:18 \xt Ieremia 31:15\x*
\s1 Izipionoꞌo Nazareta Bare Ariro
\p 
\v 19 Herodaꞌa rudaroteꞌe enogano, Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa Izipi habaꞌano Iosefa mazao iḡunao fureraro ebu niro,
\v 20 “Iḡunoꞌi ebu ene guraḡa viꞌeta Isaraela habaꞌa tutuze onamoꞌi. Mazaḡa ene guraḡa matihi reiroteꞌe azaḡa ꞌai rudau hauḡeha.”
\p 
\v 21 Eꞌanoꞌo Iosefaꞌa iḡunadu ene guraḡa viꞌeta Isaraela habaꞌa tutuze onamiro.
\v 22 Rehano ani Akelaoꞌe moga Heroda iḡuri madu Iudea habaꞌa kiniḡa reiroteꞌe igirotene, Iudea habaꞌa onamogaꞌe riharo. Eꞌanoꞌo tuḡure viganiꞌa iḡunao ihoniroteꞌe idunaḡano, ze Galilea habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 23 Ebu ne ꞌahoga, niḡa Nazaretao radiro. ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta azaḡanonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro, “Aniꞌe Nazareta vazeḡa rae huniꞌuma.”
\c 3
\s1 Ioane Babatisoꞌa Iesu Ibi Ruhiniro
\r (Mareko 1:1-8; Luka 3:1-18; Ioane 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Ioane Babatisoꞌa Iudea habaꞌano haba bohaꞌa aradu ꞌahige haramiro,
\v 2 “Haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuroꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai haniteha.”
\v 3 Peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa Ioane Babatiso moneo ꞌahige rae reiro,
\q1 “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haba bohaꞌano huau ḡoereꞌohe, raenaꞌa,
\q1 'Zuhiꞌa Boro veize ibi ruhiboꞌi,
\q2 ebu ani veize ibi mae dudunoꞌi.'”\x + \xo 3:3 \xt Isaia 40:3\x*
\p 
\v 4 Ioaneꞌa kamelo iguḡa hina haḡairoteꞌe dabuaḡa vidaro, zu mani ogaḡa miniḡa hina gabaꞌiḡano autiro, ebu fihore zu butu ꞌavoreḡa godaga aro.
\v 5 Eꞌe madaḡano Ierusalemaonoꞌo, zu Iudea habaꞌa niduꞌaonoꞌo, zu Ioridana vuḡa habaꞌa niduꞌaonoꞌo vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Ioane vaḡe onamiro.
\v 6 Ebu ze haḡaize sauꞌa rae furenadu Ioaneꞌa Ioridana vuḡano babatisoziro.
\p 
\v 7 Farisea azaḡa zu Sadukea azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa babatiso mouga radu Ioane vaḡe ariro. Ebu aneꞌa ze horozadu ziro, “Zaꞌe Zarama ubugaubuga! Iniuꞌa zae mazao, 'Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌanonoꞌo ferau muhinoꞌi,' rae reiro? Aꞌe mene idaḡa!
\v 8 Rehano ibite haḡaize sau'anono'o ḡihuniroteꞌe haḡaiḡa izidi furenoꞌi.
\v 9 Ebu ꞌahige rae ago zamaroꞌi, 'Emeꞌe Aberahamo mariga, eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa mene maḡunofiꞌuma.' Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badi'a'a hadi ꞌadi hina Aberahamo mariga haḡaoga zuni idaḡa.
\v 10 Ḡiro 'ai ire taigano amahi tiro. Eꞌanoꞌo huga manoḡa mene iniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa niduꞌa'e udi higonadu ire rogao feuniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 11 Zaeꞌa haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuroga veize eḡeꞌa vu hina babatisoziꞌohe. Rehano eḡe ḡaruna ariteꞌe vazeḡa gigiꞌaḡaꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa zu eḡe vitihoga. Eḡe'a ani tamaka odoheꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡa rae rouga zuni mene idaḡa. Aniꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa zu ire roga hina babatisoziꞌuma.
\v 12 Maho hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano,\f + \fr 3:12 \fqa Vuidi hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano \f* vazeꞌa kari hina rouḡa tenadu maho huꞌiꞌohe, ebu iguḡa manoneꞌohe zu meba hare deheneꞌohe. Ebu hugaꞌe nuꞌonadu suaba zamaḡano tiꞌohe, rehano iguḡaꞌe mene vidauꞌeteꞌe ire rogao hufi haoneꞌohe.”
\s1 Iesuꞌa Babatiso Meiro
\r (Mareko 1:9-11; Luka 3:21-22)
\p 
\v 13 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa Ioaneonoꞌo babatiso mouga radu Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo Ioane vaḡe Ioridana vuḡa ariro.
\v 14 Rehano Ioaneꞌa Iesu garariro zu niro, “Ḡaeꞌa eḡe babatisohifo. Nougaꞌahi ḡaꞌe eḡe vaḡe areha?”
\v 15 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Izidiꞌe ꞌahige haḡaoꞌi. Eme Badiꞌaꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa duduḡa niduꞌa haḡae huniꞌuma.” ꞌOugadu Ioaneꞌa Iesu babatisoniro.
\v 16 Iesuꞌa babatiso meiroteꞌe enogano vuonoꞌo gaba tiri onamiro. ꞌOugirotene, adureꞌa bohatanadu Iesuꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Tubugo niniḡa teige ane mazao ovairoteꞌe horoniro.
\v 17 Ebu ago ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ꞌahige rae reiro, “ꞌAdiꞌe eḡe zamarone ubude. Eꞌa ani mazao matu'e rudau'ohe.”
\c 4
\s1 Diaboloꞌa Iesu Tuhune Nuriro
\r (Mareko 1:12-13; Luka 4:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe ḡarugano Diaboloꞌa Iesu tuhune nuroga veize Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Iesu tutune haba bohaꞌa onamiro.
\v 2 Eꞌea mada 40 zamaḡano ohere zu madai ogomu mene aro. Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌe vinine runiro.
\v 3 Ebu Diaboloꞌa tuhunoga radu ani vaḡe ariro ebu niro, “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga roꞌidene, hadi ꞌadi ninaꞌa, 'Ḡihuradu ꞌuvahu odogano roꞌi,' rae noꞌi.”
\v 4 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Mene, Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Vaze'e ꞌuvahu odogano da'o mene ḡabode radi'uma, rehano Badiꞌa hebeonoꞌo buauꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hina ḡabode radiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 4:4 \xt Goro 8:3\x*”
\p 
\v 5 Ebu Diaboloꞌa Iesu ne zaḡoḡa, Ierusalema tutune onamiro zu kuru neḡa hitaga huneo ohonadu niro,
\v 6 “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga roꞌidene, rafatoꞌi. Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,
\q1 'Badi'aꞌa ḡaꞌe duguoga veize ane tuḡure vigaviga ḡae vaḡe tuḡuziꞌuma.
\q2 Ze'a ꞌevoreze hina mae ḡihi'i'uma ꞌahine, odaḡoꞌe hadio mene tutuhaꞌuma.'\x + \xo 4:6 \xt Salamo 91:11-12\x*”
\p 
\v 7 Iesu'a naenaeniro, “Mene, Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡae Badiꞌa ago tuhuno'i.'\x + \xo 4:7 \xt Goro 6:16\x*”
\p 
\v 8 Ebu Diaboloꞌa Iesu maḡa hitaga hune tutune itadu kini'a zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe haba'a niduꞌa zu zeḡe ḡau naeḡa boro niduꞌa ihoniro.
\v 9 Ebu aneꞌa Iesu niro, “Ḡaeꞌa eḡe zamao ḡuḡuradu kuraune, eꞌe niduꞌa ḡae ḡaniꞌuma.”
\v 10 Iesuꞌa niro, “Mene, eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi. Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡae Badiꞌa mazao da'o kurano'i zu ane veize daꞌo gauoꞌi.'\x + \xo 4:10 \xt Goro 6:13\x*”
\p 
\v 11 ꞌOugadu Diaboloꞌa Iesu mazaonoꞌo vaḡine onamiro. Ebu tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa aradu Iesu taufiro.
\s1 Galilea Habaꞌano Ḡadahe Haramiro
\r (Mareko 1:14-15; Luka 4:14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Iesuꞌa Ioaneꞌe ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoniroteꞌe egadu Galilea habaꞌa bare onamiro.
\v 13 Galilea habaꞌano ani Nazareta neḡano radiro. Ebu neḡa eꞌe modadu Kaperanauma onamiro, ebu eꞌea radiunu. Kaperanaumaꞌe Zebulono zu Nafatali habaꞌano ebu Galilea duꞌuraḡa genaḡano ne boro ꞌahoga.
\v 14 Ibite Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 
\v 15 “Zebulono zu Nafatali habaꞌaꞌe
\q2 Galilea duꞌuraḡa ibiḡano zu Ioridana vuḡa moneafao.
\q2 Galileaꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa haba.
\q1 
\v 16 Uzabo zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa agaḡa boro horoneha.
\q2 Rune zauhaḡa habaꞌano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa rana agaḡaniꞌa agazeha.”\x + \xo 4:15-16 \xt Isaia 9:1-2\x*
\p 
\v 17 Eꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo Iesuꞌa ḡadahe haramiro, “Ḡihuroꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai haniteha.”
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa Ohotiro
\r (Mareko 1:16-20; Luka 5:1-11)
\p 
\v 18 Iesuꞌa Galilea duꞌuraḡa genaḡano onameꞌeteꞌea, vaze aheuꞌa reꞌeva feune radiunuteꞌe horoziro. Zeꞌe Simona, niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Petero ebu negoḡa Anderea. Zeꞌe ḡozone mauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.
\v 19 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡe ḡaruna hegotoꞌi. Zaꞌe vaze reꞌevaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa rouga veize ohoziꞌuma.”
\v 20 ꞌOugirotene, ze zogone reꞌevaze modadu ani hegote onamiro. \fig Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa huziro|src="CN01681B.TIF" size="col" ref="4:18-20"\fig*
\p 
\v 21 Iesuꞌa eꞌeanoꞌo tahiꞌa faḡa onamirotene, vaze ꞌahoga negoḡeta horoziro. Zeꞌe Zebedeo ubuga aheu, Iakobo zu negoḡa Ioane. Zeꞌe moze teite ḡasi zamaḡano reꞌeva zigoga faine radiunu. Ebu Iesuꞌa ze huziro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.”
\v 22 ꞌOugirotene, zeꞌe zogone ḡasize zu moze modadu ani hegote onamiro.
\s1 Ugi Azaḡa Faiziro
\r (Luka 6:17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Iesuꞌe Galilea habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano ragaveꞌenaꞌa, Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano ihoziro zu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡa haramiro. Ebu vaze ḡehaḡa boꞌaḡano ugi zu gigiꞌa niduꞌa fainiro.
\v 24 Ebu Iesu hariḡaniꞌa bororanadu Siria habaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa igiro. Zeꞌa ugi azaḡa niduꞌa tutuze ani vaḡe ariro. Ugi nunu uꞌano ahirizeꞌa gigize ruzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, vine sauꞌaniꞌa ragano reiroteꞌe azaḡa, ketoketeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu ahirize haganoga mene idaḡa azaḡa tutuze arirotene, Iesuꞌa ze faiziro.
\v 25 Galilea habaꞌa, Dekapoli,\f + \fr 4:25 \fqa Ne Gaubanana \f* Ierusalema, Iudea habaꞌa zu Ioridana vuḡa moneafa habaꞌanonoꞌo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa aradu Iesu hegotiro.
\c 5
\s1 Maḡano Haramiro
\r (Luka 6:20-23)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa horozirotene, maḡa komeꞌa itadu eꞌea ehoriro. Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe ariro.
\v 2 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadahe ihoziro,
\q1 
\v 3 “Zamaze zaharaḡa azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.
\q1 
\v 4 Zamaze areꞌenaꞌa, niauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa namiziꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 5 Zamaze roḡeḡa azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa ze Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo haba meꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 6 Badiꞌa urao haḡai duduḡa haḡaihi rae inareꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe ura niduꞌa ziniꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 7 Vaze vetuḡaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa ze vetuḡaziꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 8 Zamaze deheḡa azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa zeꞌe Badiꞌa horoniꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 9 Uniho manoḡa veize gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zeꞌe ane ubugaubuga rae huziꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 10 Badiꞌa ura haḡaeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, vazeꞌa sausauzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,
\q2 mazaḡa zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.
\p 
\v 11 Eḡe uꞌano, vazeꞌa za rae sausauziꞌetene, aduga boro ziniꞌetene, ebu ḡurireꞌenaꞌa ḡoere sauꞌa nunu hina ziꞌetene, zaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe.
\v 12 Zaꞌe matuꞌe rudanoꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa adureo naeḡa boro bagaḡa ziniꞌuma. Zeḡe vouḡaniꞌa peroveta ibiꞌa azaḡa zuni deꞌuge sausauzido.”
\s1 Dama zu Ihure Agaḡa
\r (Mareko 9:50; Luka 14:34-35)
\p 
\v 13 “Zaꞌe raha ꞌadaoꞌe dama heuḡa. Rehano dama iniganiꞌa dauḡine, nougenouge bare inidaꞌuma? Dama mene inigaꞌe ḡauni ꞌahoga veize zuni mene manoḡa ꞌahine, mae modadu vazeꞌa edene oname onaeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 14 Zaꞌe raha ꞌada aganeꞌeteꞌe agaḡa. Maḡa hitagano ogoraroteꞌe neḡa boroꞌe uꞌuranoga mene idaḡa.
\v 15 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ihure hofadu siuva ꞌuꞌuḡano mene tiꞌohe, rehano ihure odaḡa rana teadu ne zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa agazeꞌohe.
\v 16 Eꞌe teige, zae agaḡa hina vaze agazoꞌi. ꞌOugine, zeꞌa zae haḡai manoḡa horonadu Moze adureo niguniꞌuma.”
\s1 Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌa moneo Ihoziro
\p 
\v 17 “Zaꞌe eḡeꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa zu peroveta azaḡa ḡoere fahoga radu ariro rae ago zamaroꞌi. E zeḡe ḡoere fahihi radu mene ariro, rehano zeḡe ḡoereꞌa hudanoga veize ariro.
\v 18 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, adure zu raha ꞌizema dauḡogano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa boꞌaḡano komeꞌa ꞌahoga zuni mene hune dauḡiꞌuma, rehano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaꞌe hudaꞌuma.
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo iniuꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahoga variꞌine ebu vaze ꞌouge ihozine, aniꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ḡonaga rae huniꞌuma. U iniuꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa tihitihinine ebu vaze ꞌouge ihozine, aniꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ḡihiꞌaḡa rae huniꞌuma.
\v 20 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zaeꞌa Badiꞌa ubumao haḡai duduḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌeꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa mene vitizine, zaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zihiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mene reꞌuma.”
\s1 Maḡunu moneo Ihoziro
\p 
\v 21 “Ibite azaḡa mazao reiroteꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌadi zaeꞌa igiro, 'Vaze ago gorunoꞌi.\x + \xo 5:21 \xt Vaḡiniro 20:13\x* Iniuꞌa vaze ꞌahoga gorunine, kotaniꞌuma.'
\v 22 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa ane nego nabudi mazao maḡunine, kotaniꞌuma. Iniuꞌa ane nego nabudi mazao, 'Kauriḡa,' rae nine, Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo boro zamaḡano kotaniꞌuma. Ebu iniuꞌa ane nego nabudi mazao, 'Baboḡa,' rae reine, ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuniꞌuma.
\v 23 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaeꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡano ḡahunoneḡo hauꞌeteꞌe madaḡano negoḡo ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡae mazao maḡuneꞌeteꞌe zamaroꞌidene,
\v 24 ḡahunoneḡoꞌe fata genaḡano modoꞌi, ebu negoḡo vaḡe onamadu ane teite uniho manofoꞌi. Eꞌe enogano bare aradu ḡahunoneḡo hanoꞌi.
\p 
\v 25 Ḡaꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa kotao ohoꞌihi radu ani teite onamoꞌidene, ibio ḡanine ḡarihe uniho manofoꞌi. Mene ꞌougine, aniꞌa oboꞌe teadu kota vazeḡa ꞌevoreo ohoꞌiꞌuma, ebu hena kota vazeḡaniꞌa ḡuꞌa neḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌevoreo ohoꞌadu ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma.
\v 26 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, za ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo mene buaꞌuma, onamo zaeꞌa ani hadi niduꞌaꞌe baroniꞌuma.”
\s1 Ubuma Ago Ḡezanoꞌi
\p 
\v 27 “Zaꞌe edeḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Ubuma ago ḡezanoꞌi.'\x + \xo 5:27 \xt Vaḡiniro 20:14\x*
\v 28 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa roḡae ꞌahoga ḡianadu roḡae ꞌomo teite bazihi reine, aniꞌe zamaḡano ubuma ḡezaneha.
\v 29 Ḡae edaꞌe ubumaḡaniꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, eꞌe ubumaḡa ḡude modoꞌi. Mazaḡa ahiriḡo tahiḡa modeꞌetaꞌaꞌe manoḡa, aꞌe ahiriḡo niduꞌa ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuneꞌeteꞌe ufeta vitinoga.
\v 30 Ebu ḡae edaꞌe ꞌevoreꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, eꞌe ꞌevoꞌa variꞌe modoꞌi. Mazaḡa ahiriḡo tahiḡa modeꞌetaꞌaꞌe manoḡa, aꞌe ahiriḡo niduꞌa ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuneꞌeteꞌe ufeta vitinoga.”
\s1 Inuga Modeꞌeteꞌe Moneo
\r (Mataio 19:9; Mareko 10:11-12; Luka 16:18)
\p 
\v 31 “Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Iniuꞌa inuga modoꞌidene, aneꞌa ihore soꞌaḡa mirihadu inuga hanoꞌi.'\x + \xo 5:31 \xt Goro 24:1\x*
\v 32 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, iniu inugaꞌe ubuma mene ḡezaro rehano, inuga modine, iꞌaniꞌa ubuma ḡezo ibiḡano inuga tuḡuneꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Ebu iꞌaniꞌa modiroteꞌe roḡaeḡa teite hahuriroteꞌe vazeḡa zuni ubuma ḡezauꞌohe.”
\s1 Ḡoere Ago Rinede Toꞌi
\p 
\v 33 “Ibite azaḡa mazao reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌadi zaeꞌa igiro, 'Nagi ḡoeꞌa rinede toꞌidene, ago variꞌoꞌi. Badiꞌa mazao ḡoere rinede toꞌidene, huga haḡaoꞌi.'\x + \xo 5:33 \xt Naba 30:2\x*
\v 34 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, ḡoereni ꞌahoga ago rinede toꞌi. Adure niḡano ḡoere ago rinede toꞌi, mazaḡa adureꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa.
\v 35 Raha niḡano ḡoere ꞌahoga ago rinede toꞌi, mazaḡa rahaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa odaḡa tiꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa. Ierusalema niḡano ḡoere ꞌahoga ago rinede toꞌi, mazaḡa Ierusalemaꞌe Kini Ḡihiꞌaḡa ane ne boro.
\v 36 Ḡoere rinede tiroteꞌe mene haḡaine rudaꞌuma rae ago ḡoitoroꞌi,\f + \fr 5:36 \fqa Vadinize rana ḡoere ꞌahoga ago rinede toꞌi \f* mazaḡa ḡabonezeꞌe zaeꞌa mene haḡairo. Zaꞌe vadinize iguze tiba zuni mae ꞌurunoga zu mae ḡuḡunoga mene idaḡa.
\v 37 Zaeꞌa nagini haḡaiꞌuma rae roꞌidene, 'Oꞌe,' rae tauḡoꞌi. Ga mene haḡaiꞌuma rae roꞌidene, 'Mene,' rae tauḡoꞌi. Ḡoere ꞌahogaꞌahoga ragate tiꞌetaꞌaꞌe sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Satanionoꞌo fureruꞌohe.”
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌano Ago Naenaetitoꞌi
\r (Luka 6:29-30)
\p 
\v 38 “Zaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi igiro, 'Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡae ubuma sausaunoꞌidene, ḡae zuni ane ubuma sausaunoꞌi. Ebu aneꞌa ḡae ḡonone vahegoꞌidene, ḡae zuni ane ḡonone vahegoꞌi.'\x + \xo 5:38 \xt Vaḡiniro 21:24; Dibuꞌo 24:20; Goro 19:21\x*
\v 39 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, vaze sauꞌa mazao ago naenaetitoꞌi. Iniuꞌa zae edaꞌe ḡanineḡa faꞌonoꞌidene, zae kauri ḡanineḡa zuni notonohanoꞌi.
\v 40 Iniuꞌa zae zizuni dabuaḡa mouga rae kotazihi roꞌidene, raga dabuaḡa zuni hanoꞌi.
\v 41 Iniu zaeꞌa ane ḡau odohadu tiba kilomita onamoga tuḡutuḡuzoꞌidene, aheu kilomita onamoꞌi.
\v 42 Iniuꞌa nagini umizoꞌidene hau tauḡoꞌi, zu ḡauze ꞌahoga umizadu vesuꞌu baroniꞌuma rae roꞌidene, ago hezahohanoꞌi.”
\s1 Agire Azaḡa Zamare Borofoꞌi
\r (Luka 6:27-28, 32-36)
\p 
\v 43 “Zaꞌe edeḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Ḡae nabudi zamare borofoꞌi, ebu ḡae agire vazeḡa heꞌeheꞌenoꞌi.'\x + \xo 5:43 \xt Dibuꞌo 19:18\x*
\v 44 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zae agire azaḡa zamare borofoꞌi ebu zae sausauzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa veize kuranoꞌi.
\v 45 ꞌOugine, zaꞌe Moze adureo ubuga rae reꞌuma. Mazaḡa Mozeꞌe vaze manoḡa zu vaze sauꞌa veize idane mada aganoziniꞌohe, ebu vaze duduḡa zu vaze veꞌoḡa veize idane irugu tuḡuneꞌohe.
\v 46 Zaeꞌa zae zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo zamare borofine, Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe naeḡa mene ziniꞌuma. Takesi azaḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa rehano, zeḡe zuni zeḡe zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zamare borofeꞌohe.
\v 47 Zaeꞌa zae nego nabudi teite daꞌo obotitine, vaze nunu mene vitiziꞌuma. Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa zuni ꞌouge haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 48 Eꞌanoꞌo zae Badiꞌa adureo mazaoꞌe veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa teige, zae zuni veꞌoḡani ꞌahoga ago haḡaoꞌi.”
\c 6
\s1 Zahara Azaḡa Zenoꞌi
\p 
\v 1 “Zaꞌe vazeꞌa ḡiazoga veize vaze zamao haḡai duduḡa mene haḡaifine tohutohoꞌi. Mene tohutohine, adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe Mozeꞌa naeḡa manoḡa mene ziniꞌuma.
\v 2 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡau ꞌahoga zahara vazeḡa haune, zama guhi azaḡa teige ago hirihiroꞌi. Zama guhi azaḡaꞌe vazeꞌa niguzoga veize nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano zu ibio haḡae fureneꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zeꞌe naeze niduꞌa mae hauḡiro.
\v 3 Ḡau ꞌahoga zahara vazeḡa haune, zae nabudi uhiḡa vazeḡa zu ago ihonoꞌi.\f + \fr 6:3 \fqa edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌaniꞌa haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe kauri ꞌevoꞌaniꞌa mene ederifine sifu hanoꞌi \f*
\v 4 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene ederoga veize sifu hanoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Mozeꞌa haḡaize sifu horonadu naeḡa manoḡa ziniꞌuma.”
\s1 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Kuru Ihoziro
\r (Luka 11:2-4)
\p 
\v 5 “Zaꞌe kuranoꞌidene, zama guhi azaḡa teige ago kuranoꞌi. Mazaḡa zeꞌe vazeꞌa horozoga veize nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano zu ibi boro genaḡano edauꞌenaꞌa, kuranoga urateꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, ze naeze niduꞌa mae hauḡiro.
\v 6 Zaꞌe kuranoꞌidene, bazuni habaꞌa diuḡadu ibiheta haranoꞌi, ebu mene horoneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa, Moze mazao kuranoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Mozeꞌa zae haḡai sifu horonadu naeḡa manoḡa ziniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 7 Ebu za kuranoꞌidene, Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa teige, huga oꞌoꞌa ḡoeꞌa hina ago barebare roꞌi. Mazaḡa zeꞌe ḡoere ḡehaḡa hina kuraune, Badiꞌaꞌa igiꞌuma rae zamareꞌohe.
\v 8 Ze ago hegotoꞌi, mazaḡa Mozeꞌe zaeꞌa ꞌizema umidogano nagini urateꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\p 
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe ꞌahige kuranoꞌi:
\q1 'Emeḡe Mama adureo,
\q1 eme umiꞌeꞌohe, ḡa niḡoꞌe zaḡoḡa reꞌuma,
\q1 
\v 10 ḡaeꞌa ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma,
\q1 zu adureo ḡae uraꞌe hudauꞌeteꞌe teige, raha ꞌadao zuni hudaꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 11 Izidi emeḡeꞌa atiteꞌe ogomuḡa rifiꞌenoꞌi,
\q1 
\v 12 ebu emeꞌa emeḡe mazao sauꞌa haḡairoteꞌe azaḡa haḡaize sauꞌa rae modiroteꞌe teige, emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modoꞌi.
\q1 
\v 13 Ebu eme haḡai sauꞌa haḡaihi raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡanonoꞌo tutufe vaḡifoꞌi,
\q2 ebu Satani mazaonoꞌo mae ḡabofoꞌi.'\f + \fr 6:13 \fqa Ḡaeꞌa ibitoziꞌetaꞌaꞌe ebu gigiꞌaḡo zu niḡo ḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu. Amen. \f*
\m 
\v 14 Zaeꞌa vaze haḡai sauꞌa rae modine, Moze adureo radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa zae haḡai sauꞌa zuni rae modiꞌuma.
\v 15 Rehano zaeꞌa vaze haḡai sauꞌa mene rae modine, Mozeꞌa zuni zae haḡai sauꞌa mene rae modiꞌuma.”
\s1 Ogomu moneo Zaḡozaḡeꞌeteꞌe Ihoziro
\p 
\v 16 “Zaeꞌa ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡoꞌidene, zama guhi azaḡa teige, ago vetuḡarau radoꞌi. Zeꞌe vazeꞌa horozadu zeḡeꞌa ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡeꞌeteꞌe ederoga veize, mene vireꞌohe zu iguze mene siꞌeꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zeꞌe naeze niduꞌa mae hauḡiro.
\v 17 Rehano zaeꞌa ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡoꞌidene, viradu iguze siꞌoꞌi.
\v 18 ꞌOugine, vazeꞌa zaꞌe zaḡozaḡeꞌeteꞌe mene ederiꞌuma, rehano mene horoneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa, Moze daꞌo ederiꞌuma. Ebu Mozeꞌa zaꞌa sifu haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa horonadu naeze ziniꞌuma.”
\s1 Ḡau Naeḡa Boroboro Adureo Nuꞌone Toꞌi
\r (Luka 12:33-34)
\p 
\v 19 “Zae veize raha ꞌadao ḡauze naeḡa boroboro ago nuꞌone toꞌi. Raha ꞌadaoꞌe zuhiꞌa sausauneꞌohe, zu atenarauꞌohe, ebu ḡonoreꞌa varade diuḡadu ḡonotuꞌohe.
\v 20 Eꞌanoꞌo zae veize ḡauze naeḡa boroꞌe adureo nuꞌone toꞌi. Eꞌea zuhiꞌa mene sausauneꞌohe, zu mene atenarauꞌohe, ebu ḡonoreꞌa varade diuḡadu mene ḡonotuꞌohe.
\v 21 Mazaḡa za ḡauze naeḡa boro nouma tine, zamaze zuni eꞌea tiꞌohe.”
\s1 Ahiri Ihureḡa
\r (Luka 11:34-36)
\p 
\v 22 “Za ubumaꞌe ahiri ihureḡa. Ubumazeꞌe manoḡa reine, ahirizeꞌe agaḡaniꞌa iriꞌavoniꞌuma.
\v 23 Rehano ubumazeꞌe sauꞌa reine, ahirizeꞌe uzaboꞌa iriꞌavoniꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo zae zamao agaḡaꞌe uzaboraune, zaꞌe uzabo ḡiḡiꞌaḡa hune zamaḡano radiꞌuma!”
\s1 Badiꞌa Aheu mazao Ago Kuranoꞌi
\r (Luka 16:13)
\p 
\v 24 “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zuhiꞌa aheu veize gauoga mene idaḡa. Ani ꞌahogaꞌe heꞌeheꞌeniꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe zamare borofiꞌuma. Ebu ꞌahoga veize faine gauiꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe turuniꞌuma. Eꞌe teige, zaꞌe Badiꞌa ebu hadi, aheu veize gauogaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\s1 Ago Zamare Adudanoꞌi
\r (Luka 12:22-34)
\p 
\v 25 “Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe. Zae ḡabone veize nagi ogomu aꞌuma ga nagini gagiꞌuma ebu ahirize veize nagi dabua vidaꞌuma rae ago zamare adudanoꞌi. Mazaḡa ḡaboneꞌe ogomu vitinoga, zu ahiriꞌe dabua vitinoga.
\v 26 Hitanao rafiuꞌeteꞌe niniḡa ḡiazoꞌi. Ze ezone mene ḡorauꞌohe, mene hiriveꞌohe, zu ogomuze godoḡo neḡano mene nuꞌone tiꞌohe. Rehano Moze adureo radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa ḡubuzeꞌohe. Zaꞌe nini vitize hunoga.
\v 27 Zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa zamare adudu radiune, ḡaboneḡaꞌe tahiḡa nu faraꞌumahe?
\p 
\v 28 Za nougaꞌahi dabua uꞌano zamare aduduꞌohe? Butu kakaḡaꞌe nougenouge ḡuhureꞌeteꞌe ḡianoꞌi. Ze mene gaueꞌohe ga dabuaze mene turineꞌohe.
\v 29 Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, butu kakaḡani ꞌahoga zuni maꞌora vazeḡa kini Solomonaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe dabuaḡa manomano vitine hunoga.
\v 30 Butu veḡaꞌe izidi ḡaboga, u ohoḡoreꞌe masinadu ireo hufi haoniꞌuma, rehano Badiꞌaꞌa dabua vidohauꞌohe. Zaꞌe ve vitinoga, eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa dabua manoḡa ufeta vidoziniꞌuma. Rehano zaꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe tahiḡa fase!
\p 
\v 31 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe nagini aꞌuma ga nagini gagiꞌuma ga nagi dabua vidaꞌuma rae ago zamare adudanoꞌi.
\v 32 Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡaniꞌa eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa vaḡe inareꞌohe, rehano Moze adureo radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe edereꞌohe.
\v 33 Ibite geno Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazoga zu ane ura haḡaoga vaḡoꞌi, ꞌougine eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa zuni ziniꞌuma.
\v 34 Eꞌanoꞌo za ohoḡore moneo ago zamare adudanoꞌi. Mazaḡa ohoḡore adugaꞌe ohoḡoruꞌu zamariꞌuma. Izidiꞌe izidi aduga daꞌo zamariꞌuma.”
\c 7
\s1 Vaze mazao Sauꞌa rae Ago Roꞌi
\r (Luka 6:37-38, 41-42)
\p 
\v 1 “Vaze mazao sauꞌa rae ago roꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa zuni zae mazao sauꞌa rae mene ziꞌuma.
\v 2 Mazaḡa zaeꞌa vaze mazao sauꞌa rae reine, eꞌe moneo Badiꞌaꞌa zuni zae mazao sauꞌa rae reꞌuma. Zaeꞌa vaze nagini hauꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌouge zae ziniꞌuma.
\v 3 Zaꞌe nabudize ubuma beꞌa dinunuḡa ḡianeꞌohe. Rehano nougadu zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa mene horoneꞌohe?
\v 4 Zaꞌe zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa mene horoneꞌe rehano, nabudize mazao ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Eḡe nabudi, eḡeꞌa ubumaḡo beꞌa dinunu eꞌe mae vaḡinihi.'
\v 5 Zama guhi azaḡa, ibite geno zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa eꞌe mae vaḡinoꞌi. ꞌOugine, zaeꞌa faine ehamanadu nabudize ubuma beꞌa dinunuḡa mae vaḡiniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 6 Ḡau zaḡoḡa ḡuni ago hanoꞌi, ebu zae hadi naeḡa boro aba zamao ago feunoꞌi. Zeꞌe oda hina edene ḡuzuhiꞌuma zu vaetadu zae vihoziꞌuma.”
\s1 Badiꞌa Uminoꞌi
\r (Luka 11:9-13)
\p 
\v 7 “Uminoꞌi, ꞌougine ziniꞌuma. Vaḡoꞌi, ꞌougine horoniꞌuma. Ibiheta toketokeroꞌi, ꞌougine ibiheta vavaoziniꞌuma.
\v 8 Umineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ziniꞌuma, zu vaḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa horoniꞌuma, ebu ibiheta toketokereꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ibiheta vavaoziniꞌuma.
\v 9 Zae boꞌaḡano iniu ubuganiꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga umidine, moganiꞌa hadi haꞌumahe?
\v 10 Ga ubuganiꞌa ḡozone umidine, moganiꞌa mohe haꞌumahe?
\v 11 Zaꞌe sauꞌa azaḡa rehano, ḡahunone manoḡa ubudeze zenoga urateꞌohe. Eꞌe teige, Moze adureo radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ane mazao umideꞌeteꞌe azaḡa hube hune ḡahunone manoḡa ziniꞌuma!
\v 12 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡau niduꞌa moneo vazeꞌa zae mazao manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe uratoꞌidene, zae zuni zeḡe mazao manoḡa haḡaoꞌi. ꞌAdiꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa zu peroveta azaḡaniꞌa ihoziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.”
\s1 Ibiheta Kokosiḡa
\r (Luka 13:24)
\p 
\v 13 “Ibiheta kokosiḡa diuḡoꞌi. Mazaḡa runeo diuḡeꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa ibihetaḡaꞌe rafaḡa zu boro ꞌahine, eꞌe ibiḡano diuḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa.
\v 14 U ḡabone tuḡutuḡu diuḡeꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa ibihetaḡaꞌe kokosiḡa zu eꞌe ibiḡano onamogaꞌe riḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌe ibihetaḡa vaḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tahiḡa daꞌo.”
\s1 Ire ebu Ire Maḡa
\r (Luka 6:43-44)
\p 
\v 15 “Ḡuriro peroveta azaḡa ḡiazoꞌi. Ze mamoe roḡeḡa teige ariꞌuma, rehano zeḡe zamaꞌe butu ḡuniḡa vihovihoḡa heuḡa.
\v 16 Ireꞌe maḡa horonadu nagi ireḡa ederiꞌuma. Vaini maḡaꞌe ire renoganonoꞌo mene iniꞌohe, zu figi maḡaꞌe ḡunu renoganonoꞌo mene iniꞌohe.
\v 17 Eꞌe teige, ire manoḡa niduꞌaꞌe maḡa manoḡa iniꞌohe, u ire sauꞌaꞌe maḡa sauꞌa iniꞌohe.
\v 18 Ire manoḡaꞌe maḡa sauꞌa mene iniꞌohe, u ire sauꞌaꞌe maḡa manoḡa mene iniꞌohe.
\v 19 Maḡa manoḡa mene iniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa niduꞌaꞌe udi modeꞌohe ebu ire rogao hufi haoneꞌohe.
\v 20 Eꞌanoꞌo zeḡe haḡai horonadu zeꞌe vaze nagiga ederiꞌuma.”
\s1 Badiꞌa Ura Haḡaiꞌuma
\r (Luka 13:25-27)
\p 
\v 21 “Eḡe mazao, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, Zuhiꞌa Boro,' rae huheꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano mene niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano diuḡiꞌuma. Rehano eḡe Mama adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe, ane ura haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa daꞌo diuḡiꞌuma.
\v 22 Badiꞌa kota madaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige ihiꞌuma, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, Zuhiꞌa Boro, emeꞌe ḡae niḡano Badiꞌa ḡoere rae furenido, zu ḡae niḡano vine sauꞌa hegoze buzido, zu ḡae niḡano gigiꞌa haḡaiḡa ḡehaḡa haḡaido.'
\v 23 ꞌOugine, eḡeꞌa dehene ziꞌuma, 'E zaꞌe mene hune ederiro. Haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa, eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.'”
\s1 Egadu Haḡaeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa
\r (Luka 6:47-49)
\p 
\v 24 “Eꞌanoꞌo eḡe ḡoere egadu ꞌouge haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe huhuzaḡa. Aniꞌe vatava rana neḡa ogoraroteꞌe vazeḡa heuḡa.
\v 25 Iruguꞌa ruꞌanadu zobozoboꞌa bororarotene, ebu zavara boroꞌa feuradu neḡa beirotene, ne aꞌe mene higaro, mazaḡa vatava rana ogoraro.
\v 26 Rehano eḡe ḡoere egadu ꞌouge mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe kauriḡa. Aniꞌe niꞌuri rana neḡa ogoraroteꞌe vazeḡa heuḡa.
\v 27 Iruguꞌa ruꞌanadu zobozoboꞌa bororarotene, zu zavara boroꞌa feuradu neḡa beirotene, eꞌe neḡaꞌe higau bauradu fahau ḡuzuhiro.”
\p 
\v 28 Iesuꞌa eꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hauḡirotene, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ane ihore uꞌano zaguzagaro.
\v 29 Mazaḡa Iesuꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teige mene ihoziro, rehano Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa hina ihoziro. \fig Vatava rana ogoraroteꞌe neḡaꞌe mene hagariro|src="GR-lllf02n.tif" size="col" ref="7:24-27"\fig*
\c 8
\s1 Refera Vazeḡa Fainiro
\r (Mareko 1:40-45; Luka 5:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa maḡanonoꞌo ovairotene, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ane hegote onamiro.
\v 2 Ebu refera vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ani vaḡe aradu ane zamao obenaḡa hina tuḡadu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa uratine, eḡe faihogaꞌe idaraꞌuma.”
\v 3 Iesuꞌa ꞌevoꞌa einadu vaze eꞌe oboniro ebu niro, “E urateꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe deheru manoroꞌi!” ꞌOugadu refera eꞌeꞌa zogone manoriro.
\v 4 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi. Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa vaḡe onamadu ahiriḡo ihonoꞌi. Ebu ḡaeꞌa manorateꞌe vazeꞌa ederifine, Moseꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡahunoneḡa mae onamadu Badiꞌa dibuꞌohanoꞌi.”
\s1 Uti Vazeḡa Boroꞌa Iesu mazao Firo
\r (Luka 7:1-10; Ioane 4:43-54)
\p 
\v 5 Iesuꞌa Kaperanauma diuḡirotene, uti vazeḡa boro ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu dananoga uminiro,
\v 6 ebu ꞌahige rae niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe ahiꞌa haganoga mene idaḡa radu neo bazeꞌohe zu ufeta giginadu ḡaniḡanauꞌohe.”
\v 7 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡeꞌa onamadu fainiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 8 Rehano uti vazeḡa boroꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eꞌe mene vaze manoḡa, eꞌanoꞌo ḡaeꞌa eḡe ne diuḡogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Rehano ḡae ḡoere daꞌo roꞌi, ꞌougine eḡe tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa manoriꞌuma.
\v 9 Mazaḡa eḡe zuni vaze ꞌahoga ꞌuꞌuḡano gaueꞌohe, ebu uti azaḡa zuni eḡe ꞌuꞌuḡano gaueꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa uti vazeḡa ꞌahi ninaꞌa, 'Onamoꞌi,' raꞌetene aniꞌe onameꞌohe, ebu ꞌahoga ꞌomo ninaꞌa, 'Aroꞌi,' raꞌetene aniꞌe areꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga ninaꞌa, 'ꞌAdi haḡaoꞌi,' raꞌetene aniꞌe haḡaeꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 10 Iesuꞌa eꞌe ḡoeꞌa igirotene zaguzagaro ebu ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Isaraela azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahige fie gigaruꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe e ꞌize mene horoneha.
\v 11 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo zu madaꞌa zubureꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo aradu adureo Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano Aberahamo, Isako zu Iakobo teite ogau tiburaꞌuma.
\v 12 Rehano Iuda azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ze zuhiꞌaziꞌohe rae zamareꞌe rehano, enona mae feuzadu uzabo zamaḡano radiꞌuma, ebu eꞌea niaꞌuma zu ḡononeze atitiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 13 Ebu Iesuꞌa uti vazeḡa boro niro, “Onamoꞌi. Ḡaꞌe eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ḡae tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe manoriꞌuma.” Aniꞌa ꞌouge reiroteꞌe madaḡano tuḡure vazeḡa aꞌe manoriro.
\s1 Vaze Ḡehaḡa Faiziro
\r (Mareko 1:29-34; Luka 4:38-41)
\p 
\v 14 Ebu Iesuꞌa Petero ne diuḡirotene, Petero emoḡa roḡaeḡa ahiꞌaniꞌa gigine runadu evane rana baze radoga horoniro.
\v 15 Iesuꞌa roḡae eꞌe ꞌevoꞌa obonirotene, ahiꞌa gigiꞌa ꞌai dauḡiro. Ebu ani iḡunadu Iesu veize ogomu ruhibiro.
\p 
\v 16 Ḡoravararotene, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa vine sauꞌaniꞌa ragano reiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡehaḡa Iesu vaḡe tutuze ariro. Aniꞌe ḡoere hina vine sauꞌa hegoze buziro ebu ugi azaḡa niduꞌa faiziro.
\v 17 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro, “Aniꞌe emeḡe gigiꞌa meiro ebu emeḡe ugi odohiro.”\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Isaia 53:4\x*
\s1 Iesu Hegoteꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa
\r (Luka 9:57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Iesuꞌa ane uhiḡano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa horozirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Duꞌura moneafa fare onamihi.”
\v 19 Eꞌe madaḡano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, ḡaꞌa noꞌe onamine eḡeꞌa ḡae hegotiꞌuma.”
\v 20 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Butu ḡuniḡaꞌe bazuni habaꞌazeta ebu hitana niniḡaꞌe nezeta. Rehano Vaze Ubugaꞌe bazuni habaꞌa oꞌoꞌa.”
\p 
\v 21 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ibite geno mamahe guri onamihi.”
\v 22 Rehano Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe eḡe hegotoꞌi. Rune azaḡaniꞌa rune azaḡa guriꞌuma.”
\s1 Zavara ꞌUiro
\r (Mareko 4:35-41; Luka 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡasio tirirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ani hegote tiriro.
\v 24 Ebu zavara boroꞌa duꞌurao feuriro ebu saꞌuꞌa ḡasio kafere diuḡiro. Rehano Iesuꞌe baze radiro.
\v 25 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ane vaḡe onamadu evaniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme ḡabofoꞌi! Eme hunuhuneꞌohe!”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Za nougadu rihauꞌohe? Zaꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe komeꞌa!” Ebu ani iḡunadu zavara zu saꞌu roziro. ꞌOugirotene, zavara zu saꞌuꞌe roḡeru hauḡiro.
\p 
\v 27 Ebu zeꞌa zaguzagauꞌenaꞌa, ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌahiꞌe nagi vaze? Zavara zu saꞌuꞌa zuni ani ḡoere egohuꞌohe!”
\s1 Vine Sauꞌazeta Azaḡa Faiziro
\r (Mareko 5:1-20; Luka 8:26-39)
\p 
\v 28 Iesuꞌa duꞌura moneafa, Gadara\f + \fr 8:28 \fqa Gerasa \f* azaḡa habao feurirotene, vine sauꞌazeta azaḡa aheuꞌa idu habaꞌanonoꞌo areꞌenogano Iesu hidiro. Zamazeꞌe ufeta ḡugiziro ꞌahine, eꞌe ibiḡano vazeꞌa onamoga mene idararo.
\v 29 Ebu ze Iesu ḡihau ḡoreniro, “Badiꞌa Ubuga, ḡaꞌe emeḡe mazao nagini urateꞌohe? Ḡaꞌe, kota madaḡa ḡonaga ꞌizema mougano, aduga rifoga veize emeḡe vaḡe arahe?”
\p 
\v 30 Zeḡe mazaonoꞌo faḡano aba ḡehaḡaniꞌa ogau radiunu.
\v 31 Ebu vine sauꞌasauꞌaniꞌa Iesu uminiro, “Ḡaeꞌa eme hegofe bufoꞌidene, aba ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌomo mazao tuḡufoꞌi.”
\v 32 Ebu aniꞌa vine sauꞌasauꞌa ziro, “Onamoꞌi!” ꞌOuge reirotene, ze vaze aheu mazaonoꞌo buanadu aba ḡuḡuvaḡa zamaḡano diuḡiro. Ebu aba ḡuḡuvaḡa niduꞌaꞌe maḡa komeꞌa gagaḡanonoꞌo dure ovoradu duꞌurao hunuhune rudaro.
\v 33 ꞌOugirotene, aba taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa neze ferau manahadu vine sauꞌasauꞌaniꞌa ragano reiroteꞌe azaḡa mazao naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa meꞌodoziniro.
\v 34 Ebu ne azaḡa niduꞌa buanadu Iesu hidoga veize ariro. Ze Iesu horonirotene, aniꞌe zeḡe habaꞌanonoꞌo vaḡinoga uminiro.
\c 9
\s1 Ahiꞌa Mene Haganeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Fainiro
\r (Mareko 2:1-12; Luka 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ḡasio tiradu duꞌura moneafa fariro ebu aneꞌa radiunuteꞌe neḡa boro, Kaperanauma bare onamiro.
\v 2 Ebu vaze nuꞌa ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga faratao bazune teadu ani vaḡe herate ariro. Zeḡeꞌa Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe Iesuꞌa horonirotene, ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa niro, “Ubude, zamaḡo rinedoꞌi. Ḡae haḡai sauꞌa ꞌai aḡutu modeha.”
\v 3 ꞌOugirotene, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌe ꞌahige zamariro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌohe!”
\p 
\v 4 Iesuꞌe zeḡeꞌa nagini zamareꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederadu ziro, “Nougadu za zamarone sauꞌa zamareꞌohe?
\v 5 Ugi vazeḡa mazao nagi ḡoeꞌa nine, ufiḡa? 'Ḡae haḡai sauꞌa ꞌai rae modeha,' rae niꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ga, 'Iḡunadu onamoꞌi,' rae niꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa?
\v 6 Rehano Vaze Ubugaꞌe raha ꞌadao haḡai sauꞌa rae modeꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa meirotaꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa ederiꞌuma.” Ebu Iesuꞌa ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa niro, “Iḡunoꞌi ebu farataḡo madu neḡo onamoꞌi.”
\v 7 Ebu ugi vazeḡa ꞌai iḡunadu neḡa onamiro.
\v 8 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe eꞌe horonirotene rihau rudaro ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌuguḡa gigiꞌaḡa vaze ziniroteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa niguniro.
\s1 Mataio Huniro
\r (Mareko 2:13-17; Luka 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Iesuꞌa eꞌeanoꞌo iḡunadu onamirotene, vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Mataioꞌa takesi fataḡa uhiḡano ehore radiroteꞌe horoniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.” Ebu Mataioꞌa iḡunadu Iesu hegotiro.
\p 
\v 10 Iesuꞌa Mataio neo ḡorava ogomu aroteꞌe zamaḡano, takesi azaḡa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ogau tiburaro.
\v 11 Farisea azaḡaniꞌa eꞌe horonirotene, Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa ḡadiziro, “Nougadu zae ihore vazeḡaꞌe takesi azaḡa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa teite ogau tiburuꞌohe?”
\p 
\v 12 Iesuꞌa eꞌe egadu ziro, “Ugi oꞌoꞌa azaḡaꞌe gohe vazeḡa mene vaḡeꞌohe, rehano ugi azaḡaꞌe gohe vazeḡa vaḡeꞌohe.
\v 13 Zaꞌe onamadu Badiꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi huga ederoꞌi, 'Eꞌe dibuꞌo mene urateꞌohe, rehano zaeꞌa vaze vetuḡazoga urateꞌohe.'\x + \xo 9:13 \xt Hosea 6:6 \x* E iniu zeḡeꞌa bare duduḡa azaḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe azaḡa huzoga radu mene ariro, rehano iniu zeḡeꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe azaḡa huzoga radu ariro.”
\s1 Ogomu moneo Zaḡozaḡeꞌeteꞌe
\r (Mareko 2:18-22; Luka 5:33-39)
\p 
\v 14 Ebu Ioane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Eme zu Farisea azaḡaꞌe ḡae ḡehaḡa ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡeꞌohe. Rehano ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe nougadu ogomu moneo mene zaḡozaḡeꞌohe?”
\v 15 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hahu muiḡa madaḡano hahu ohozeḡa iziganiꞌa huziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe, hahu ohozeḡa iziga teite radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zamazeꞌa aradu niaꞌumahe? Rehano zeḡe mazaonoꞌo hahu ohozeḡa izigaꞌe mae vaḡiniteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano ze ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 16 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa dabua iziga variꞌe madu dabua amahiḡa mene banineꞌohe, mazaḡa dabuaḡa vuzuꞌine, dabua siꞌiga izigaꞌe ḡuanadu amahiḡa hutubiꞌuma zu borofe zigiꞌuma.
\v 17 Ebu vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa vaini vuḡa fuse\f + \fr 9:17 \ft Vaini vuḡa fuseḡaꞌe mani ogaḡa hina haḡairo. \f* amahiḡa zamaḡano vaini vuḡa iziga mene beꞌune ufiꞌohe. Beꞌune ufine, vaini vuḡa iziganiꞌa bare busure bororanadu vaini vuḡa fuse amahiḡaniꞌa zigaꞌuma, ebu vaini vuḡaꞌe sore rururaꞌuma zu vaini vuḡa fuse amahiḡa sausauniꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo vaini vuḡa izigaꞌe vaini vuḡa fuse izigano beune ufine, aheuni manoḡa radiꞌuma.”
\s1 Rune Roḡae Tahiꞌaḡa ebu Ugi Roḡaeḡa
\r (Mareko 5:21-43; Luka 8:40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Iesuꞌa eꞌe ḡoeꞌa ziꞌeteꞌea, nuꞌonuꞌo neḡa vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu vaḡe ariro. Ebu Iesu zamao obenaḡa hina tuḡadu niro, “Eḡe aboeꞌe iziduꞌu rudaneha. Rehano ḡaeꞌa aradu ani rana ꞌevoꞌo toꞌi, ꞌougine ani ḡabodiꞌuma.”
\v 19 Ebu Iesuꞌa iḡunadu ani teite onamiro ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa zuni ani teite onamiro.
\p 
\v 20 Eꞌe ibiḡano roḡae ugi madu muri gaubanana aheu fare adugano radiunuteꞌe roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu ḡaruna aradu ani dabua ꞌariḡa tahiḡa oboniro.
\v 21 Mazaḡa aniꞌe ꞌahige zamariro, “E ani dabua tahiḡa obonine, manoriꞌuma.”
\v 22 Ebu Iesuꞌa tehadu ani ḡianadu niro, “Aboe, zamaḡo rinedoꞌi. Ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ugiḡoꞌa manoreha.” ꞌOuge reirotene, ani manoriro. \fig Ugi roḡaeḡaniꞌa Iesu dabua ꞌariḡa oboniro|src="WA03827b.tif" size="col" ref="9:20-22"\fig*
\p 
\v 23 Iesuꞌa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡa vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa neo feurirotene, rune vazeḡa veize suraꞌi hodiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu borofe haraeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ḡuḡuvaḡa horoziro.
\v 24 Ebu aneꞌa ziro, “Zae niduꞌa buanoꞌi. Roḡae komeꞌa aꞌe mene rudaneha, rehano bazeꞌohe.” Rehano zeꞌe Iesu eḡofoharo.
\v 25 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa enoneo tuḡuze buziroteꞌe ḡarugano, ne zamaḡa diuḡadu roḡae komeꞌa ꞌevoꞌa oboniro. ꞌOugadu ani iḡuniro.
\v 26 Ebu eꞌe hariḡaꞌe eꞌe habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano bororaro.
\s1 Ubumaze Kuruḡa Azaḡa Aheu Faiziro
\p 
\v 27 Iesuꞌa eꞌea mode onamirotene, ubumaze kuruḡa azaḡa aheuꞌa ani hegotiro. Zeꞌa ḡihau huaro, “Davida mariga, eme vetuḡafoꞌi!”
\v 28 Iesuꞌa ne diuḡirotene, ubuma kuruḡa azaḡaniꞌa ane vaḡe ariro. Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe eḡeꞌa faizoga idaḡa rae mae ḡihiheꞌehe?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro.”
\v 29 Ebu aniꞌa ubumaze obonadu ziro, “Zaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano ubumazeꞌa manoriꞌuma.”
\v 30 ꞌOugirotene, ubumazeꞌa raꞌaro. Ebu Iesuꞌa riḡa ziro, “Zae mazao naginiꞌa fureranateꞌe vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi.”
\v 31 Rehano ze onamadu eꞌe habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano ani hari rae ḡehaniro.
\s1 Mumutafa Vazeḡa Fainiro
\p 
\v 32 Ebu ze neonoꞌo buau onamirotene, vaze nuꞌa vaze ꞌahoga Iesu vaḡe tutune ariro. Vine sauꞌaniꞌa vaze eꞌe ragano radu aniꞌe ḡoeroga mene idararo.
\v 33 Ebu Iesuꞌa vine sauꞌa vaze eꞌe mazaonoꞌo hegone bunirotene, mumutafa vazeḡaniꞌa ḡoeriro. Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa zaguzaganadu reiro, “Ibite Isaraela habaꞌano ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa mene fureraro.”
\v 34 Rehano Farisea azaḡaniꞌa reiro, “Iesuꞌe vine sauꞌa zuhiꞌaḡa gigiꞌaḡa hina vine sauꞌasauꞌa hegoze buzeꞌohe.”
\s1 Gau Azaḡaꞌe Tahiḡa
\p 
\v 35 Iesuꞌe ne boro nunu zu ne komeꞌa nunu ragave onamadu Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano ihoziro, zu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡa haramiro. Ebu ugi zu gigiꞌa niduꞌa fainiro.
\v 36 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa horozadu vetuḡaziro, mazaḡa zeꞌe vazeꞌa mene taufeꞌeteꞌe mamoeḡa teige ufeta taoraro zu dana ꞌahoga mene hidiro.
\v 37 ꞌOugadu ani ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Hiriviteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa bagaḡa, rehano gau azaḡaꞌe tahiḡa.
\v 38 Eꞌanoꞌo hiriveꞌeteꞌe Zuhiꞌaḡa Boro mazao gau azaḡa ane mebao tuḡuzoga veize uminoꞌi.”
\c 10
\s1 Iesu Apostolo Azaḡa Gaubanana Aheu Fare
\r (Mareko 3:13-19; Luka 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare huze nuꞌoziro, ebu vine sauꞌa hegoze buzeꞌeteꞌe zu ugi nunu faineꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa ziniro.
\v 2 Iesu apostolo gaubanana aheu fare nizeꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Ibiꞌaꞌe Simona (niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Petero), ani negoḡa Anderea, Zebedeo ubuga Iakobo zu ane negoḡa Ioane,
\v 3 Filipi, Batolomeo, Tomasi, takesi vazeḡa Mataio, Alefeo ubuga Iakobo, Tadeo,
\v 4 Zelota\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Roma gavamani utitoziniroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Zelota duḡuru rae huziro. \f* vazeḡa Simona ebu Iesu revoharoteꞌe vazeḡa, Isakariota vazeḡa Iuda.
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌa Gaubanana Aheu Fareꞌa Ragave Onamadu Haramiro
\r (Mareko 6:7-13; Luka 9:1-6)
\p 
\v 5 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige ihoziro, “Iuda mene azaḡa haba ago onamoꞌi, ebu Samaria azaḡa ne zuni ago diuḡoꞌi.
\v 6 Rehano Isaraela habaꞌano dauḡiroteꞌe mamoeḡa vaḡe onamoꞌi.
\v 7 Ebu neḡaneḡa ragave onamoꞌidene, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai haniteha,' rae haramozenoꞌi.
\v 8 Ugi azaḡa faizoꞌi, rune azaḡa ḡabozoꞌi, refera azaḡa faizoꞌi ebu vine sauꞌa hegoze buzoꞌi. Zaeꞌa naeḡa oꞌoꞌa ḡauḡa hidiro ꞌahine, naeḡa ago maꞌenaꞌa, ḡahugoꞌi.
\v 9 Niharazeo hadi boro ga komeꞌa zuni ago odohoꞌi.
\v 10 Zae ragavo veize nihara ga dabua ꞌahoga ga tamaka ga tuḡu ago odohoꞌi, mazaḡa gau azaḡaꞌe nagini urateꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe hideꞌohe.
\p 
\v 11 Noꞌe ne boro ga ne komeꞌa diuḡoꞌidene, zae mae ḡihiziteꞌe vazeḡa vaḡadu ane neo radoꞌi onamo ne eꞌe mode iḡunoꞌi.
\v 12 Ane ne diuḡoꞌidene, ibite geno ꞌahige unihoꞌi, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zama roḡeḡa zenoꞌi.'
\v 13 Ebu eꞌe neo radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zama roḡeḡa urateꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reine, zaeꞌa rateꞌe zama roḡeḡaꞌe zeḡe rana radiꞌuma. U mene reine, zaeꞌa rateꞌe zama roḡeḡa eꞌeꞌa zae bare vaḡiꞌuma.
\v 14 Ne azaḡaniꞌa zae mene mae zouzoꞌidene, ga ḡoereze mene egozenoꞌidene, odaze huꞌuruḡa zauhe mode manahadu eꞌe habaꞌa ga neḡa mode iḡunoꞌi.\f + \fr 10:14 \ft Aꞌe ne azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe mazao sauꞌa haḡairotaꞌaꞌe ihozeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa. \f*
\v 15 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa kota madaḡano za mene mae ḡihiziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Sodoma zu Gomora azaḡa ufeta vitize aduga boro hidiꞌuma.”
\s1 Aduga Boro Hidiꞌuma
\r (Mareko 13:9-13; Luka 21:12-17)
\p 
\v 16 “Ḡianoꞌi. Butu ḡuniḡa boꞌaḡano mamoe tuḡuzeꞌeteꞌe teige, e za agire azaḡa boꞌaḡano tuḡuzeꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo mohe teige zamarone huhuzaḡa moꞌi,\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Zaramaꞌa maniḡa veize edaꞌerau avotiteꞌohe. \f* zu Tubugo niniḡa teige sauꞌa ago haḡaoꞌi.
\v 17 Rehano vaze ḡiazoꞌi. Ze zae oboze teadu kotao ohoziꞌuma ebu zeḡe nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano masiziꞌuma.
\v 18 Eḡe uꞌano, gavana azaḡa zu kini mazao zae tutuze onamiꞌuma, ebu zaeꞌa eḡe hari manoḡa zeḡe zu Iuda mene azaḡa zamao rae fureniꞌuma.
\v 19 Rehano zeꞌa kotao za oboze toꞌidene, nougenouge zae bare biriteꞌe ga nagini rae ḡoeriteꞌe moneo zamaze ago adudanoꞌi, mazaḡa eꞌe madaḡano zaeꞌa nagini rae ḡoeriteꞌe moneo ihoziꞌuma.
\v 20 Ḡoere aꞌe mene zae mazaonoꞌo, rehano Moze Viganiꞌa zae mazaonoꞌo ḡoeriꞌuma.
\p 
\v 21 Negoḡaniꞌa negoḡa revohanadu runeo tuḡuniꞌuma. Ebu moganiꞌa ubuga revohanadu runeo tuḡuniꞌuma. Ebu ubudezeꞌa vize moze agirozeadu runeo tuḡuziꞌuma.
\v 22 Eḡe uꞌano, vaze niduꞌa za heꞌeheꞌeziꞌuma. Rehano iniu edau gigaru onamo ḡonaga meiteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone hidiꞌuma.
\v 23 Ne ꞌahogano za sausauzoꞌidene, feranadu ne ꞌahoga onamoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaeꞌa Isaraela habaꞌa niduꞌa ꞌizema harame oname hauḡogano Vaze Ubuganiꞌa ariꞌuma.
\p 
\v 24 Tahiꞌaꞌe ane ihore vazeḡa mene vitinoga, ebu tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌa mene vitinoga.
\v 25 Tahiꞌaꞌe ane ihore vazeḡa teigeꞌohe rae reine, aꞌe idaḡa, ebu tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌa teigeꞌohe rae reine, aꞌe idaḡa. Zaꞌe eḡe teite ne tibano tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa heuḡa. Vazeꞌa eꞌe\f + \fr 10:25 \fqa ne vazeḡa boroꞌe \f* Belezebulo\f + \fr 10:25 \ft Niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Satani.\f* rae huhiro. Eꞌanoꞌo eḡe teite tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, zaꞌe ufeta sauꞌano huziꞌuma.”
\s1 Iniu Rihoniꞌuma?
\r (Luka 12:2-7)
\p 
\v 26 “Eꞌanoꞌo vazeꞌa sausauzoꞌidene, ago rihozoꞌi. Uꞌuru radiuꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma, ebu ogone ḡahineꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa zuni ederiꞌuma.
\v 27 Eḡeꞌa uzabo zamaḡano zae daꞌo ziꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe za mada agaḡano vaze niduꞌa zoꞌi. Ebu eḡeꞌa nagini sifu gumude ziꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ne binuḡa hitaganonoꞌo rae furenoꞌi.
\v 28 Vazeꞌe ahiri manogaꞌe idaḡa rehano, vine manogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo ze ago rihozoꞌi. Rehano Badiꞌa daꞌo rihonoꞌi, mazaḡa aniꞌe vine zu ahiriꞌe ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano ruizoga idaḡa.
\v 29 Tiburi niniḡa aheuꞌe hadi komeꞌa hina seroneꞌohe. Rehano Badiꞌa, zae Mamaꞌa mene uratine, zeḡe boꞌaḡano tiba zuni rahao mene uitiꞌuma.
\v 30 Badiꞌaꞌa zae zamare borofadu vadinize iguḡa niduꞌaꞌe nugu zuni edereꞌohe.
\v 31 Eꞌanoꞌo ago rihanoꞌi, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao Tiburi niniḡa ḡehaḡa ufeta vitizoga.
\p 
\v 32 Iniuꞌa vaze ubumao eḡe moneo edaune, eḡe zuni adureo Mamahe ubumao ane moneo edaꞌuma.
\v 33 Rehano iniuꞌa vaze ubumao eḡe oꞌohine, eḡe zuni adureo Mamahe ubumao ani oꞌoniꞌuma.”
\s1 Mene Uniho Manoḡa, Rehano Benisi
\r (Luka 12:51-53, 14:26-27)
\p 
\v 34 “Eḡeꞌa uniho manoḡa rahao ꞌada mae ariro rae ago zamaroꞌi. Eꞌe uniho manoḡa mene mae ariro, rehano benisi mae ariro.
\q1 
\v 35 Eꞌa ubugaꞌe moga teite agirotitoga,
\q2 avoḡaꞌe viꞌa teite agirotitoga,
\q1 roḡaeꞌe ani hadoga roḡaeḡa teite agirotitoga veize ariro.
\q2 
\v 36 Za agire azaḡaꞌe zae teite ne tibano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reꞌuma.\x + \xo 10:35-36 \xt Mika 7:6\x*
\p 
\v 37 Iniuꞌa moga ga viꞌa eḡe ufeta vitihe zamare borofine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma, ebu iniuꞌa ubuga ga aboḡa eḡe ufeta vitihe zamare borofine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.
\v 38 Iniuꞌa ane satauro odoheꞌenaꞌa eḡe ḡaruna mene hegotine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.
\v 39 Iniu ani ḡabone obone giganine, ani ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mene hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa ane ḡabone eḡe veize ahetine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.”
\s1 Naeḡa Hidiꞌuma
\r (Mareko 9:41)
\p 
\v 40 “Zae mae ḡihizeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌohe. Ebu eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 41 Iniuꞌa peroveta vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere rae fureneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae mae ḡihinine, aniꞌe peroveta vazeḡaniꞌa hiditeꞌe naeḡa hidiꞌuma. Iniuꞌa duduḡa vazeḡaꞌe vaze duduḡa rae mae ḡihinine, aniꞌe vaze duduḡaniꞌa hiditeꞌe naeḡa hidiꞌuma.
\v 42 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa nize komeꞌa azaḡa ꞌadi boꞌaḡano ꞌahogaꞌe eḡe tahiꞌa radu vu nahuga bioḡa tiba haune, aniꞌe aneꞌa meiteꞌe naeḡa mene hune dauniꞌuma.”
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare ihoze hauḡirotene, eꞌeanoꞌo iḡunadu ne uhiḡauhiḡano ihozifine zu haramifine onamiro.
\s1 Iesu zu Ioane Babatiso
\r (Luka 7:18-35)
\p 
\v 2 Ioane Babatisoꞌa ḡuꞌa neḡano radiunuteꞌe zamaḡano Kerisoꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe hariḡa igiro. ꞌOugadu aniꞌe Iesu ḡadinoga veize ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa Iesu vaḡe tuḡuziro.
\v 3 Ebu zeḡeꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡahe? Mene reine, eme vaze ꞌahoga guhiniꞌumahe?”
\p 
\v 4 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Bare onamadu zaeꞌa igiꞌeteꞌe zu horoneꞌeteꞌe Ioane ihonoꞌi.
\v 5 Ubuma kuru azaḡaꞌe ehamuꞌohe, oda sauꞌa azaḡaꞌe edau ragaveꞌohe, refera azaḡaꞌe manoreꞌohe, teḡaze uhuḡa azaḡaꞌe igiꞌohe, rune azaḡaꞌe bare ḡabodeꞌohe ebu zahara azaḡaniꞌa hari manoḡa igiꞌohe.
\v 6 Eḡe mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene modeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe matuꞌe rudauꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 7 Ioane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa iḡunirotene, Iesuꞌa Ioane moneo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ḡadahe ziro, “Za nagini horonoga veize haba bohaꞌa onamiro? Zavaraꞌa imi hudi naeninaeniꞌeteꞌe horonoga radu onamirohe?
\v 8 Mene reine, za nagini horonoga veize onamiro? Dabua manomano vidaroteꞌe vazeḡa horonoga veize onamirohe? Mene, dabua manomano vidaroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe kini neo radiuꞌohe.
\v 9 Tena nagini horonoga veize onamiro? Peroveta vazeḡahe? Oꞌe, eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, peroveta azaḡa vitizeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Ioane.
\v 10 Ioane moneo Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,
\q1 'Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa ḡae zamao vaze ꞌahoga ibite tuḡuniꞌuma.
\q2 Aniꞌe ḡae zamao ḡae ibi ruhibiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 11:10 \xt Malaki 3:1\x*
\m 
\v 11 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Ioaneꞌe rahao ꞌada fureraroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa vitizoga. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe ḡonaga vazeḡa zuni Ioane vitinoga.
\v 12 Ioane Babatisoꞌa haramiroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo onao izidi, Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe hariḡaꞌe riḡa harame onameꞌohe. Ebu vaze inaraḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano diuḡeꞌohe.
\v 13 Ioaneꞌa ꞌizema ariroteꞌe madaḡanoꞌe peroveta azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo rae fureniro.
\v 14 Zeḡeꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zaeꞌa mae ḡihinihi rae reine, zaꞌe ederiꞌuma, Ioaneꞌe ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡa, Elia.\x + \xo 11:14 \xt Malaki 4:5\x*
\v 15 Teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe faifaine egadu huga ederoꞌi.
\p 
\v 16 Izidi azaḡaꞌe naginio idaziꞌuma? Zeꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌaniꞌa ne hunio ehoradu araheꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Ze rovozadu none tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa mone tahiꞌaḡa mazao ꞌahige huauꞌohe,
\q1 
\v 17 'Eme muio suraꞌi hodeha, rehano za mene zavoneha.
\q1 Ebu eme rune habaꞌano niau ḡoinaheha, rehano za mene nianeha.'
\m 
\v 18 Ioane Babatisoꞌa aradu ogomu mene audo zu vaini vuḡa mene gagido. ꞌOugadu ze ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Ioaneꞌe vine sauꞌaḡeta.'
\v 19 U Vaze Ubugaꞌe aradu ogomu auꞌohe ebu vaini vuḡa gageꞌohe. ꞌOugeꞌetene, ze ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Ḡianoꞌi, aniꞌe ogomu fuꞌa zu vaini vuḡa fuꞌa. Ebu ani takesi azaḡa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa teite tiburuꞌohe.' Rehano iniu Badiꞌa zamarone huhuzaḡa hegotiroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌazamarone huhuzaḡaꞌe duduḡa rae fureneꞌohe.”
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌanonoꞌo Mene Ḡihureꞌeteꞌe Habaꞌa
\r (Luka 10:13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌe aneꞌa haḡai gigiꞌa ḡehaḡa haḡairoteꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa roziro, mazaḡa zeꞌe haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo mene ḡihuriro.
\v 21 Aneꞌa ziro, “Korasini azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Betesaida azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Eḡeꞌa zae mazao haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa gigiꞌaꞌe Turo zu Sidono\f + \fr 11:21 \ft Turo zu Sidonoꞌe Iuda mene habaꞌa.\f* azaḡa mazao haḡaifone, ze dabuaze ḡuꞌa vidanadu vega vadinizeo ase ḡuzuheꞌenaꞌa, haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihurifo.
\v 22 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa kota madaḡano zaꞌe Turo zu Sidono azaḡa ufeta vitize aduga boro hidiꞌuma.
\v 23 Kaperanauma azaḡa, zaꞌe adureo Badiꞌa haba tutuze itiꞌuma rae zamareꞌehe? Mene! Zaꞌe rune habaꞌano mae feuziꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa zae mazao haḡairoteꞌe haḡai gigiꞌaḡa Sodoma azaḡa mazao haḡaifone, zeꞌe haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuradu izidi ꞌize radiuꞌefo.
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa kota madaḡano zaꞌe Sodoma azaḡa ufeta vitize aduga boro hidiꞌuma.”
\s1 Eḡe Vaḡe Aradu Ahirize Ohonoꞌi
\r (Luka 10:21-22)
\p 
\v 25 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Mama, ḡaꞌe adure zu raha Zuhiꞌaḡa. E niguꞌeꞌohe, mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa vaze huhuzaḡa zu edeḡa boro azaḡa mazaoꞌe ḡoere huga ꞌahiguḡa ꞌuꞌuru tiro, rehano tahiꞌa komeꞌa teigeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaoꞌe rae fureniro.
\v 26 Mama, a hube, ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe ḡae ura.
\p 
\v 27 Eḡe Mamaꞌa ḡau niduꞌa eḡe iniro. Vazeni ꞌahoga Ubuga aḡuꞌa, rehano Moga ane daꞌo edeḡa. Ebu vazeni ꞌahoga Moga aḡuꞌa, rehano ane Ubuga daꞌo zu Ubuganiꞌa Moga moneo ihozoga veize ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo Moga edeḡa.
\v 28 Taoḡa zu aduga odoheꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, eḡe vaḡe aroꞌi, ꞌougine eḡeꞌa ahirize ohoniꞌuma.
\v 29 Eꞌe namiḡa zu roḡeḡa ꞌahine, eḡe ihore mae ḡihinadu\f + \fr 11:29 \fqa eḡe ḡau aduga odohadu \f* eḡe mazaonoꞌo edeḡa moꞌi. ꞌOugine, zamaze roḡeraꞌuma.
\v 30 Mazaḡa eḡe ihoreꞌe mene riḡa\f + \fr 11:30 \fqa eḡe ḡauꞌe ufiḡa \f* zu eꞌe hegotogaꞌe mene aduga.”
\c 12
\s1 Bana Madaḡa Zuhiꞌaḡa
\r (Mareko 2:23-28; Luka 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano, Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡano vuidi mebaḡa zamaḡano onamiro. Ebu ani tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe viniziroteꞌe uꞌano, vuidi maḡa ririꞌe madu ḡadahe aro.
\v 2 Farisea azaḡaniꞌa eꞌe horonadu Iesu niro, “Ḡianoꞌi! Ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Bana Madaḡa goroḡa varadeꞌohe.”
\v 3 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡa mene meꞌodirohe? Davida zu ani ḡatiniroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe vinize ruzirotene, Davidaꞌa nougiro?
\v 4 Aniꞌe Badiꞌa ne diuḡadu dibuꞌo azaḡaniꞌa daꞌo auꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌo ꞌuvahuḡa odoga aro, ebu ani ḡatiniroteꞌe azaḡa zuni aro. Aꞌe ze anogaꞌe mene idaḡa rae reiroteꞌe ḡauḡa.
\v 5 Ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Bana Madaḡano dibuꞌo azaḡaniꞌa kuru neḡano gaueꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene veꞌoḡa.' Za ꞌahi mene meꞌodirohe?
\v 6 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, kuru neḡa ufeta vitineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe.
\v 7 Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'E dibuꞌo mene urateꞌohe, rehano zaꞌe vaze vetuḡazoga urateꞌohe.'\x + \xo 12:7 \xt Hosea 6:6\x* Zaeꞌa ḡoere eꞌe huga ederifone, veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa azaḡa mazao veꞌoḡa rae mene zifo.
\v 8 Vaze Ubugaꞌe Bana Madaḡa Zuhiꞌaḡa.”
\s1 ꞌEvoꞌa Hoega Vazeḡa Fainiro
\r (Mareko 3:1-6; Luka 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌe habaꞌa modadu Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡa diuḡiro.
\v 10 Eꞌea naeḡa ꞌevoꞌa hoega vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Farisea azaḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa vaze eꞌe fainine, kotao ohonihi radu ḡadiniro, “Bana Madaḡano ugi azaḡa faizogaꞌe idaḡahe?”
\v 11 Aniꞌa ziro, “Zae boꞌaḡano iniu mamoe tibuhugaḡeta radu Bana Madaḡano mamoeḡaniꞌa iduo uite ovoine, iduonoꞌo mene mae vaḡiniꞌumahe?
\v 12 Vazeꞌe mamoe ufeta vitizoga zu ḡihiꞌaḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo Bana Madaḡano manoḡa haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe idaḡa.”
\v 13 Ebu aniꞌa ꞌevoꞌa hoega vazeḡa niro, “ꞌEvoꞌo ꞌeinoꞌi.” Aniꞌa ꞌevoꞌa ꞌeinirotene, naeḡa ꞌevoꞌa teige ꞌevoꞌaniꞌa manoriro.
\v 14 Rehano Farisea azaḡaniꞌa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡanonoꞌo buanadu nougenouge Iesu matiteꞌe moneo ḡoꞌaniro.
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Ohotiroteꞌe Tuḡure Vazeḡa
\p 
\v 15 Iesuꞌe Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ani matihi raꞌeteꞌe ederirotene, eꞌe habaꞌa mode vaḡiniro. Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani hegotiro ebu aneꞌa ugi azaḡa niduꞌa faiziro.
\v 16 Ebu ani riḡa ḡoreziro, “Eꞌe iniu rae vaze ago ihozoꞌi.”
\v 17 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 
\v 18 “ꞌAhiꞌe eḡeꞌa ohotiroteꞌe vazeḡa zu eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa.
\q2 Aniꞌe eḡe zamarone vazeḡa zu eḡe matuꞌoniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\q1 Eḡeꞌa Vinehe ane rana ohoniꞌuma,
\q2 aniꞌa habaꞌahabaꞌano Badiꞌa kota moneo haramiꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 19 Aniꞌe mene rotetiꞌuma ga mene hounaꞌiꞌuma,
\q2 aniꞌa ne hunio mene hounaꞌe ḡoeriꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 20 Roratiteꞌe veḡa mene mae vaḡineꞌeteꞌe
\q2 ga vidatiteꞌe ihureḡa mene hudi vineꞌeteꞌe teige,
\q1 aniꞌa zoreḡa azaḡa mene mae vaḡiziꞌuma, onamo ḡau veꞌoḡa niduꞌa mae vaḡinadu zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 21 Ebu Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡaniꞌa ani niḡano ḡabone hiditeꞌe madaḡa guhiniꞌuma.”\x + \xo 12:18-21 \xt Isaia 42:1-4\x*
\s1 Iesu ebu Belezebulo
\r (Mareko 3:20-30; Luka 11:14-23, 12:10)
\p 
\v 22 Ebu vaze nuꞌe vine sauꞌaniꞌa agatoharoteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga Iesu vaḡe tutune ariro. Aniꞌe ubumaḡa kuruḡa zu mumutafa. Ebu Iesuꞌa ani fainadu aniꞌe ḡoeriro zu ehamaro.
\v 23 Ebu vaze niduꞌa zaguzaganadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “ꞌAhiꞌe Davida mariga, Keriso gaogi!”
\p 
\v 24 Rehano Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ḡoereze igirotene, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Aniꞌe vine sauꞌa zuhiꞌaḡa, Belezebulo\f + \fr 12:24 \ft Ni ꞌahogaꞌe Satani. \f* inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌasauꞌa hegoze buzeꞌohe.”
\v 25 Rehano Iesuꞌa ze nouge rae zamareꞌeteꞌe ederadu ziro, “Haba tiba zamaḡano zeḡeꞌa rovotadu utitine, eꞌe habaꞌaꞌe aneꞌa bare ruiniꞌuma. Ebu ne boro ꞌahoga ga ne tiba zamaḡano zeḡeꞌa rovotadu utitine, ze mene edau gigaraꞌuma.
\v 26 Sataniꞌa Satani hegone bunine, ani aneꞌa bare rovotadu utitiꞌuma. ꞌOugine, aneꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe nougenouge edau gigaraꞌuma?
\v 27 Eḡeꞌa Belezebulo inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌa hegoze buzine, zae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe iniu inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌa hegoziꞌuma? Zae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare zaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae reꞌuma.
\v 28 Rehano eḡeꞌa vine sauꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa Viga hina hegoze buzeꞌohe. Aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa amahi zae zuhiꞌazirotaꞌaꞌe ihozeꞌohe.
\v 29 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa inara vazeḡa ꞌahoga mene batune tine, nougenouge ani ne diuḡadu ane tohe ḡonotu buau tauḡiꞌuma? Ani ibite inara vazeḡa batune teadu ane ne toheḡa ḡonotaꞌuma.\f + \fr 12:29 \ft Hugaꞌe, 'Iesuꞌe Satani ogoru teadu vine sauꞌa hegozeꞌohe.' \f*
\p 
\v 30 Iniu eḡe teite mene reine, aniꞌe eḡe agirohiꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Ebu iniu Badiꞌa veize eḡe teite vaze mene nuꞌozine, ani Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo vaze rovozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 31 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, vaze haḡai sauꞌa niduꞌa ebu Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa rae modiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa rae sausaunine, ani haḡai sauꞌaꞌe mene rae modiꞌuma.
\v 32 Iniuꞌa Vaze Ubuga agirohauꞌenaꞌa rae sausaunine, Badiꞌaꞌa ani haḡai sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma, rehano iniuꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa agirohauꞌenaꞌa rae sausaunine, ane haḡai sauꞌaꞌe izidi ebu zazore madaḡano zuni mene rae modiꞌuma.”
\s1 Ire ebu Ire Maḡa
\r (Luka 6:43-45)
\p 
\v 33 “Ire manoḡaꞌe maḡa manoḡa iniꞌuma zu ire sauꞌaꞌe maḡa sauꞌa iniꞌuma. Ireꞌe maḡa horonadu nagi ireḡa rae edereꞌohe.
\v 34 Zaꞌe Zarama mariga! Zaꞌe sauꞌa azaḡa uꞌano, ḡoere manoḡa ꞌahoga mene raꞌohe. Naginiꞌa ane zamao iriꞌave radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe hebeꞌanonoꞌo buauꞌohe.
\v 35 Vaze manoḡaꞌe ani zamao manoḡa nuꞌonadu manoḡa fureneꞌohe, ebu sauꞌa vazeḡaꞌe ane zamao sauꞌa nuꞌonadu sauꞌa fureneꞌohe.
\v 36 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa kota madaḡano vaze niduꞌa zeḡeꞌa bare ibite reiroteꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa moneo Badiꞌaꞌa kotaziꞌuma.
\v 37 Zaeꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa zaꞌe duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae kotaziꞌuma.”
\s1 Iona Haḡai Nu Badeḡa
\r (Mareko 8:11-12; Luka 11:29-32)
\p 
\v 38 Eꞌe madaḡano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa boꞌaḡano nuꞌa Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eme ḡaeꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe ḡianihi raꞌohe.”
\v 39 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Sauꞌa zu ubuma ḡezo azaḡaniꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa umideꞌohe. Rehano peroveta vazeḡa Iona mazao fureraroteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa daꞌo ihoziꞌuma.
\v 40 Ionaꞌe mada uḡidu zu ohere uḡidu ḡozone boro isio radiro. Eꞌe teige, Vaze Ubuganiꞌa zuni mada uḡidu zu ohere uḡidu raha zamaḡano radiꞌuma.
\v 41 Badiꞌa kota madaḡano Nineva azaḡaniꞌa izidi ega azaḡa teite iḡune edanadu izidi ega azaḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae roziꞌuma. Mazaḡa ibite madaḡano Nineva azaḡaꞌe Iona haramo abitadu haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihure ḡouriro. Izidi Iona vitinoga vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe, rehano ze ani ḡoere mene abitadu mene ḡihureꞌohe.
\v 42 Badiꞌa kota madaḡano Siba habaꞌa kini roḡaeḡaniꞌa izidi ega azaḡa teite iḡune edanadu izidi ega azaḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae roziꞌuma. Mazaḡa ibite madaḡano Siba habaꞌa kini roḡaeḡaniꞌa haba ḡonaga faḡa huneonoꞌo kini Solomona zamarone huhuzaḡa abitoga veize onamiro. U izidi Solomona vitinoga vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe, rehano ze ani ḡoere abitoga mene urateꞌohe.”
\s1 Vine Sauꞌaniꞌa Bariro
\r (Luka 11:24-26)
\p 
\v 43 “Vine sauꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo buauꞌetene, ahiꞌa ohonoga radu vu oꞌoꞌa habaꞌa vaḡe ragaveꞌohe. Rehano mene horonadu,
\v 44 ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'E eḡeꞌa vaḡinateꞌe vazeḡa vaḡe bare onamihi.' Ebu ani baradu vaze eꞌe horoneꞌetene, aniꞌe neḡa bohaꞌa, deheḡa hune zu idaidane touga heuḡa.
\v 45 Ebu vine sauꞌa eꞌeꞌa onamadu vine sauꞌa niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fare, ufeta hune sauꞌa zamaze areꞌohe ebu ze vaze eꞌe zamao diuḡe radiuꞌohe. ꞌOugadu vaze eꞌeꞌa ibiꞌa vitine ufeta sautuꞌohe. Eꞌeguḡaꞌe izidi ega sauꞌa mazao fureraꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesu Viꞌa zu Negoḡa
\r (Mareko 3:31-35; Luka 8:19-21)
\p 
\v 46 Iesuꞌa ꞌize vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ḡoreziroteꞌe zamaḡano viꞌa zu negoḡa duḡuruꞌa feuradu ani teite ḡoeroga veize enona edaro.
\v 47 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu niro, “Viꞌu zu negoḡo duḡuruꞌa ḡae teite ḡoerihi radu enona edau radiuꞌohe.”\f + \fr 12:47 \ft Fare mirihiroteꞌe nuꞌe vesi 47 oꞌoꞌa. \f*
\v 48 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Iniuꞌe eḡe nanu? Iniuꞌe eḡe nego duḡuru?”
\v 49 Ebu aniꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa surizeꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Eḡe nanu zu eḡe nego duḡuruꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe.
\v 50 Iniuꞌa eḡe Mama adureo ura haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe nego, eze ebu nanu.”
\c 13
\s1 Ezone Feune Ḡorauꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Mareko 4:1-9; Luka 8:4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa neonoꞌo iḡunadu duꞌura genaḡano ehoriro.
\v 2 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani babaḡano nuꞌorarotene, aniꞌe ḡasio tiradu ehoriro ebu vaze niduꞌaꞌe duꞌura genaḡano edaro.
\v 3 Ebu Iesuꞌa hari idaidaḡa hina ḡau ḡehaḡa ihoziro,
\p “Egoꞌi. Hihi vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa mebaḡano ezone ḡora onamiro.
\v 4 Ani ezone feune ḡorarotene, nuꞌe ibio rururaro ebu nini'a aradu au hauḡiro.
\v 5 Ezone nuꞌe hadi habaꞌano rururaro ebu rahaḡaꞌe mene baruḡa. Rahaḡaꞌe mene baruḡa radu ezoneꞌe ḡarihe ḡuhuriro.
\v 6 Rehano madaꞌa hiarotene, ane gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa ḡuhuḡa manadu roraro, mazaḡa taiga oꞌoꞌa.
\v 7 Ezone nuꞌe ve renogano rururaro. Ebu ve renoganiꞌa ḡuhure bororanadu ezone ḡuhuḡa simariniro.
\v 8 U ezone nuꞌe raha manoḡano rururanadu faine ḡuhure bororaro. ꞌOugadu nuꞌe huga ḡae 100, nuꞌe huga ḡae 60 ebu nuꞌe huga ḡae 30 hudaro.
\v 9 Teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe faifaine egadu huga ederoꞌi.” \fig Ezone feune ḡorauꞌohe|src="DN00470b.tif" size="col" ref="13:3-8"\fig*
\s1 Nagini veize Hari Idaidaḡa hina Ḡoeriroteꞌe moneo Ihoziro
\r (Mareko 4:10-12; Luka 8:9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa nougadu vaze mazaoꞌe hari idaidaḡa hina ḡoereꞌohe?”
\v 11 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo ꞌuꞌuru tirotaꞌaꞌe zae mazao fureniro, rehano vaze nunu mazaoꞌe mene fureniro.
\v 12 Faifaine zamare igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa edeḡa boro zenadu ze edeḡaꞌe ufeta bororaꞌuma. U mene faine zamare igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ze edeḡa zuni mae vaḡiniꞌuma.
\v 13 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa hari idaidaḡa hina ze ḡorezeꞌohe. Buka zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae reiro,
\q1 'Zeꞌe horoneꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene horoneꞌohe.
\q1 Zeꞌe igiꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene igiꞌohe ga mene edereꞌohe.'
\m 
\v 14 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaonoꞌo rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa zeḡe mazao hugano fureraro,
\q1 'Zeꞌe igiꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene ederiꞌuma.
\q1 Zeꞌe horoneꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene horoniꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 15 ꞌAhi duḡuru zamaꞌe tuḡa, teḡazeꞌe uhuḡa zu ubumazeꞌe kuruḡa.
\q1 Ze mene ꞌougifone, ubumaze hina horonifo, teḡaze hina igifo zu zamazeo ederifo.
\q2 Ebu ḡihuradu eḡeꞌa ze faizifo.'\x + \xo 13:14-15 \xt Isaia 6:9-10\x*
\m 
\v 16 Rehano zaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe, mazaḡa naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe ubumaze hina horoneꞌohe zu teḡaze hina igiꞌohe.
\v 17 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, peroveta azaḡa zu duduḡa azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa zaeꞌa izidi nagini horoneꞌeteꞌe horonihi rae reiro, rehano mene horoniro, ebu zaeꞌa izidi nagini igiꞌeteꞌe igihi rae reiro, rehano mene igiro.”
\s1 Hari Idaidaḡa Huga Ihoziro
\r (Mareko 4:13-20; Luka 8:11-15)
\p 
\v 18 “Ezone feune ḡorauꞌeteꞌe hariḡa idaidaḡa huga egoꞌi.
\v 19 Vaze nuꞌe ibio rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa igiꞌe rehano, huga mene edereꞌeteꞌe uꞌano Sataniꞌa aradu zamazeo ḡoraroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mae vaḡineꞌohe.
\v 20 Vaze nuꞌe hadi habaꞌano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌetene matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, zogone mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 21 Rehano zeꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe taiga oꞌoꞌa radu mada tahiḡa daꞌo fieꞌohe. Ebu Badiꞌa ḡoere mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, aduga zu sauꞌa hideꞌetene, zogone uiteꞌohe.
\v 22 Vaze nuꞌe ve renogano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌe rehano, ḡaboneze zamaḡano zamaze aduga borofeꞌohe zu haba toheḡa barebare mouga veize ufeta zamareꞌohe. ꞌUguḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere ꞌuadu zeꞌe mene iniꞌohe.
\v 23 U vaze nuꞌe raha manoḡano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌohe zu eꞌe huga edereꞌohe. Ebu ḡae 100, ḡae 60 ga ḡae 30 hudauꞌohe.”
\s1 Ve Hariḡa Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 24 Iesu'a hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ani mebao ezone manoḡa ḡoraroteꞌe heuḡa.
\v 25 Rehano vaze niduꞌa bazeꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ane agire vazeḡaniꞌa aradu vuidi boꞌaḡano ve ḡoraro ebu vaḡiniro.
\v 26 Vuidiꞌa ḡuhuradu maḡa haḡairotene ve zuni ḡuhuriro.
\v 27 Eꞌanoꞌo meba vazeḡa tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa aradu niro, ꞌZuhiꞌa, ḡaꞌa ḡae mebao vuidi ezone manoḡa ḡoraro. Rehano ve aꞌe noumanoꞌo?'
\v 28 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, 'Agire vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌougiro.' Tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ḡadiniro, 'Ḡaꞌe emeꞌa onamadu ve eꞌe ḡoroga urateꞌehe?'
\v 29 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, 'Mene, zaꞌa ve ḡurine vuidi zuni ḡuriꞌuma gaogi.
\v 30 Aheuꞌa tibano ḡuhuroga modoꞌi, onamo hiriviteꞌe madaḡa meꞌuma. Hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano eḡeꞌa hiriveꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zeadu zeꞌa ibite geno ve ḡoraꞌuma ebu tibano utadu hufiꞌuma. Hena vuidiꞌe tibano nuꞌonadu eḡe suabao zounoꞌi.'”
\s1 Kuava Maḡa zu Isiti Hariḡa Idaidaḡa
\r (Mareko 4:30-32; Luka 13:18-21)
\p 
\v 31 Aniꞌa hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe Kuava\f + \fr 13:31 \fqa fufu. \ft Fufuꞌe Papua New Guinea habaꞌanoꞌe mini, rehano Isaraela habaꞌanoꞌe ire. \f* maḡa tiba vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa madu mebaḡano ḡoraroteꞌe heuḡa.
\v 32 kuava maḡaꞌe maḡa niduꞌa boꞌaḡano komeꞌa fase, rehano ḡuhurine meba ḡauḡa niduꞌa boꞌaḡano ufeta bororanadu ire boro raꞌohe. Ebu hitagano nini'a rafiu aradu ezagano neze ogoruꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 33 Aniꞌa hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga bare ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazitaꞌaꞌe isiti heuḡa. Roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa isiti tahiḡa madu ꞌuvahu ḡehaḡa teite mirune tibunirotene, ꞌuvahu niduꞌaꞌe ubaruꞌohe.”
\s1 Hari Idaidaḡa hina Ḡoeriro
\r (Mareko 4:33-34)
\p 
\v 34 Iesuꞌa hari idaidaḡa hina ḡoere niduꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ziro. Aniꞌe hari idaidaḡa hina daꞌo vaze ḡoreziro.
\v 35 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡanonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 “Eḡeꞌa ḡorezine, hari idaidaḡa hina ziꞌuma.
\q2 Raha ꞌadi haḡairoteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo onao izidi ꞌuꞌuru tirotaꞌaꞌe eḡeꞌa rae fureniꞌuma.”\x + \xo 13:35 \xt Salamo 78:2\x*
\s1 Ve Hariḡa Idaidaḡa Huga Ihoziro
\p 
\v 36 Ebu aniꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa muhizadu ne zamaḡa diuḡiro. Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa hegote diuḡadu niro, “Mebao ḡoraroteꞌe ve hari idaidaḡa huga ihofoꞌi.”
\v 37 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, “Ezone manoḡa ḡoraroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Vaze Ubuga.
\v 38 Mebaꞌe raha ꞌadi. Ezone manoḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, u veꞌe Diabolo mone azaḡa.
\v 39 Ve ḡoraroteꞌe agire vazeḡaꞌe Diabolo. Hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡaꞌe mada ḡonaga, ebu hiriveꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tuḡure vigaviga.
\p 
\v 40 Mada ḡonagaꞌe ve niduꞌa nuꞌonadu ire rogao hufi haoneꞌeteꞌe teigiꞌuma.
\v 41 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa ane tuḡure vigaviga tuḡuziꞌuma, ebu zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaonoꞌo vaze ibi sauꞌano tutuzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa rovoze nuꞌoziꞌuma.
\v 42 Ebu zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe ire roga gigiꞌaḡano mae feuzadu ze eꞌea niaꞌuma zu ḡononeze atitiꞌuma.
\v 43 Ebu duduḡa azaḡaꞌe Mozeꞌa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano mada teige hiaꞌuma. Teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe faifaine egadu huga ederoꞌi.”
\s1 Uꞌuru Tiroteꞌe Ḡauḡa Naeḡa Boroboro Hariḡa Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 44 “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe mebao ꞌuꞌuru tiroteꞌe ḡauḡa naeḡa boroboro heuḡa. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa horonirotene bare uꞌuranadu matuꞌuḡeta ne onamiro. Ebu ane ḡau niduꞌa seronadu meba eꞌe hoitiro.
\p 
\v 45 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe hadi naeḡa boroboro vaḡeꞌeteꞌe sero vazeḡa heuḡa.
\v 46 Aniꞌa hadi naeḡa boro tiba horonirotene, ne onamadu ane ḡau niduꞌa seronadu eꞌe hoitiro.”
\s1 Reꞌeva Hariḡa Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 47 “Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe reꞌeva heuḡa. Davarao reꞌeva feunadu ḡozone nunu niduꞌa oḡaro.
\v 48 Reꞌevaꞌa iri'avirotene, vazeꞌa mae hesao rehaniro, ebu zeꞌa ehoradu ḡozone manoḡaꞌe inahe tunahuo mae ufiro, ebu ḡozone sauꞌaꞌe mae modiro.
\v 49 Mada ḡonaga zuni ꞌahiguḡa reꞌuma. Tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa aradu duduḡa azaḡa mazaonoꞌo sauꞌa azaḡa mae rovoziꞌuma.
\v 50 Ebu ze ire roga gigiꞌaḡano mae feuzadu eꞌea niaꞌuma zu ḡononeze atitiꞌuma.”
\s1 Iziga zu Amahiḡa
\p 
\v 51 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe eḡe ḡoere huga niduꞌa ederahe?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe.”
\v 52 Aniꞌa ziro, “Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo ederifone, zeꞌe ne vazeḡa heuḡa reifo. Ne vazeḡaꞌe ane godoḡo neḡanonoꞌo ḡau iziga zu ḡau amahiḡa mae buneꞌohe.”\f + \fr 13:52 \ft Ḡau amahiḡaꞌe ihore amahiḡano zu ḡau izigaꞌe ihore izigano idaniro. \f*
\p 
\v 53 Iesuꞌa hari idaidaḡa eꞌeguḡa hauḡirotene, eꞌeanoꞌo vaḡiniro.
\s1 Nazareta Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Hezahoharo
\r (Mareko 6:1-6; Luka 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 54 Iesuꞌa ane haba, Nazareta neḡa onamadu Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano ihoze ḡadahiro. Ze ani ḡoere egadu zaguzagaro ebu ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe noumanoꞌo zamarone huhuzaḡa zu haḡai gigiꞌa inaraḡa ꞌahi meiro?
\v 55 Vaze ꞌahiꞌe ne ogoruꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ubuga, oꞌehe? Ani viꞌaꞌe Maria, ani negoḡa duḡuruꞌe Iakobo, Iosefa, Simona zu Iuda.
\v 56 Ani ezeḡa niduꞌaꞌe ꞌaha emeḡe teite radiuꞌohe. Aniꞌa ꞌahiguḡa niduꞌa nouma meiro?”
\v 57 Ebu zeꞌa ani hezahoharo.
\p ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Peroveta vazeḡaꞌe haba nunu zamaḡano vazeꞌa gubaneꞌohe, rehano ane haba azaḡa zu ane ne azaḡaniꞌa daꞌo mene gubaneꞌohe.”
\v 58 Ebu aniꞌe eꞌe neḡano haḡai gigiꞌa ḡehaḡa mene haḡairo, mazaḡa zeꞌa ani mazao mene firo.
\c 14
\s1 Ioane Babatiso Maro
\r (Mareko 6:14-29; Luka 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Galilea habaꞌa kiniḡa, Herodaꞌa Iesu hariḡa igiro.
\v 2 Ebu aniꞌa ane gau azaḡa ziro, “Iesuꞌe Ioane Babatiso. Aneꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodeha. ꞌOugadu aneꞌa haḡai gigiꞌa inaraḡa hina gaueꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 3 Ibite Herodaꞌa negoḡa Filipi inuga, niḡa Herodia uꞌano, Ioane obone teadu ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoniro.
\v 4 Mazaḡa Ioaneꞌa Heroda mazao ꞌahige barebare niro, “Ḡaꞌa negoḡo inuga meirotaꞌaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\v 5 Herodaꞌa Ioane matihi reiro, rehano aniꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa rihoziro, mazaḡa zeꞌe Ioaneꞌe peroveta vazeḡa rae mae ḡihiniro.
\p 
\v 6 Herodaꞌa fureraroteꞌe madaḡa meirotene, Heroda aboḡaniꞌa vaze ḡehaḡa zamao zavonadu Heroda zama ufeta matuꞌoharo.
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo Herodaꞌa ani teite ꞌahige ḡoitoradu ane ḡoere rinede tiro, “Ḡaeꞌa nagini umidine zuni, eḡeꞌa ḡaniꞌuma.”
\v 8 Ebu aniꞌa viꞌa ḡoere egadu Heroda niro, “Ioane Babatiso vadiniꞌe siuva rana teadu izidi ꞌada enoꞌi.”
\v 9 ꞌOugadu Heroda zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro. Rehano ani aneꞌa huziroteꞌe azaḡa zamao ane ḡoere rinede tiro ꞌahine, ani uti azaḡa mazao aboḡaniꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa hanoꞌi rae ziro.
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌa uti azaḡa tuḡuzadu ḡuꞌa neḡano Ioane Babatiso ꞌunu variꞌe riꞌiro.
\v 11 Ebu vadigaꞌe siuva rana teadu odohe ariro ebu roḡae tahiꞌaḡa hanadu aneꞌa viꞌa haro.
\v 12 Ebu Ioane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa aradu ane ahiri meiro ebu guriro. Eꞌe enogano zeꞌe Iesu vaḡe onamadu Ioane rune hariḡa meꞌodoharo.
\s1 Vaze 5,000 Ḡubuziro
\r (Mareko 6:30-44; Luka 9:10-17; Ioane 6:1-14)
\p 
\v 13 Iesuꞌa Ioane hariḡa igirotene, eꞌe habaꞌa modadu ḡasi hina vaze oꞌoꞌa habaꞌa sifu ruhau onamiro. Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa eꞌe egadu nezeonoꞌo odao Iesu hegote onamiro.
\v 14 Iesuꞌa ḡasionoꞌo buanadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa horozirotene, vetuḡazeadu ugi azaḡa faiziro.
\p 
\v 15 Ḡoravararotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “ꞌAhiꞌe haba bohaꞌa ebu mada ꞌai zubureha. Eꞌanoꞌo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌadi tuḡuze vaḡizoꞌi. ꞌOugine, ze neḡaneḡa onamadu ogomuze hoitiꞌuma.”
\v 16 Rehano aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Ze mene onamiꞌuma, rehano zaeꞌa ogomu nu zenoꞌi.”
\v 17 Zeꞌa niro, “Eme mazaoꞌe ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo zu ḡozone aheu daꞌo.”
\v 18 Aniꞌa ziro, “Eḡe vaḡe mae aroꞌi.”
\v 19 Ebu aniꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ve rana ehoroga radu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro. Ebu aniꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo zu ḡozone aheu madu adure ite ḡianeꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi reiro. Ebu vahege tahitahadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziniro, ebu zeḡeꞌa vaze niduꞌa ḡahugo ziniro.
\v 20 ꞌOugadu zeḡe niduꞌa au ubararo, ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌaꞌe nuꞌonadu tunahu niduꞌa gaubanana aheu fare iriꞌavoniro.
\v 21 Eꞌea ogaroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano ohoze niduꞌa daꞌoꞌe 5,000, ebu roḡaeroḡae zu tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa ḡehaḡa zuni aro. \fig Vaze 5,000 ḡubuziro|src="WA03855b.tif" size="col" ref="14:15-21"\fig*
\s1 Vu rana Onamiro
\r (Mareko 6:45-52; Ioane 6:15-21)
\p 
\v 22 Iesuꞌa zogone ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa tuḡuze ḡasio tiriro ebu ziro, “Eḡe vitihe duꞌura moneafa fare onamoꞌi.” U Iesuꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa tuḡuziro.
\v 23 Iesuꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa tuḡuze hauḡiroteꞌe enogano, ane daꞌo maḡa komeꞌa itadu kuraro. Ḡoravararotene, eꞌea ane daꞌo radiunu.
\v 24 Eꞌe madaḡano ḡasizeꞌe hesaonoꞌo fararo ebu zavara boroboroꞌa ariro ꞌahine, saꞌu boroꞌa ragatadu ḡasize ḡihuḡihuniro.
\p 
\v 25 Iraranae reirotene, Iesuꞌa vu rana ragaveꞌenaꞌa, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe onamiro.
\v 26 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe Iesuꞌa vu rana edau ariroteꞌe horonirotene, rihau rudanadu huau ḡaniḡanaro, “Aꞌe vine!”
\v 27 Rehano Iesuꞌa zogone ziro, “Zamaze rinedoꞌi! ꞌAdiꞌe eḡe. Ago rihanoꞌi.”
\v 28 Peteroꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, a hube hune ḡa roꞌidene, eḡe zuni vu rana ḡae vaḡe amoga veize huhoꞌi.”
\v 29 Iesuꞌa niro, “Aroꞌi.” Ebu Peteroꞌa ḡasionoꞌo buanadu vu rana Iesu vaḡe edau onamiro.
\v 30 Rehano aniꞌa zavara boro horonirotene, rihanadu vu zamaḡa zubure ovoiro ebu ḡaniḡanaro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ḡabohoꞌi!”
\v 31 Iesuꞌa zogone ꞌevoꞌa ꞌeinadu ani abine ḡihiniro ebu niro, “Ḡaꞌe mene gigaru fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa! Nougadu ꞌadaꞌadeha?”
\p 
\v 32 Anianine ḡasio tirirotene, zavara ꞌai dauḡiro.
\v 33 Ebu ḡasi zamaḡa azaḡaꞌe Iesu mazao kuraro ebu niro, “Hube hune ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga.” \fig Iesuꞌa Petero ḡaboniro|src="cn01722B.tif" size="col" ref="14:28-31"\fig*
\s1 Ugi Azaḡa Faiziro
\r (Mareko 6:53-56)
\p 
\v 34 Zeꞌa duꞌura faradu Genesareta habaꞌano hebetiro.
\v 35 Haba eꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa ariroteꞌe ederadu ne uhiḡauhiḡa azaḡa niduꞌa veize ḡoere tuḡuriro. Ebu ze ugi azaḡa niduꞌa Iesu vaḡe tutuze ariro.
\v 36 Ebu ugi azaḡaꞌe Iesu dabuaḡa ꞌariḡa tahiḡano daꞌo obonoga veize Iesu uminiro. ꞌOugadu oboniroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ugizeꞌa manoriro.
\c 15
\s1 Vouḡaze Azaḡa Haḡai
\r (Mareko 7:1-23)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Farisea azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌa Ierusalemaonoꞌo Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro,
\v 2 “Ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ꞌizema oganogano ꞌevoreze mene vuzuꞌeꞌohe. Nougadu zeꞌa emeḡe vouḡa haḡai variꞌeꞌohe?”
\p 
\v 3 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌe nougadu vouḡaze haḡai hegotoga veize Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe variꞌeꞌohe?
\v 4 Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Viꞌu mogo gubazoꞌi,'\x + \xo 15:4 \xt Vaḡiniro 20:12; Goro 5:16\x* ebu 'Iniuꞌa ane viꞌa moga rae sausauzine, ani mau runiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 15:4 \xt Vaḡiniro 21:17; Dibuꞌo 20:9\x*
\v 5 Rehano zaꞌe vize moze mazao ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Fase, e zae danazoga mene idaḡa, mazaḡa eḡeꞌa danaziteꞌe ḡauḡa ꞌahiꞌe Badiꞌa hatiteꞌe ḡahunoneḡa raha.' Zaeꞌa ꞌouge radu,
\v 6 vize moze mene gubazoga zuni idaḡa raꞌohe. Zaeꞌa vouḡaze haḡai hegotoga veize, Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa mae vaḡineꞌohe.
\v 7 Zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa zae moneo Badiꞌa ḡoere rae furenirotaꞌaꞌe duduḡa,
\q1 
\v 8 'Vaze ꞌahiguḡaꞌe hebeze hina eḡe gubaheꞌohe,
\q2 rehano zamazeꞌe eḡe mazaonoꞌo faḡa hune.
\q1 
\v 9 Zeḡeꞌa Badiꞌa mazao kurauꞌetaꞌaꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa.
\q2 Zeꞌe vazeꞌa tiroteꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌohe.'”\x + \xo 15:8-9 \xt Isaia 29:13\x*
\p 
\v 10 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ane vaḡe huze onamadu ziro, “Eḡe ḡoere egadu huga ederoꞌi.
\v 11 Hebeo diuḡeꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe vaze mene toratoraneꞌohe. Rehano hebeonoꞌo buauꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaniꞌa vaze toratoraneꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 12 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe aradu niro, “Ḡa Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ḡae ḡoere egadu maḡuneꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡahe?”
\v 13 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe Mama adureo radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa mene ḡoraroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe taiganonoꞌo ḡuri modiꞌuma.
\v 14 Ze mode tauḡoꞌi. Zeꞌe ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa rehano, ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa ibitoziꞌohe. Ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡaniꞌa ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa ibitohaune, anianine hoꞌona uite ovoiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 15 Peteroꞌa niro, “Hari idaidaḡa eꞌe huga ihofoꞌi.”
\v 16 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe ꞌize mene edeḡahe?
\v 17 Ogomuꞌe vaze hebeonoꞌo diuḡadu isi zamaḡa ovoeꞌohe ebu vesuꞌu ahirionoꞌo buauꞌohe. Za eꞌe aḡuꞌahe?
\v 18 Rehano hebeonoꞌo buauꞌetaꞌaꞌe zamaonoꞌo buanadu vaze toratoraneꞌohe.
\v 19 Vaze zamaonoꞌo buauꞌetaꞌaꞌe zamarone sauꞌa. Aꞌe gorugoru, ubuma ḡezo, daro fuꞌa, ḡonore, vaze moneo ḡurireꞌeteꞌe zu vaze rae sausauzeꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 20 Eꞌeguḡaniꞌa vaze toratoraneꞌohe. Rehano ꞌevore mene vuzuꞌadu ogomu auꞌeteꞌeꞌa vaze mene toraneꞌohe.”
\s1 Kanana Roḡaeḡaniꞌa Iesu mazao Firo
\r (Mareko 7:24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Iesuꞌa Galilea habaꞌa modadu Turo zu Sidono habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 22 Ebu eꞌe habaꞌano Kanana roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ani vaḡe aradu ḡihau huniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Davida mariga, eḡe vetuḡahoꞌi! Vine sauꞌaniꞌa eḡe aboe ragano radu ani ufeta aduga hideꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 23 Rehano Iesuꞌa ḡoere ꞌahoga mene naenaeniro. Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa aradu uminiro, “Aniꞌa eme hegoteꞌenaꞌa, barebare huau ḡunuḡunufeꞌohe. Ani tuḡune vaḡinoꞌi.”
\v 24 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Isaraela azaḡa boꞌaḡano dauḡiroteꞌe mamoeḡa veize daꞌo eḡe tuḡuhiro.”
\p 
\v 25 Rehano roḡaeḡaniꞌa aradu ani zamao ḡuḡuriro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, danahoꞌi.”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Tahiꞌatahiꞌa ogomu madu ḡuni hanogaꞌe mene duduḡa.”
\v 27 Roḡaeḡaniꞌa niro, “A hube, Zuhiꞌa Boro. Rehano ḡuni zuni ane zuhiꞌa fataḡanonoꞌo buauꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa mumuḡa auꞌohe.”
\v 28 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Roḡae, ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe boro hune! Ḡaeꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe hidiꞌuma.” Eꞌe madaḡano ani aboḡaniꞌa manoriro.
\s1 Vaze Ḡehaḡa Faiziro
\p 
\v 29 Iesuꞌa haba eꞌe modadu Galilea duꞌuraḡa onamiro. Ebu maḡa komeꞌa itadu eꞌea ehoriro.
\v 30 ꞌOugadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa mene edauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa, oda sauꞌa azaḡa, mumutafa azaḡa zu ugi azaḡa nunu ḡehaḡa tutuze ane vaḡe ariro. Ebu zeꞌe ane oda babaḡano ugi azaḡa bazuze teadu aneꞌa faiziro.
\v 31 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe mumutafa azaḡaniꞌa ḡoereꞌeteꞌe, oda sauꞌa azaḡaniꞌa manorateꞌe, mene edauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ragaveꞌeteꞌe zu ubuma kuruḡa azaḡaniꞌa ehamuꞌeteꞌe horozirotene, zaguzagaro ebu Isaraela azaḡa Badiꞌaḡa niguniro.
\s1 Vaze 4,000 Ḡubuziro
\r (Mareko 8:1-10)
\p 
\v 32 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ane uhiḡano huze onamadu ziro, “Eꞌe ꞌahi duḡuru vetuḡaziꞌohe, mazaḡa ze ꞌaha mada uḡidu eḡe teite radiuꞌohe zu ogomuze oꞌoꞌa. Eꞌe ze vinini tare nezeo tuḡuzoga mene urateꞌohe, mazaḡa ze ibio higau bauriꞌuma gaogi.”
\v 33 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa niro, “Haba bohaꞌano ꞌahi eme nouma ogomu ḡehaḡa horonadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌahi ḡubuziꞌuma?”
\v 34 Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Za mazao ꞌuvahu odogaꞌe nugu?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “ꞌUvahu odogaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare zu ḡozone komeꞌaꞌe tahiḡa.”
\p 
\v 35 Ebu aniꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa rahao ehoroga radu ziro.
\v 36 Ebu hena ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo aheu fare zu ḡozone nu madu Badiꞌa mazao kuraro. Ebu vahegadu tahiꞌaḡa ziniro ebu zeꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ḡahugiro.
\v 37 ꞌOugadu zeḡe niduꞌa au idararo. Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌa mae ofadu tunahu fuꞌo aheu fare iri'avoniro.
\v 38 Ogaroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano ohoze daꞌo niduꞌaꞌe 4,000. Roḡaeroḡae zu tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌaꞌe mene meꞌodiro.
\v 39 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa tuḡuze vaḡiziroteꞌe ḡarugano ḡasio tiradu Magadana habaꞌa onamiro.
\c 16
\s1 Haḡai Nu Badeḡa Uratiro
\r (Mareko 8:11-13; Luka 12:54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Farisea zu Sadukea azaḡaniꞌa Iesu tuhune nuroga veize ani vaḡe aradu niro, “Ḡaeꞌa Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa hina haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe ihofoꞌi.”
\v 2 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Za ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Ḡorava madaꞌa kanaru zuburine, ohoḡore mada manoḡa reꞌuma,'
\v 3 ebu 'Oherebau adureꞌa ḡutanoga horonine, iruguꞌa ruꞌaꞌuma.' Zaꞌe adure iraḡa horonadu naginiꞌa fureratitaꞌaꞌe edereꞌohe. Rehano izidi madaḡano naginiꞌa fureru radiuꞌeteꞌe moneo hugaꞌe aḡuꞌa.
\v 4 Sauꞌa zu ubuma ḡezo azaḡaꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa vaḡeꞌohe. Rehano Iona mazao fureraroteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa daꞌo ihoziꞌuma.” Ebu aneꞌa ze muhize onamiro.
\s1 Farisea zu Sadukea Azaḡa Isiti
\r (Mareko 8:14-21)
\p 
\v 5 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe duꞌura moneafa farirotene ꞌuvahu odoga mae odohoga aḡutaro.
\v 6 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Farisea zu Sadukea azaḡa ḡiazoꞌi, mazaḡa zeꞌe isiti heuḡa.”
\p 
\v 7 ꞌOugadu ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Emeꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga mene mae aradu ani ꞌouge raꞌohe.”
\v 8 Iesuꞌa ze nagini reirotaꞌaꞌe ederadu ziro, “Zaꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe komeꞌa! Nougadu zae mazao ꞌuvahu odoga oꞌoꞌa radu ḡadimutiteꞌohe?
\v 9 Zaꞌe ꞌize mene edeḡahe? Eḡeꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo hina vaze 5,000 ḡubuzirotaꞌaꞌe mene zamareꞌehe? Ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌaꞌe tunahu nugu iriꞌavoniro?
\v 10 Ebu ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo aheu fare hina vaze 4,000 ḡubuzirotaꞌaꞌe mene zamareꞌehe? Ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌaꞌe tunahu nugu iriꞌavoniro?
\v 11 Eḡeꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga moneo mene zeataꞌaꞌe nougadu zaꞌe mene edereꞌohe? Farisea zu Sadukea azaḡa isiti ḡianoꞌi!”
\p 
\v 12 ꞌOuge reirotene, zeꞌe ederiro, aniꞌe ꞌuvahu odoga isitiḡa moneo mene ziro, rehano Farisea zu Sadukea azaḡa ihoreḡa ḡianoga veize ziro.
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesuꞌe Keriso rae Reiro
\r (Mareko 8:27-30; Luka 9:18-21)
\p 
\v 13 Iesuꞌa Kaisarea Filipo habaꞌa onamirotene, ani ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ḡadiziro, “Vazeꞌa Vaze Ubugaꞌe iniu rae raꞌohe?”
\v 14 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Nuꞌe Ioane babatiso, nuꞌe Elia ebu nuꞌe Ieremia ga amahi peroveta vazeḡa ꞌahoga rae raꞌohe.”
\v 15 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “U zaꞌe eꞌe iniu rae raꞌohe?”
\v 16 Simona Peteroꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡaꞌe Keriso, ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga.”
\v 17 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Iona ubuga Simona, matuꞌoꞌi, mazaḡa vazeꞌa ḡae mazao ꞌadi mene ihoꞌeha, rehano adureo eḡe Mamaꞌa ihoꞌeha.
\v 18 Eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe, ḡaꞌe Petero, hugaꞌe vatava. Eḡeꞌa vatava eꞌe rana ekalesia ohoziꞌuma ebu rune gigiꞌaniꞌa ze mene raharahaziꞌuma.
\v 19 E Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano diuḡeꞌeteꞌe ibihetaḡa kiḡa ḡaniꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaꞌe nagini rahao gararine, Badiꞌaꞌa adureo zuni garariꞌuma, ebu ḡaꞌa nagini rahao ahetine, Badiꞌaꞌa adureo zuni ahetiꞌuma.”
\v 20 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡoere riḡa ziro, “Eꞌe Keriso rae vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi.”
\s1 Iesu Rune moneo Ihoziro
\r (Mareko 8:31-9:1; Luka 9:22-27)
\p 
\v 21 Eꞌe madaḡano onamo, Iesuꞌa ane rune moneo ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ḡadahe ihoziro, “Eḡeꞌa Ierusalema oname huniꞌuma, ebu vaze boroboro, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaonoꞌo aduga ḡehaḡa hidiꞌuma. Zeꞌa uḡuhiꞌuma, rehano eḡeꞌa mada uḡiduḡano bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”
\v 22 Ebu Peteroꞌa Iesu ane genaḡano zamahu onamadu ḡadahe roniro, “Mene, Zuhiꞌa Boro! ꞌUguḡaniꞌa ḡae mazao mene hune fureraꞌuma!”
\v 23 Rehano Iesuꞌa tehadu Petero niro, “Satani, eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi! Ḡaꞌe hadi feꞌoḡa teige eḡeꞌa uitoga veize ḡoereꞌohe, mazaḡa zamaroneḡoꞌe mene Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo, rehano vaze mazaonoꞌo areha.”
\p 
\v 24 Ebu hena Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Iniuꞌa eḡe ḡaruna hegotihi rae roꞌidene, ani ura niduꞌa modadu ane satauro odoheꞌenaꞌa, eḡe hegotoꞌi.
\v 25 Mazaḡa iniu ane ḡabone obone giganine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mene hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniu ane ḡabone eḡe veize ahetine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.
\v 26 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haba niduꞌa meiroteꞌe ḡarugano ḡaboneḡa daunine, nagi manoḡa hidiꞌuma? Ḡau ꞌahoga hanadu ḡaboneḡa bare mouga idaḡahe?
\v 27 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa Moga agaḡa zamaḡano tuḡure viga niduꞌa teite ariꞌuma, ebu hena vazeꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe idunaḡano aneane naeḡa ziniꞌuma.
\v 28 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, izidi ꞌada edau radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze nuꞌe mene rudaꞌuma, onamo Vaze Ubuganiꞌa aradu zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma.”
\c 17
\s1 Iesu Iraḡaniꞌa Nufiro
\r (Mareko 9:2-13; Luka 9:28-36)
\p 
\v 1 Mada fuꞌo tiba fare ḡarugano Iesuꞌa Petero, Iakobo zu Iakobo negoḡa Ioane zamazadu zeḡe daꞌo maḡa boro itiro.
\v 2 Eꞌea ani iraḡaniꞌa zeḡe ubumao nufiro. Iraḡaniꞌa mada teige agararo ebu dabuaḡaniꞌa agaḡa teige ꞌuraro.
\v 3 Eꞌe madaḡano zeḡe zamao Mose zu Eliaꞌa fureranadu Iesu teite ḡoeriro.
\v 4 Ebu Peteroꞌa Iesu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme ꞌaha radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe manoḡa. Ḡa uratine e taruha uḡidu ogoraꞌuma. Tibaꞌe ḡae veize, tibaꞌe Mose veize ebu tibaꞌe Elia veize ogoraꞌuma.”
\v 5 Aniꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, ḡoze vazavazahoganiꞌa ovadu ze ogoziro. Ebu ḡozeonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa ziro, “ꞌAhiꞌe eḡe zamarone Ubude. Ani uꞌano, e matuꞌe rudauꞌohe. Zaꞌe ani ḡoere egohanoꞌi.”
\v 6 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ago eꞌe igirotene, rihau rudanadu rahao ḡuḡuriro.
\v 7 Rehano Iesuꞌa aradu oboziro ebu ziro, “Iḡunoꞌi. Ago rihanoꞌi.”
\v 8 Zeḡeꞌa dude ehamarotene, vaze ꞌahoga mene horoniro, rehano Iesu daꞌo horoniro. \fig Iesu iraḡaniꞌa nufiro|src="GR-lllb22n.tif" size="col" ref="17:1-9"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Ze maḡanonoꞌo ovairoteꞌea, Iesuꞌa riḡa ziro, “Zaeꞌa horonataꞌaꞌe vaze ꞌahoga ago noꞌi, onamo Vaze Ubuganiꞌa runeonoꞌo bare ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma.”
\v 10 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ḡadiniro, “Nougadu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa, ꞌKerisoꞌa ꞌizema arogano Eliaꞌa ibite ariꞌuma,' rae raꞌohe?”
\v 11 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Hube hune Eliaꞌa aradu ḡau niduꞌa ruhibiꞌuma.
\v 12 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Elia ꞌai amahi ariro. Rehano vazeꞌa ani mene ederadu ani mazao zeḡeꞌa uratiroteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡairo. Eꞌe teige, Vaze Ubuga zuni zeḡe mazaonoꞌo aduga hidiꞌuma.”
\v 13 ꞌOuge reirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe Iesuꞌa Ioane Babatisoꞌe Elia rae reirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.
\s1 Tahiꞌa Komeꞌa Vine Sauꞌaḡeta Manoniro
\r (Mareko 9:14-29; Luka 9:37-43)
\p 
\v 14 Iesu zu ane tahiꞌa uḡiduꞌa maḡanonoꞌo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa vaḡe ovairotene, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu ane zamao obenaḡa hina tuḡiro ebu niro,
\v 15 “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eḡe ubude vetuḡanoꞌi. Aniꞌe ketoketeꞌohe ebu ahiꞌaꞌe gigiꞌa boro maꞌohe. Aniꞌe ḡae ḡehaḡa ire rogao ga vuo higauꞌohe.
\v 16 Eꞌa ani tutune ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe areha, rehano zeꞌe ani manonoga mene idaraneha.”
\v 17 Iesuꞌa eꞌea radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ziro, “Zaꞌe Badiꞌa mazao mene fiꞌeꞌeteꞌe zu veꞌoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa! E zae teite noꞌe faḡa radiꞌuma? E noꞌe faḡa zae mazao zamahe obone tiꞌuma? Tahiꞌa komeꞌa eꞌe eḡe vaḡe tutune aroꞌi.”
\v 18 Ebu Iesuꞌa vine sauꞌa ronadu vine sauꞌaniꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌa eꞌe mazaonoꞌo buaro. ꞌOugadu tahiꞌa komeꞌa eꞌeꞌa zogone manoriro.
\p 
\v 19 Ebu ani tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa zeḡe daꞌo Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Emeꞌa nougadu vine sauꞌa hegone bunoga mene idaraneha?”
\v 20 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, “Mazaḡa zaeꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe tahiḡa fase. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe fufu maḡa komeꞌa tiba heuḡa radu maḡa ꞌahi mazao ninaꞌa, 'ꞌAdanoꞌo vaḡinadu ꞌomo onamoꞌi,' rae reine, maḡa eꞌeꞌa ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma. Zaeꞌa eḡe mazao fine, ḡau niduꞌa haḡaogaꞌe idaḡa.”\f + \fr 17:20 \fv 21 \fqa Kuraune zu ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡine, vine sauꞌa ꞌahiguḡa hegone buniꞌuma. \f*
\s1 Iesu Rune zu Bare Ḡaboditeꞌe moneo Ziro
\r (Mareko 9:30-32; Luka 9:43b-45)
\p 
\v 22 Zeꞌa Galilea habaꞌano nuꞌorarotene, Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vaze Ubugaꞌe agireḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniꞌuma.
\v 23 Zeꞌa ani maꞌuma ebu aniꞌa mada uḡiduḡano bare ḡabodiꞌuma.” ꞌOugadu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe zamaze are rudaro.
\s1 Kuru Neḡa Takesiḡa
\p 
\v 24 Zeꞌa Kaperanaumao feurirotene, kuru neḡa takesi azaḡaniꞌa Petero vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Zae ihore vazeḡaꞌe kuru neḡa takesi\f + \fr 17:24 \fqa derakema aheu. \ft Derakema tibaꞌe mada tiba gau naeḡa heuḡa. \f* mene hauꞌehe?”
\v 25 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Mene, aniꞌe takesiḡa hauꞌohe.”
\p Peteroꞌa ne diuḡirotene, Iesuꞌa ibite ḡadiniro, “Petero,\f + \fr 17:25 \fqa Simona\f* ḡa nouge rae zamareꞌohe? Haba kiniḡaꞌe iniu mazao takesi ufeꞌohe, ani haba azaḡa mazao ga avoꞌa azaḡa mazao?”
\v 26 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Avoꞌa azaḡa mazao ufeꞌohe.” Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Oꞌe, ani haba azaḡaꞌe takesi mene hauꞌohe.
\v 27 Rehano emeꞌa takesi azaḡa mene maḡunozinifine takesi ziniꞌuma. Ḡaꞌe duꞌura ovoadu kimai feunoꞌi. Ebu ibite manateꞌe ḡozoneḡa hebeꞌa mae nahanine, siliva hadiḡa tiba\f + \fr 17:27 \fqa sitatera tiba. \ft Aꞌe derakema ḡazaḡa heuḡa. \f* horoniꞌuma. Eꞌe madu emenane veize zenoꞌi.”
\c 18
\s1 Iniuꞌe Ḡihiꞌa Hune
\r (Mareko 9:33-37; Luka 9:46-48)
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano iniuꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune?”
\v 2 Iesuꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahoga hunadu zeḡe boꞌaḡano mae ohoniro,
\v 3 ebu ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaeꞌa ḡihuradu tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahi mene teigine, Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano mene hune diuḡiꞌuma.
\v 4 Iniu tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌadi teige aneꞌa bare ovoeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ḡihiꞌa hune rae raꞌohe.
\v 5 Ebu iniu eḡe niḡano tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahiguḡa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌohe.”
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌa Haḡaihi raꞌeteꞌe Zamaroneḡa
\r (Mareko 9:42-48; Luka 17:1-2)
\p 
\v 6 “Eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa komeꞌakomeꞌa ꞌahiguḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga zuni haḡai sauꞌano tutune veꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe hadi horeḡa ꞌunuḡano autadu davara guniḡano mae feunineꞌe ufeta manoḡa.
\v 7 Vaze ibi sauꞌano tutuzeꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa uꞌano, raha ꞌadi azaḡaniꞌa aduga boro hidiꞌuma. Eꞌeguḡaꞌe mada niduꞌa fureruꞌohe rehano, vaze haḡai sauꞌano tutuzeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma.
\v 8 ꞌEvoꞌo naeḡa ga odaḡo naeḡaniꞌa haḡai sauꞌano tutuꞌe veꞌoꞌoꞌidene, variꞌe modoꞌi. ꞌEvo'o tiba ga odaḡo tiba hina ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidogaꞌe ufeta manoḡa. Aꞌe ꞌevoꞌo aheu ga odaḡo aheu hina ire roga mene hauḡeꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano mae feuꞌoga vitineꞌohe.
\v 9 Ubumaḡo naeḡaniꞌa haḡai sauꞌano tutuꞌe veꞌoꞌoꞌidene, ḡude modoꞌi. Ubumaḡo tiba hina ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidogaꞌe ufeta manoḡa. Aꞌe ubumaḡo aheu hina ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuꞌoga vitineꞌohe.”
\s1 Mamoeꞌa Dauḡiroteꞌe Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Luka 15:3-7)
\p 
\v 10 “Nize komeꞌa ꞌahiguḡa boꞌaḡano tiba zuni mene ovoe ḡianoga veize tohutohoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zeḡe taufeꞌeteꞌe tuḡure vigavigaꞌe eḡe Mama adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe teite iḡaiḡa radiuꞌohe.\f + \fr 18:10 \fv 11 \fqa Vaze Ubugaꞌe dauḡiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡabozoga veize ariro. \f*
\p 
\v 12 Zaꞌe nouge rae zamareꞌohe? Vaze ꞌahoga mazao mamoeḡaꞌe 100. Rehano tibaniꞌa dauḡine, ani nougiꞌuma? Aniꞌe mamoeḡa 99 maḡa habaꞌano modadu mamoeḡa dauḡoga vaḡe ragaviꞌuma.
\v 13 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, aneꞌa mamoe dauḡoga horone meine, mamoe tiba eꞌe uꞌano matuꞌe rudaꞌuma. Aniꞌe mamoe 99 mene dauḡoḡa ufeta vitize matuꞌiꞌuma.
\v 14 Eꞌe teige, nize komeꞌa ꞌahiguḡa boꞌaḡano tiba zuni dauḡogaꞌe zae Moze adureo radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa mene urateꞌohe.” \fig Mamoe dauḡoga|src="41_Mat18:12-13_LostSheep" size="col" ref="18:12-14"\fig*
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌa Haḡaeꞌeteꞌe Nabuga Duduneꞌeteꞌe Ibiḡa
\r (Luka 17:3)
\p 
\v 15 “Ekalesia boꞌaḡano negoḡo ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡae mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, ane vaḡe onamadu ḡanine daꞌo radiuꞌenaꞌa haḡaiḡa sauꞌa ihonoꞌi. Aniꞌa egoḡanadu ḡihurine, ḡaꞌe nabugota bare tiburaneha.
\v 16 U aniꞌa mene egoḡanoꞌidene, vaze tiba ga aheu zamazadu ane vaḡe bare onamoꞌi, mazaḡa ḡanine nagini raꞌetaꞌaꞌe vaze aheu ga uḡiduꞌa zuni ederiꞌuma.
\v 17 Aniꞌa zeḡe ḡoere mene egozenoꞌidene, ekalesia zamaḡano rae furenoꞌi. Aniꞌa ekalesia zuni mene egozenoꞌidene, aniꞌe Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa vazeḡa ga takesi vazeḡa sauꞌa heuḡa rae zamaroꞌi.
\p 
\v 18 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaeꞌa nagini rahao gararine, Badiꞌaꞌa adureo zuni garariꞌuma, ebu zaeꞌa nagini rahao ahetine, Badiꞌaꞌa adureo zuni ahetiꞌuma.
\v 19 Eḡeꞌa bare hube hune ziꞌohe, rahao ꞌada zae boꞌaḡano vaze aheuꞌa zamaze tibano nagini umidine, eḡe Mama adureo radiuꞌeteꞌeꞌa zae umido haḡaoziniꞌuma.
\v 20 Mazaḡa eḡe niḡano aheu ga uḡiduꞌa nuꞌoraune, eḡeꞌa zeḡe boꞌaḡano radiuꞌohe.”
\s1 Vaze Haḡai Sauꞌa mene Aḡutu Modiroteꞌe Tuḡure Vazeḡa Hari Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 21 Ebu Peteroꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eḡe ekalesia negoḡaniꞌa eḡe mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaine, ḡae nugu eḡeꞌa haḡaiḡa sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma? Ḡae fuꞌo aheu fare ga?”
\v 22 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe, mene ḡae fuꞌo aheu fare daꞌo, rehano barebare\f + \fr 18:22 \fqa ḡae 470 zuni \f* rae modoꞌi.
\p 
\v 23 Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe hari idaidaḡa ꞌahi heuḡa. Kini ꞌahoganiꞌa ane mazaonoꞌo hadi meiroteꞌe tuḡure azaḡa huzadu ani hadi bare meihi rae reiro.
\v 24 ꞌOugirotene, hadi borofe\f + \fr 18:24 \fqa talanti 10,000. \ft Aꞌe muri 16 gau naeḡa heuḡa. \f* meiroteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ani vaḡe tutune ariro.
\v 25 Aniꞌe hadi baronoga mene idararo ꞌahine, kiniꞌa riḡa ḡoreniro, 'Ḡa ḡae bare, inugo, ubugo zu ḡae mazao ḡau niduꞌa seronadu eḡe hadi baronoꞌi!'
\v 26 ꞌOugadu tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa ani zamao obenaḡa hina tuḡadu uminiro, 'Geno mada nu enoꞌi, ꞌougine e hadiḡo niduꞌa baroniꞌuma.'
\v 27 ꞌOuge reirotene, zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa vetuḡaniro ebu hadiḡa baronogaꞌe ahiḡa radu ani tuḡuniro.
\p 
\v 28 Eꞌe ḡarugano tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa ani teite tiburu gaueꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡa ꞌahoga hidiro. Tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ani mazaonoꞌo hadi nu\f + \fr 18:28 \fqa denari 100. \ft Aꞌe mada 100 gau naeḡa heuḡa. \f* meiroteꞌe uꞌano, aneꞌa ani matanadu oḡorabiḡa harinoharo ebu riḡa niro, 'Eḡe hadi baronoꞌi!'
\v 29 ꞌOugirotene, ane vaze, tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa obenaḡa hina tuḡadu uminiro, 'Geno mada nu enoꞌi, ꞌougine hadiḡo baroniꞌuma.'
\v 30 Rehano aniꞌe ane vaze hezahoharo ebu onamadu ḡuꞌa neḡano mae ohoniro, onamo aniꞌa hadi eꞌe baroniꞌuma.
\v 31 Tuḡure azaḡa nuꞌa naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe horonirotene, ze maḡune rudanadu zeḡe zuhiꞌa vaḡe onamiro ebu hariḡa niduꞌa ihoniro.
\v 32 ꞌOugadu zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa tuḡure vazeḡa ibiꞌa hunadu niro, 'Ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa sauꞌa! Ḡaꞌa umihadu ḡa eḡe mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe hadiḡa niduꞌa baronogaꞌe eḡeꞌa ahiḡa rae reiro.
\v 33 Eḡeꞌa ḡae vetuḡaḡadateꞌe teige, ḡae zuni ḡae vaze, tuḡure vazeḡa eꞌe vetuḡanifo!'
\v 34 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa zama ḡugiꞌano ani aduga hanoga veize ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoniro, onamo ane hadi niduꞌa barone hauḡiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 35 Eꞌe teige, zaeꞌa zamaze niduꞌa hina zae nego nabudi haḡaize sauꞌa mene rae modine, eḡe Mama adureo zuni zae mazao ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma.”
\c 19
\s1 Roḡae Modeꞌeteꞌe moneo Ihoziro
\r (Mareko 10:1-12)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa eꞌe ḡoeꞌa hauḡirotene Galilea habaꞌa modadu Ioridana vuḡa moneafa Iudea habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 2 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani hegotiro ebu aniꞌa eꞌea ugi azaḡa faiziro.
\p 
\v 3 Farisea azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu tuhune nurifine ani vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Ohoze ꞌahoganiꞌa inuga mazao mene matuꞌine, inuga modogaꞌe idaḡahe?”
\v 4 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Za Buka Zaḡoḡa mene meꞌodirohe? Ḡadaheḡano Badiꞌaꞌa vaze haḡairotene, ohoze zu roḡae haḡairo.\x + \xo 19:4 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 1:27\x*
\v 5 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Eꞌanoꞌo ohozeꞌe viꞌa moga modadu inuga teite tiburaꞌuma ebu anianine ahiri tiba reꞌuma.'\x + \xo 19:5 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 2:24\x*
\v 6 Eꞌe uꞌano, zeꞌe mene aheu, rehano ahiri tiba. Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa tibuzirotaꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa mene rovoniꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 7 Zeꞌa ḡadiniro, “ꞌOugine, nougadu Moseꞌa ḡoere riḡa ꞌadi ziro, 'Ohozeꞌa inuga modoꞌidene, ihore soꞌaḡa mirihadu inuga hanoꞌi ebu ani modoꞌi.'\x + \xo 19:7 \xt Goro 24:1\x*”
\v 8 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zamaze riḡa ꞌahine, Moseꞌa inudeze modogaꞌe idaḡa rae reiro. Rehano ḡadaheḡanoꞌe mene idararo.
\v 9 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa inugaꞌe mene ubuma ḡezaro rehano, inuga modadu roḡae ꞌahoga teite hahurine, aniꞌe ubuma ḡezauꞌohe.”
\p 
\v 10 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Iesu niro, “ꞌAhiguḡaniꞌa iꞌa inuga mazao fureraune, guruvorau radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ufeta manoḡa.”
\v 11 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Vaze niduꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi mae ḡihinogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa danazeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo idaḡa.
\v 12 Vaze nuꞌe fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo ahiri ugiḡeta radu mene hahureꞌohe. Nuꞌe vazeꞌa ahiri ariro. Nuꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazoga veize gauihi radu zeḡeꞌa bare mene hahuriro. Iniuꞌa ꞌahi ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihinoga idaḡa roꞌidene, mae ḡihinoꞌi.”
\s1 Tahiꞌa Komeꞌakomeꞌa ebu Iesu
\r (Mareko 10:13-16; Luka 18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze nuꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa tutuze Iesu vaḡe ariro, mazaḡa aniꞌa ze rana ꞌevoꞌa teadu kuranoga uratiro. Rehano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa tutuze ariroteꞌe azaḡa roziro.
\v 14 ꞌOugirotene, Iesuꞌa ziro, “Tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa eḡe vaḡe tuḡuzoꞌi zu ze ago gararoꞌi. Mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa teigeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.”
\v 15 Ebu aniꞌa zeḡe rana ꞌevoꞌa teadu kuraroteꞌe ḡarugano eꞌea iḡune onamiro.
\s1 Maꞌora Vazeḡa
\r (Mareko 10:17-31; Luka 18:18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, e nagi manoḡa haḡaine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma?”
\v 17 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡaꞌe nougadu eḡe mazao naginiꞌe manoḡa rae ḡadimuꞌohe? Manoḡaꞌe Badiꞌa tibuhuga daꞌo. Ḡaꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidihi roꞌidene, Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa hegotoꞌi.”
\v 18 Vaze eꞌeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Noꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa hegotiꞌuma?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “'Vaze ago gorunoꞌi, ubuma ago ḡezanoꞌi, ago ḡonotanoꞌi, vaze moneo ago ḡuriroꞌi,
\v 19 viꞌu mogo gubazoꞌi\x + \xo 19:19 \xt Vaḡiniro 20:12-16; Goro 5:16-20\x* ebu ḡaeꞌa bare zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige nabugo zuni zamare borofoꞌi.\x + \xo 19:19 \xt Dibuꞌo 19:18\x*'”
\v 20 Tahiꞌa iziganiꞌa niro, “E goro ḡoeꞌa eꞌe niduꞌa hegote ariro. Hena nagini bare haḡaiꞌuma?”
\v 21 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa reihi roꞌidene, onamadu ḡauḡo niduꞌa seronoꞌi ebu zahara azaḡa zenoꞌi. ꞌOugine, ḡa adureo ḡau naeḡa boroboro hidiꞌuma. Ebu aradu eḡe hegotoꞌi.”
\v 22 Tahiꞌa iziganiꞌa Iesu ḡoere igirotene, zamaḡaniꞌa adudu bororuꞌenaꞌa iḡuniro, mazaḡa aniꞌe ufeta maꞌora vazeḡa.
\p 
\v 23 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, maꞌora vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rougaꞌe riḡa bagaḡa.
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa bare ziꞌohe, kameroꞌa niduru hoꞌoga diuḡogaꞌe riḡa. Rehano maꞌora vazeḡaniꞌa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano rougaꞌe ufeta riḡa.”
\v 25 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa eꞌe igirotene, zaguzagau rudaro ebu ḡadiniro, “ꞌOugine, iniuꞌa ḡabone hidiꞌuma?”
\v 26 Iesuꞌa ḡiazadu ziro, “Vaze aneꞌa bare ḡabone hidogaꞌe mene idaḡa, rehano Badiꞌaꞌe ḡau niduꞌa haḡaoga idaḡa.”
\p 
\v 27 Ebu Peteroꞌa niro, “Eme emeḡe ḡau niduꞌa modadu ḡa hegotiro. ꞌOugadu emeꞌe nagini hidiꞌuma?”
\v 28 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Raha ꞌahi niduꞌaꞌe bare izidatiteꞌe madaḡano Vaze Ubuganiꞌa kini ehoro habaꞌa ḡihiꞌaḡa hune rana ehorine, eḡe hegotiroteꞌe azaḡa, zae zuni kini ehoro habaꞌa gaubanana aheu fare rana ehoradu Isaraela azaḡa, urabo niduꞌa gaubanana aheu fare kotaziꞌuma.
\v 29 Ebu iniuꞌa eḡe uꞌano neḡa, negoḡa, ezeḡa, viꞌa, moga, tahiꞌaḡa ga ane haba modine, aniꞌe naeḡa ḡae 100 hidiꞌuma ebu Moga mazaonoꞌo ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.
\v 30 Rehano vaze ibiꞌa ḡehaḡaꞌe ḡonaga reꞌuma, u vaze ḡonaga ḡehaḡaꞌe ibiꞌa reꞌuma.”
\c 20
\s1 Vaini Mebaḡa Gau Azaḡa Hari Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe hari ꞌadi heuḡa. Haba vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ane vaini meba veize gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa vaḡihi radu oherebau uzeuze onamiro.
\v 2 Ebu aneꞌa vaze nu horozadu ziro, 'Eḡe meba onamadu gauoꞌi. Mada tiba gauḡa hadiḡa\f + \fr 20:2 \fqa denari tiba \f* ziniꞌuma.' ꞌOugadu aniꞌa ze mebaḡano tuḡuze onamiro.
\v 3 Ebu oherebau mada fuꞌo ḡazaḡa fare meirotene ani bare onamiro. Ebu maketi habaꞌano mene gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌe edau radiuꞌeteꞌe horoziro.
\v 4 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, 'Za zu eḡe vaini mebaḡa onamoꞌi ebu gauḡa hadiḡa idane ziniꞌuma.'
\v 5 ꞌOugadu ze ane meba onamiro. Aniꞌa madai zu mada uḡidu ḡoravaḡano bare onamadu ꞌouge haḡairo.
\v 6 Mada fuꞌo ḡoravaḡano ani onamirotene, vaze nuꞌe edau ragaveꞌeteꞌe horozadu ḡadiziro, 'Za nougadu mada niduga mene gaueꞌenaꞌa edau tauḡeꞌohe?'
\v 7 Zeꞌa naenaeniro, 'Mazaḡa vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa eme gau ꞌahoga mene refeha.' ꞌOugadu aneꞌa ziro, 'Zae zuni eḡe vaini mebaḡa onamadu gauoꞌi.'
\p 
\v 8 Madaꞌa ovorirotene, vaini mebaḡa vazeḡaniꞌa meba taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa niro, 'Gau azaḡa huzadu ḡonaga vazeḡanonoꞌo ibite vazeḡa gau hadiḡa zenoꞌi.'
\v 9 Mada fuꞌo ḡoravaḡano huziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa aradu aneane mada tiba gau hadiḡa meiro.
\v 10 ꞌOugadu ibite ariroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ze hadi ufeta boro meꞌuma rae zamariro. Rehano zeḡe zuni aneane mada tiba gau hadiḡa idane meiro.
\v 11 Zeꞌa eꞌe hadiḡa madu haba vazeḡa mazao maḡuniro ebu tururuꞌenaꞌa niro,
\v 12 'Ḡonagano arateꞌe azaḡaꞌe mada tahiḡa daꞌo gauꞌeha. U emeꞌa mada gigiꞌa zamaḡano mada niduga gau boro haḡaeha. Rehano ḡaꞌe zeḡe hadiꞌe emeḡe teite idane zeneha.'
\v 13 Haba vazeḡaniꞌa zeḡe boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga naenaeniro, 'Eḡe vaze, eꞌe mene nae daꞌo badareha. Ḡaꞌe eḡe teite ḡoere idane teadu mada tiba gau hadiḡa meꞌuma rae raha.
\v 14 Eꞌanoꞌo hadiḡo madu onamoꞌi. E ḡonagano arateꞌe vazeḡa gau hadiꞌe ḡae hadi teite idane hatihi raꞌohe.
\v 15 Eḡeꞌa eḡe hadi hina eḡe edeḡano haḡaine, veꞌoḡahe? Eḡeꞌa vaze ufeta danazadu ḡaeꞌa ahiahiheꞌehe?'”
\v 16 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eꞌanoꞌo vaze ḡonagaꞌe ibiꞌa reꞌuma ebu vaze ibiꞌaꞌe ḡonaga reꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Rune moneo Bare Ziro
\r (Mareko 10:32-34; Luka 18:31-34)
\p 
\v 17 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema iteꞌeteꞌea, ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare ane uhiḡano huzadu ibio ziro,
\v 18 “Eme Ierusalema iteꞌohe. Ebu Vaze Ubugaꞌe dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniꞌuma zu runeo tuḡuniꞌuma.
\v 19 Ebu Iuda mene azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌinadu zeꞌa ḡirihohaꞌuma, masiniꞌuma zu satauroniꞌuma. Rehano mada uḡiduḡano aneꞌa bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”
\s1 Iakobo zu Ioane Vizeꞌa Iesu Uminiro
\r (Mareko 10:35-45)
\p 
\v 20 Eꞌe madaḡano Zebedeo ubugaubuga, Iakobo zu Ioane, ze vizeꞌa zeḡe teite Iesu vaḡe aradu obena hina tuḡiro ebu ḡau ꞌahoga uminiro.
\v 21 Iesuꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe nagini urateꞌohe?” Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡaeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡa moꞌidene, eḡe ubude aheu ohozadu tibaꞌe ḡae edaꞌe mone zu ꞌahogaꞌe ḡae kauri mone iḡuꞌa ḡihiꞌaḡano ehoroga urateꞌohe.”
\v 22 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za zaeꞌa nagini umiheꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa. Eḡeꞌa gagiteꞌe bioḡa aduga zaeꞌa gagoga idaḡahe?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe, eme idaḡa.”
\v 23 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hube hune eḡe bio zae zuni gagiꞌuma. Rehano eḡe edaꞌe mone zu kauri mone iḡuꞌa ḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa mene ziniꞌuma, rehano eḡe Mamaꞌa ohoziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa daꞌo iḡuꞌa eꞌe meꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 24 Iesu tahiꞌa gaubananaꞌa eꞌe igirotene, Iakobo zu Ioane mazao maḡuniro.
\v 25 Rehano Iesuꞌa huze nuꞌozadu ziro, “Za edeḡa, Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa habaꞌano zuhiꞌa niduꞌaꞌe zeḡe haba azaḡa riḡa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe, ebu gavana vazeḡa boroboroꞌe inaraze hina zeḡe haba azaḡa rana edauꞌohe.
\v 26 Rehano zaꞌe ze ago teigoꞌi. Zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune reihi reine, aniꞌe zae tuḡure vazeḡa reꞌuma.
\v 27 Ebu iniuꞌe zae boꞌaḡano vaze ibiꞌa reihi reine, aniꞌe zae tuḡure vazeḡa rae reꞌuma.
\v 28 Mazaḡa Vaze Ubugaꞌe vazeꞌe ane tuḡure azaḡa rouga radu mene ariro, rehano aniꞌe vaze tuḡure vazeḡa rouga radu ariro. Ebu vaze ḡehaḡa veize ane ḡabone hina dibuꞌohafine ariro.”
\s1 Ubuma Kuruḡa Azaḡa Faiziro
\r (Mareko 10:46-52; Luka 18:35-43)
\p 
\v 29 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Ieriko mode iḡunirotene, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani hegotiro.
\v 30 Ebu ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa aheuꞌe ibi genaḡano ehore radiunu. Ze Iesuꞌa vitau onameꞌeteꞌe egadu ḡihau huaro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Davida mariga, eme vetuḡafoꞌi!”
\v 31 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa horozadu roziro, “Za sifu radoꞌi!” Rehano zeꞌe ufeta ḡihau huaro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Davida mariga, eme vetuḡafoꞌi!”
\v 32 Ebu Iesuꞌa tue edanadu huziro ebu ḡadiziro, “Eḡeꞌa zae veize nagini haḡaoga urateꞌohe?”
\v 33 Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme ehamatihi.”
\v 34 Ebu Iesuꞌa vetuḡazeadu ubumaze oboniro. ꞌOugirotene, ubumazeꞌa zogone manoradu ze ehamaro ebu Iesu hegotiro. \fig Iesuꞌa ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa faiziro|src="WA03884b.tif" size="col" ref="20:30-34"\fig*
\c 21
\s1 Ierusalema Diuḡiro
\r (Mareko 11:1-11; Luka 19:28-38; Ioane 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Ierusalema hanitadu Olivi Maḡano Betefage neḡano feuriro. Ebu ane tahiꞌa aheu tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa, ziro,
\v 2 “Zama ḡoha neḡa onamoꞌi. Eꞌe neḡa diuḡine, doniki ꞌahoga batune touga ubugeta horoziꞌuma. Ebu fuhiꞌadu eḡe vaḡe zamaze aroꞌi.
\v 3 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡoere nu zoꞌidene, 'Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa urateꞌohe,' rae noꞌi. ꞌOugine ani zogone tuḡuziꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 4 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡanonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro,
\q1 
\v 5 “Ierusalema azaḡa\f + \fr 21:5 \fqa Sioni aboḡa\f* mazao ꞌahige zoꞌi,
\q2 'Ḡianoꞌi, zae Kiniꞌe zae vaḡe areꞌohe.
\q1 Aniꞌe vaḡuꞌa ebu doniki rana ehoreha.
\q2 Doniki ubuga rana ehoradu areꞌohe.'”\x + \xo 21:5 \xt Zekaria 9:9\x*
\p 
\v 6 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa aheuꞌa onamadu Iesuꞌa nagini ziroteꞌe idunaḡano haḡairo.
\v 7 Ze doniki ubugeta tutuze Iesu vaḡe aradu dabuaze doniki ubuga ḡarunio zahariro, ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌe rana tire ehoriro.
\v 8 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa dabuaze ibio hirau tiro, u vaze nuꞌe ire ezaga variꞌe madu ibi rana hiraro.
\v 9 Ebu Iesu zamao onameꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu ḡaruna hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa huaro,
\q1 “Hosana, Davida mariga nigunihi!
\q1 Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune!
\q1 Hosana, hitana huneo nigunihi!”\x + \xo 21:9 \xt Salamo 118:26\x*
\p 
\v 10 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema diuḡirotene, ne azaḡa niduꞌa haraeꞌenaꞌa, ḡadimutitiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe iniu?”
\v 11 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa naenaeziro, “ꞌAdiꞌe peroveta vazeḡa Iesu, Galilea habaꞌano Nazareta neḡa vazeḡa.” \fig Iesuꞌa Ierusalema diuḡiro|src="CN01784B.TIF" size="col" ref="21:1-11"\fig*
\s1 Kuru Neḡa Deheniro
\r (Mareko 11:15-19; Luka 19:45-48; Ioane 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Ebu Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌa diuḡadu hoiteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu seroneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa hegoze buziro. Ebu hadi seniso ziniꞌeteꞌe\f + \fr 21:12 \ft Kuru neḡa takesiḡa veize. \f* azaḡa fata zu Tubugo niniḡa seroneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ehoro habaꞌa mae ḡihuniro.
\v 13 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Badiꞌa neꞌe kuru neḡa reꞌuma.'\x + \xo 21:13 \xt Isaia 56:7; Ieremia 7:11 \x* Rehano zaeꞌa kuru neḡaꞌe ḡonore azaḡa neḡano ḡihuniro.”
\p 
\v 14 Ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa ebu oda sauꞌa azaḡaniꞌa ani vaḡe kuru neḡa habaꞌa aradu aniꞌa faiziro.
\v 15 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa haḡai gigiꞌa nunu haḡairoteꞌe horoniro. Ebu tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌaꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌano huauꞌenaꞌa, “Hosana, Davida mariga!” rae reiroteꞌe igiro. ꞌOugadu ze maḡune rudaro.
\v 16 Ebu ze Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌaꞌa nagini raꞌeteꞌe igiꞌehe? Ze gararoꞌi!” Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “E igiꞌohe. Rehano zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡa mene meꞌodirohe? 'Badiꞌaꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa zu ene guraḡaguraḡaniꞌa ani nigunoga ihoziro.'\x + \xo 21:16 \xt Salamo 8:2\x*”
\v 17 Eꞌe enogano ani ze muhizadu Ierusalema ḡutuꞌaḡa onamiro ebu Betania neḡa onamadu ohere eꞌea baziro.
\s1 Figi Ireḡaniꞌa Roraro
\r (Mareko 11:12-14, 20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Irarirotene, Iesuꞌa Ierusalema bare onamiro. Eꞌe ibiḡano ani vininiro.
\v 19 Ebu figi ireḡa ibi genaḡano horonadu huga vaḡe onamiro. Rehano ire huga oꞌoꞌa zu rouḡa daꞌo horonadu ire eꞌe niro, “Ḡa mene bare hudaꞌuma!” ꞌOugadu ire eꞌeꞌa zogone roraro.
\p 
\v 20 Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa eꞌe horonadu zaguzagaro ebu ḡadiniro, “Nougenouge figi ireḡaniꞌa ḡarihe roraneha?”
\v 21 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, za Badiꞌa mazao fine zu mene ꞌadaꞌadazine, eḡeꞌa figi ireḡa ꞌahi mazao haḡataꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa zuni haḡaiꞌuma. Ebu maḡa ꞌahi ninaꞌa, 'Ḡihitadu davara zamaḡano buanoꞌi,' rae reine, ꞌouge fureraꞌuma.
\v 22 Zaeꞌa kurauꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano nagini umineꞌeteꞌeꞌa hugano fureraꞌuma. Zaeꞌa eꞌe mae ḡihinine, zae umino niduꞌa hidiꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesu Gigiꞌaḡa moneo Ḡadiniro
\r (Mareko 11:27-33; Luka 20:1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa diuḡadu vaze ihozirotene, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa ani vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa noꞌe gigiꞌaḡa hina ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌohe? Iniuꞌa ꞌahi gigiꞌaḡa ḡaniro?”
\v 24 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe zuni ḡadimu ꞌahoga zinihi. Zaeꞌa naenaehine, eḡe zuni noꞌe gigiꞌaḡa hina ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe ihoziꞌuma.
\v 25 Ioaneꞌa babatiso zinirotaꞌaꞌe noumanoꞌo? Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ga vaze mazaonoꞌo?” Ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡoꞌaneꞌenaꞌa, ḡadimutitiro, “Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo reine, 'Za nougadu Ioane ḡoere mene mae ḡihiniro?' rae ifiꞌuma.
\v 26 Rehano vaze mazaonoꞌo reine, eme vaze rihozeꞌohe, mazaḡa zeḡe niduꞌa Ioaneꞌe hube hune peroveta vazeḡa rae mae ḡihineꞌohe.”
\v 27 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ꞌahige naenaeniro, “Emeꞌe aḡuꞌa.” Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡe zuni noꞌe gigiꞌaḡa hina haḡai ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe mene ihoziꞌuma.”
\s1 Ubuga Aheu Hari Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 28 Iesuꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboro mazao hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga ziro, “Za hari idaidaḡa ꞌahi zamaroꞌi. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ubuga aheu teite radiunu. Aniꞌa ubuga ibiꞌa vaḡe onamadu niro, 'Eḡe tahiꞌa, ḡa izidi vaini mebaḡano gaui onamoꞌi.'
\v 29 Ebu ubuganiꞌa naenaeniro, 'E mene onamiꞌuma.' Rehano ani vesuꞌu zamaḡa ḡihunadu onamiro.
\v 30 Ebu moganiꞌa ubuga veḡa vaḡe onamadu ubuga ibiꞌa niroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa idaḡa niro. Aniꞌa Moga niro, 'E onamiꞌuma.' Rehano ani mene onamiro.
\v 31 Zaꞌa zamareꞌetene, ubuga aheu boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa moga ura haḡairo?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Ubuga ibiꞌa.”
\p Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, takesi azaḡa zu daro fuꞌa roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ibite diuḡiꞌuma. Zeḡeꞌa zae vitiziꞌuma.
\v 32 Ioane Babatisoꞌe ibi duduḡa ihozoga radu zae vaḡe ariro, rehano za mene mae ḡihiniro. U takesi azaḡa zu daro fuꞌa roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡaꞌe ani ḡoere mae ḡihiniro. Za zeḡeꞌa ꞌouge haḡairoteꞌe horoniro rehano, mene ḡihuradu ani mene mae ḡihiniro.”
\s1 Hihi Azaḡa Sauꞌa Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Mareko 12:1-12; Luka 20:9-19)
\p 
\v 33 Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga egoꞌi. Haba vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌa vaini mebaḡa ḡoranadu ḡabiꞌa merau varahiro, ebu vaini maḡa vuḡa gigeꞌeteꞌe veize iduḡa ꞌahoga huꞌiro, zu ehamuꞌeteꞌe neḡa hitaga haḡairo. Hena vaini mebaḡa eꞌe hihi azaḡa nu ꞌevoreo tiro, ebu aniꞌe haba ꞌahoga onamadu mada faḡa ragavinu.
\p 
\v 34 Hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa hanitirotene, vaini maḡa nu mouga radu aniꞌa ane tuḡure azaḡaꞌe hihi azaḡa vaḡe tuḡuze onamiro.
\v 35 Rehano zeḡeꞌa tuḡure azaḡa oboze teadu tibaꞌe bouniro, ꞌahogaꞌe maro ebu ꞌahogaꞌe hadi hina mau bohiniro.
\v 36 Hena haba vazeḡaniꞌa tuḡureḡa azaḡa ibiꞌa vitine ufeta ḡehaḡa zeḡe vaḡe bare tuḡuziro, rehano ze tuḡure azaḡa eꞌe mazao haḡai tiba eꞌe bare haḡairo.
\p 
\v 37 Ḡonagano aniꞌa ubuga zeḡe vaḡe tuḡunadu ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Ze eḡe ubude gubaniꞌuma gaogi.'
\v 38 Rehano hihi azaḡaniꞌa ubuga horonirotene, zeḡeꞌa neneḡaniro, 'Aniꞌe moga mazaonoꞌo vaini mebaḡa ꞌadi meiteꞌe vazeḡa. Eme ani matihi ebu vaini mebaḡa ꞌadi emeḡeꞌa meihi.'
\v 39 Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌa ani obone teadu vaini mebaḡanonoꞌo ani uhine bunadu mau runiro.”
\p 
\v 40 Ebu Iesuꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboro ḡadiziro, “ꞌOugadu vaini mebaḡa vazeḡaꞌe hihi azaḡa eꞌe vaḡe arine, zeḡe mazao nougiꞌuma?”
\v 41 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aniꞌa hihi azaḡa eꞌe mau ruziꞌuma. Ebu vaini mebaḡaꞌe hihi azaḡa ꞌahoga nu ziniꞌuma. ꞌOugine, hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano zeḡeꞌa ani huga nu haꞌuma.”
\v 42 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano ḡoere ꞌahi mene meꞌodirohe?
\q1 'Vazeꞌa hadi hina ne ogorarotene, zeꞌa mae modiroteꞌe hadiḡaꞌe ne duꞌe rinedeꞌeteꞌe hadiḡa reiro.
\q1 Aꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa. Emeḡeꞌa ḡianadu zaguzagauꞌohe.'\x + \xo 21:42 \xt Salamo 118:22-23\x*
\p 
\v 43 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌaꞌa za, Isaraela azaḡa mene bare zuhiꞌaziꞌuma, rehano haba ꞌahoga azaḡa ane ura haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.
\v 44 Iniuꞌa hadi eꞌe rana higaune, ani varadu tahitahiꞌuma zu hadi eꞌeꞌa iniu rana higaune, aniꞌe seꞌetiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 45 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iesu hari idaidaḡa igirotene, Iesuꞌa zeḡe moneo reirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.
\v 46 ꞌOugadu zeꞌe Iesu obone tihi reiro. Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa zeḡe mazao maḡuniꞌuma radu rihoziro, mazaḡa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌe peroveta vazeḡa rae mae ḡihiniro.
\c 22
\s1 Hahu Muiḡa Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Luka 14:15-24)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa hari idaidaḡa nu hina bare ḡoreziro,
\v 2 “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe kini ꞌahoga heuḡa. Aniꞌa ubuga veize hahu muiḡa haḡairo.
\v 3 Ebu huziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa mui aroga veize tuḡure azaḡa zeḡe vaḡe tuḡuziro. Rehano zeꞌe aroga hezahiro.
\v 4 Ebu aniꞌa tuḡure azaḡa ꞌahoga nu bare tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa, ziro, 'Eḡeꞌa huzateꞌe azaḡaꞌe ꞌahige rae zoꞌi: Eḡeꞌa zae veize mui ruhibeha. Boromakau zu mani iga manadu ogomu niduꞌa ꞌai ruhibeha. Hahu muiḡa uꞌa aroꞌi.'
\v 5 Rehano ze teḡa riraro ebu zeḡe edeḡano onamiro. ꞌAhogaꞌe mebaḡa onamiro ebu ꞌahogaꞌe hadi vaḡi onamiro.
\v 6 Ebu nuꞌe tuḡure azaḡa oboze teadu sausauziro ebu zimi ruziro.
\v 7 Kiniꞌa eꞌe igirotene, ani maḡune rudaro. Ebu ani uti azaḡa tuḡuzadu gorugoru azaḡa eꞌe zimi hauḡiro zu neze zuni hufi haoniro.
\p 
\v 8 Ebu ane tuḡure azaḡa huzadu ziro, 'E hahu muiḡa ꞌai ruhibe idaneha, rehano eḡeꞌa huziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe arogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo ibi boroboro onamadu horoziteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa mui aroga veize huzoꞌi.'
\v 10 Ebu ane tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ibi boroboro onamadu hidiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa, manoḡa zu sauꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa nuꞌoziro ebu zamaze onamadu huziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa mui neḡa iri'avoniro.
\p 
\v 11 Ebu kiniꞌa iꞌudo azaḡa ḡiazihi radu diuḡirotene, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa hahu mui dabuaḡa mene vidaroteꞌe horoniro.
\v 12 ꞌOugadu aneꞌa ḡadiniro, ꞌEḡe nabudi, ḡaꞌe hahu dabuaḡa mene vidaneha. Nougenouge ꞌadi diuḡi areha?' Rehano ani ḡoere ꞌahoga mene reiro.
\v 13 ꞌOugadu kiniꞌa ane gau azaḡa ziro, 'Ani ꞌevoꞌa zu odaḡa batunadu enone uzaboḡano feune bunoꞌi. Ane eꞌea niaꞌuma zu ḡononeḡa atitiꞌuma.'”
\v 14 Ḡonagano Iesuꞌa ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa huziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa, rehano ohotiroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tahiḡa daꞌo.”
\s1 Takesi Hadiḡa Iniu Haꞌuma?
\r (Mareko 12:13-17; Luka 20:20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Eꞌe madaḡano Farisea azaḡaniꞌa onamadu, “Iesuꞌa ḡoere veꞌoḡa ꞌahoga reine obone tiꞌuma,” rae ḡoꞌaniro.
\v 16 Ebu zeꞌa zeḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa zu kini Heroda mone azaḡaꞌe Iesu mazao tuḡuzadu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, emeꞌe edeḡa, ḡaꞌe huga daꞌo ḡoereꞌohe zu Badiꞌa mone ibiḡa hugano ihozeꞌohe ebu vaze niduꞌa mazao mene inaheꞌenaꞌa, vaze uꞌano zamaḡo mene haganeꞌohe.
\v 17 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaꞌe nouge rae zamareꞌohe? Emeꞌe Roma kiniḡa mazao takesi haune, duduḡa ga mene?”
\p 
\v 18 Iesuꞌe zeḡe zamarone sauꞌa ederadu ziro, “Zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa, nougadu eḡe tuhuheꞌohe?
\v 19 Takesi hadiḡa ihohoꞌi.” Ze Roma hadiḡa\f + \fr 22:19 \fqa denari\f* tiba mae harotene,
\v 20 aneꞌa ḡadiziro, “Iniu viga zu iniu niḡaꞌe eꞌe rana mirihiro?”
\v 21 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aꞌe Roma kiniḡa viga zu niḡa.” Ebu aneꞌa ziro, “Tena Roma kiniḡa ḡauꞌe Roma kiniḡa hanoꞌi, u Badiꞌa ḡauꞌe Badiꞌa hanoꞌi.”
\v 22 Ze ani ḡoere igirotene zaguzagaro ebu ani muhinadu oname ḡouriro.
\s1 Runeonoꞌo Bare Ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe Ḡadimuḡa
\r (Mareko 12:18-27; Luka 20:27-40)
\p 
\v 23 Eꞌe madaḡano Sadukea azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu vaḡe ariro. Sadukea azaḡaꞌe vazeꞌa runeonoꞌo mene bare ḡabodiꞌuma rae reiro. Zeḡeꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro,
\v 24 “Ihore vazeḡa, Moseꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌahoga ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Ohoze ꞌahoganiꞌa rudanadu ani inugaꞌe ubuga ꞌoꞌoꞌa reine, ohoze negoḡaniꞌa ḡozobaḡa teite hahuriꞌuma, ebu ubuga furenadu ubuganiꞌa rune negoḡa ehaꞌa meꞌuma.'\x + \xo 22:24 \xt Goro 25:5-6\x*
\p 
\v 25 Tena hari ꞌahi zamaroꞌi. Negoḡa niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa radiunu. Ibiꞌaniꞌa hahuriro ebu ubuga oꞌoꞌa rudaro. ꞌOugadu negoḡa aheuḡaniꞌa ḡozobaḡa teite hahuriro.
\v 26 Rehano ane zuni ubuga oꞌoꞌa rudaro, ebu negoḡa uḡiduḡa onamo fuꞌo aheu fare mazao ꞌuguḡaniꞌa idane fureraro.
\v 27 Ḡonagano ḡozoba eꞌe zuni rudaro.
\v 28 Tena runeonoꞌo bare ḡaboditeꞌe madaḡano roḡae aꞌe iniu inuga reꞌuma? Mazaḡa ohoze niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa ani teite hahuriro.”
\p 
\v 29 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌa zamareꞌetaꞌaꞌe veꞌoḡa, mazaḡa zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡa ga Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa moneo aḡuꞌa.
\v 30 Runeonoꞌo bare ḡaboditeꞌe madaḡanoꞌe ohoze zu roḡaeꞌe mene hahuriꞌuma. Zeꞌe tuḡure viga adureo teigiꞌuma.
\v 31 Rune azaḡaniꞌa bare ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe moneo, Badiꞌaꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zaeꞌa mene meꞌodirohe? Aneꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro,
\v 32 'Eꞌe Aberahamo Badiꞌa, Isako Badiꞌa zu Iakobo Badiꞌa.' \x + \xo 22:32 \xt Vaḡiniro 3:6\x*Badiꞌaꞌe mene rune azaḡa Badiꞌa, rehano ḡabone azaḡa Badiꞌa.”
\v 33 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu ihoreḡa ḡoeꞌa igirotene, zaguzagaro.
\s1 Goro Ḡoeꞌa Ḡihiꞌa Hune
\r (Mareko 12:28-34; Luka 10:25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Ebu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌa Sadukea azaḡa ḡadimu naenaenadu hebeze ꞌuiroteꞌe hariḡa igirotene, tibano nuꞌoraro.
\v 35 Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu tuhune nurihi radu ḡadiniro,
\v 36 “Ihore vazeḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano noꞌe goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune?”
\p 
\v 37 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Goro ḡoeꞌa ḡihiꞌa huneꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: 'Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡae Badiꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina, vineḡo niduꞌa hina zu zamaroneḡo niduꞌa hina zamare borofoꞌi.'\x + \xo 22:37 \xt Goro 6:5 \x*
\v 38 Aꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa ibiꞌa zu ḡihiꞌa hune.
\v 39 Goro ḡoeꞌa ḡihiꞌa hune aheuḡa zuni eꞌe heuḡa: 'Ḡa ḡae bare zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, nabugo zuni zamare borofoꞌi.'\x + \xo 22:39 \xt Dibuꞌo 19:18\x*
\v 40 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa ebu peroveta azaḡaniꞌa ihoziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa aheu eꞌe rana ohoniro.”
\s1 Kerisoꞌe Iniu Mariga?
\r (Mareko 12:35-37; Luka 20:41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Farisea azaḡaniꞌa nuꞌoraroteꞌe zamaḡano Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro,
\v 42 “Zaꞌe Keriso moneo nouge rae zamareꞌohe? Aniꞌe iniu mariga?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aniꞌe Davida mariga.”
\v 43 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Tena nougadu Davidaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ihonadu Keriso mazao Zuhiꞌa Boro rae huniro? Aniꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro,
\q1 
\v 44 'Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro niro,
\q1 “Eḡe edaꞌe moneo ehoroꞌi, onamo eḡeꞌa agireḡo niduꞌa madu odaḡo ꞌuꞌuḡano raharahaziꞌuma.”'\x + \xo 22:44 \xt Salamo 110:1\x*
\m 
\v 45 Davidaꞌa Keriso mazao Zuhiꞌa Boro rae huniro. Tena Kerisoꞌe nougenouge Davida mariga reꞌuma?”
\v 46 Ebu vazeni ꞌahoga zuni Iesu mene naenaeniro. Eꞌe enogano vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu mene bare ḡadiniro.
\c 23
\s1 Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌa Ihozeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa zu Farisea Azaḡa Roziro
\r (Mareko 12:38-40; Luka 11:37-52, 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 1 Ebu Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro,
\v 2 “Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe iḡuꞌa meiroteꞌe azaḡa.
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌa nagini raꞌeteꞌe egozenadu haḡaoꞌi. Rehano zeḡe haḡaiꞌe ago hegotoꞌi, mazaḡa zeꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare zae ihozeꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano mene haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 4 Ze ihoreꞌe riga hune radu vazeꞌa eꞌe hegotoga mene idaḡa. Zeꞌe vaze daꞌo aduga boro ziniꞌohe, rehano zeḡe ꞌevore huduꞌa tiba hina zu mene hune danazeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 5 Ze vazeꞌa horozoga veize haḡai niduꞌa haḡaeꞌohe. Ze Badiꞌa ḡoere soꞌaḡa ufeꞌeteꞌe umaḡa ufeta rafane haḡadu amusize rana tatuhe uteꞌohe zu dabuaze faḡafeꞌohe.
\v 6 Muioꞌe nize boro azaḡaniꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano ehoroga urateꞌohe, zu nuꞌonuꞌo neḡanoꞌe vaze boroboroꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano ehoroga urateꞌohe.
\v 7 Ebu vaze ḡehaḡa habaꞌanoꞌe vazeꞌa gubazeꞌenaꞌa, zeḡe mazao unihoga zu 'Ihore Vazeḡa,'\f + \fr 23:7 \fqa Rabi \f* rae huzoga urateꞌohe. \fig Badiꞌa ḡoere soꞌaḡa ufeꞌeteꞌe umaḡa|src="41_Mat23:5_PhylacteryLarge_2" size="col" ref="23:5"\fig*
\p 
\v 8 Rehano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zae mazao 'Ihore Vazeḡa' rae huzoga gararoꞌi, mazaḡa za ihore vazeḡaꞌe tiba daꞌo. Zae niduꞌaꞌe idaḡa daꞌo, negoze zu ezeze.
\v 9 Ebu rahao ꞌada vaze ꞌahoga 'Mama,' rae ago hunoꞌi, mazaḡa adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa daꞌoꞌe zae Mama.
\v 10 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zae mazao 'Ibitoziꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa' rae huzoga gararo'i, mazaḡa zae ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Keriso daꞌo.
\v 11 Zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌe vaze ḡihiꞌa hune reine, aniꞌe zae tuḡure azaḡa reꞌuma.
\v 12 Iniu vaze aneꞌa bare niḡa mae itine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae ovoiꞌuma, u iniu vaze aneꞌa bare niḡa mae ovoine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae itiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 13 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazoga urateꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ibize ꞌueꞌohe. Zaꞌe zaeꞌa bare eꞌe mene urateꞌohe ebu urateꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni ꞌueꞌohe.\f + \fr 23:13 \fv 14 \fqa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Zaꞌe ḡozoba soꞌozadu toheze niduꞌa meizeꞌohe, zu vaze ihozifine faḡafe ḡurire kurauꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe aduga boro bagaḡa hidiꞌuma! \f*
\p 
\v 15 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Vaze tibaniꞌa ḡihuradu zae ihore hegotoga veize zaeꞌa davara zu haba ragave onameꞌohe. Ebu vaze ꞌahoga matene, ani ihonadu aniꞌa haḡai sauꞌa zae vitize ufeta haḡaeꞌohe. Ebu aniꞌe ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu diuḡadu adugaꞌe zae vitize ḡae aheu hideꞌohe.
\p 
\v 16 Zaꞌe vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, rehano ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Zaeꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Iniuꞌa kuru neḡa niḡano ḡoitorine, aꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa. Rehano iniuꞌa kuru neḡa zamaḡano golo hina ḡoitorine, aꞌe riḡa radu aniꞌa ane ḡoitore tihitihiniꞌuma.'
\v 17 Zaꞌe ubuma kuruḡa kauriḡa azaḡa! Noꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa? Golo ga kuru neḡa? Kuru neḡaꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa, mazaḡa goloꞌe kuru neḡa zamaḡano tiroteꞌe uꞌano aꞌe zaḡoḡa raꞌohe.
\v 18 Ebu za ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Iniuꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡa niḡano ḡoitorine, aꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa. Rehano iniuꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡano ḡahunoneḡa hina ḡoitorine, aꞌe riḡa radu aniꞌa ane ḡoitore tihitihiniꞌuma.'
\v 19 Zaꞌe ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa! Noꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa? Ḡahunoneḡa ga dibuꞌo fataḡa? Dibuꞌo fataḡaꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa, mazaḡa ḡahunoneḡaꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡa rana tiroteꞌe uꞌano aꞌe zaḡoḡa raꞌohe.
\v 20 Iniuꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡa niḡano ḡoitoreꞌetene, dibuꞌo fataḡa ebu eꞌe rana ḡau niduꞌa hina ḡoitoreꞌohe.
\v 21 Ebu iniuꞌa kuru neḡano ḡoitoreꞌetene, kuru neḡa niḡano ebu eꞌea ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa niḡano ḡoitoreꞌohe.
\v 22 Zu iniuꞌa adure niḡano ḡoitoreꞌetene, Badiꞌa ehoro habaꞌa hina zu eꞌe rana ehoreꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa niḡano ḡoitoreꞌohe.
\p 
\v 23 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe tirara mebaḡano eḡa zu murari teige komeꞌa fase ogomuḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo sinu gaubananao rovonadu sinu tiba mone ḡauḡa Badiꞌa hauꞌohe. Rehano Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ḡau ufeta boroboroꞌe igi modeꞌohe. Aꞌe haḡai duduḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe, vaze vetuḡaziꞌeteꞌe zu zama niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe. Za ḡau boro ꞌadiꞌe haḡaifo ebu komeꞌakomeꞌa zuni mene igi modifo.
\v 24 Zaꞌe vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, rehano ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa! Zaꞌe vu zamaḡano ofene horoneꞌetene beuꞌe modadu gageꞌohe, rehano kameloꞌe une tauḡeꞌohe.\f + \fr 23:24 \ft Ofene zu Kameloꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ago anoꞌi rae reiroteꞌe ḡauḡa. \f*
\p 
\v 25 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Zaꞌe bioze zu siuvaze enoga daꞌo vuzuꞌe deheneꞌohe, mazaḡa zamazeo matuꞌu veize daꞌo radiu tauḡitauḡeꞌohe zu ununuꞌa iriꞌaveꞌohe.
\v 26 Ubuma kuruḡa Farisea azaḡa! Bio zu siuva zamaḡa ibite geno vuzuꞌe dehenoꞌi, ꞌougine enoga zuni deheraꞌuma.
\p 
\v 27 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Zaꞌe ꞌuruḡa hina asiroteꞌe rune iduḡa heuḡa. Rune iduḡa enoga ḡianine manoḡa tauḡi, rehano zamaḡaꞌe rune azaḡa isine zu torare niduꞌa iriꞌaveꞌohe.
\v 28 Eꞌe teige, vazeꞌa zae enone daꞌo ḡiazadu zaꞌe duduḡa azaḡa rae raꞌohe, rehano zamazeꞌe zama guhi zu haḡai sauꞌaniꞌa iriꞌaveꞌohe.
\p 
\v 29 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Zaꞌe vouḡazeꞌa ibite zimiroteꞌe peroveta azaḡa rune iduḡa ogoruꞌohe, ebu haḡai duduḡa azaḡa rune iduḡa rohorohoneꞌohe.
\v 30 Ebu zaꞌe ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Emeꞌa vouḡafe madaḡano radifone, zeḡeꞌa peroveta azaḡa goruzihi rae reirotene zeḡe teite mene tiburafo.'
\v 31 ꞌOugadu za zaeꞌa bare peroveta azaḡa goruziroteꞌe azaḡa mariga rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 32 Eꞌanoꞌo zae zuni vouḡaze teige haḡaoꞌi. Zeḡeꞌa ḡadahiroteꞌe gauḡa zaeꞌa haḡae hauḡoꞌi!
\v 33 Zaꞌe mohe! Zarama ubugaubuga! Badiꞌaꞌa kotazadu zaꞌe ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuziꞌuma ebu eꞌeanoꞌo feranogaꞌe mene idaraꞌuma.
\v 34 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa peroveta azaḡa, huhuzaḡa azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zae vaḡe tuḡuzeꞌohe. Rehano nuꞌe zaeꞌa goruziꞌuma, nuꞌe satauroziꞌuma ebu nuꞌe zae nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano masiziꞌuma zu haba ꞌahoganonoꞌo haba ꞌahoga ze hegotadu sausauziꞌuma.
\v 35 Zaeꞌa raha ꞌada duduḡa azaḡa niduꞌa goruziro. Ze ibite duduḡa vazeḡa Abela mau runiroteꞌeanoꞌo onao ḡonagano Berekia ubuga Zekaria maro. Zekariaꞌe kuru neḡa zu dibuꞌo fataḡa boꞌaḡano mau runiro. ꞌOugadu eꞌe naeḡa niduꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa odohiꞌuma.
\v 36 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, eꞌe aduga niduꞌaꞌe izidi eganiꞌa odohiꞌuma.”
\s1 Ierusalema Aduga Hidiꞌuma
\r (Luka 13:34-35)
\p 
\v 37 “O, Ierusalema, Ierusalema, zaꞌa peroveta azaḡa zimiro zu Badiꞌaꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡa hadi hina zimi ruziro. Kokorokuꞌa isaḡa zamaḡano ubuga gugubeꞌeteꞌe teige, eḡeꞌa ḡae ḡehaḡa zae taufihi reiro, rehano zaꞌe mene uratinu!
\v 38 Ḡianoꞌi, neze fahadu haba bohaꞌa teigiꞌuma.
\v 39 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, za e mene bare horohiꞌuma, onamo zaeꞌa raenaꞌa, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune,'\x + \xo 23:39 \xt Salamo 118:26\x* rae reiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa meꞌuma.”
\c 24
\s1 Kuru Neḡa Fahe Ḡuzuhiteꞌe moneo Ḡoeriro
\r (Mareko 13:1-2; Luka 21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa kuru neḡanonoꞌo buau onamirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ani vaḡe aradu kuru neḡa habaꞌano ne iraḡa nunu ihoniro.
\v 2 ꞌOugadu aniꞌa ziro, “Za ḡau ꞌadi niduꞌa horoneꞌehe? Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, kuru neḡa ꞌadi fahe ḡuzuhadu hadini ꞌahoganiꞌa hadi ꞌahoga ranao mene radiꞌuma.”
\s1 Mada Ḡonagano Haḡai Nu Badeḡa
\r (Mareko 13:3-13; Luka 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Iesuꞌa Olivi Maḡano ehorirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe zeḡe daꞌo ani vaḡe sifu onamadu ḡadiniro, “Eꞌeguḡaniꞌa naniꞌa fureraꞌuma? Mada ḡonagano zu ḡaeꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡanoꞌe nagi haḡai nu badeḡaniꞌa ibite fureraꞌuma? Eme efoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 4 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa za mene soꞌosoꞌozifine tohutohoꞌi.
\v 5 Vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa eḡe niḡano aradu 'Eꞌe Keriso,' rae reꞌuma ebu vaze ḡehaḡa soꞌosoꞌoziꞌuma.
\v 6 Zaꞌe utiutiꞌa fureraroteꞌe hariḡa zu fureraꞌuma rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa nunu igiꞌuma, rehano zamazeꞌa ago ꞌadaꞌadazoꞌi. Eꞌeguḡaniꞌa hube hune ibite fureraꞌuma, rehano ꞌize mene mada ḡonaga.
\v 7 Haba ꞌahoganiꞌa haba ꞌahoga teite utitiꞌuma, zu gavamani ꞌahoganiꞌa gavamani ꞌahoga teite utitiꞌuma. Haba nunu zamaḡano zagaꞌa hiaꞌuma, zu habaꞌa borofe hagariꞌuma.
\v 8 Eꞌeguḡa niduꞌaꞌe ene ꞌizema fureranogano gigiꞌaniꞌa ḡadahe fureruꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.
\p 
\v 9 Ebu vazeꞌa za riꞌizadu sausauziꞌuma zu zimiꞌuma. Eḡe uꞌano, haba azaḡa niduꞌa zae heꞌeheꞌeziꞌuma.
\v 10 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌeꞌa dauḡiꞌuma, revotitiꞌuma zu heꞌeheꞌetitiꞌuma.
\v 11 Ebu ḡuriro peroveta azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa fureranadu vaze ḡehaḡa soꞌoziꞌuma.
\v 12 Vaze sauꞌaniꞌa ufeta bororuꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa zeḡe negoze nabudize mene zamare borofiꞌuma.
\v 13 Rehano iniu edau gigaru onamo ḡonaga meiteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡabone hidiꞌuma.
\v 14 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe hariḡa manoḡaꞌe raha ꞌadi niduꞌa zamaḡano haramadu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa mazao rae fureniꞌuma. Ebu hena mada ḡonaganiꞌa ariꞌuma.”
\s1 Aduga Boro Hune
\r (Mareko 13:14-23; Luka 21:20-24)
\p 
\v 15 “Ibite peroveta vazeḡa, Danielaꞌa ḡoeriroteꞌe teige, haba sausauneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa sauꞌa bagaḡaniꞌa\x + \xo 24:15 \xt Daniela 9:27, 11:31, 12:11\x* haba zaḡoḡano edauꞌeteꞌe zaꞌa horoniteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma (ꞌadi meꞌodeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, ḡoere huga ꞌadi faine ederoꞌi).
\v 16 Eꞌe madaḡano Iudea habaꞌano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe maḡa ferau itoꞌi.
\v 17 Iniuꞌa ne enogano\f + \fr 24:17 \fqa ne binu hitagano \f* radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡauḡa mouga veize ne zamaḡa ago diuḡoꞌi.
\v 18 Mebao hiheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zuni dabua mouga veize ago bare onamoꞌi.
\v 19 Eꞌe madaḡano ahiꞌeta roḡaeḡa ebu nune hina ene guraḡa ḡubuzeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡaꞌe feranoga mene idaḡa radu aduga boro hidiꞌuma!
\v 20 ꞌUguḡaniꞌa irugu madaḡano\f + \fr 24:20 \fqa nahune madaḡano. \ft Isaraela habaꞌano nahune madaḡaꞌe nahune boro zu irugu boro radu vazeꞌa ragavogaꞌe riḡa. \f* ga Bana Madaḡano mene fureranoga veize kuranoꞌi.
\v 21 Mazaḡa eꞌe madaḡano vaze niduꞌa aduga boro hune hidiꞌuma. Badiꞌaꞌa ḡadaheḡano ḡau niduꞌa haḡairoteꞌeanoꞌo onao izidi aduga ꞌuguḡaniꞌa mene fureraro, ebu vesuꞌu zuni mene bare fureraꞌuma.
\v 22 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa eꞌe madaḡa mene futufine, vazeni ꞌahoga zuni mene ḡabode radiꞌuma. Rehano ani aneꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa veize eꞌe madaḡa futufiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 23 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zinaꞌa, 'Ḡianoꞌi, Kerisoꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe!' ga 'Aniꞌe ꞌomo eꞌe!' rae zoꞌidene, ze ḡoere ago mae ḡihinoꞌi.
\v 24 Mazaḡa ḡuriro kerisoḡa zu ḡuriro perovetaḡa azaḡaniꞌa fureranadu haḡai nu badeḡa boro bagaḡa zu haḡai gigiꞌa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa, vaze soꞌoziꞌuma. Ze idaḡa reine, Badiꞌaꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa zuni soꞌoziꞌuma.
\v 25 Tohutohe radoꞌi. Eꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ꞌizema fureranogano eḡeꞌa ibite zae ihozeꞌohe.
\v 26 Eꞌanoꞌo vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zinaꞌa, 'Ḡianoꞌi, Kerisoꞌe haba bohaꞌano,' rae roꞌidene, ḡianihi radu ago onamoꞌi. Ga, 'Ḡianoꞌi, aniꞌe ne zamaḡano,' rae roꞌidene, eꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ago mae ḡihinoꞌi.
\v 27 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare arine, vaze niduꞌa huneꞌa horoniꞌuma. Aꞌe viriꞌa vazahadu madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo ovoeꞌeteꞌe moneo aganadu vaze niduꞌa tabara horoneꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.
\v 28 Naginiꞌa rudaroteꞌe habaꞌano gaozaꞌa nuꞌoraꞌuma.”
\s1 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa Ariꞌuma
\r (Mareko 13:24-27; Luka 21:25-28)
\p 
\v 29 “Aduga madaḡaniꞌa hauḡine,
\q1 'Zogone madaꞌa uzaboraꞌuma, batoꞌa mene agaraꞌuma,
\q1 buzuvaꞌa adureonoꞌo rururu buaꞌuma, ebu adure gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa hagahagariꞌuma.'\x + \xo 24:29 \xt Isaia 13:10, 34:4 \x*
\p 
\v 30 Eꞌe madaḡano Vaze Ubuganiꞌa ariteꞌe ihozeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa nu badeḡaniꞌa adureo fureraꞌuma, ebu raha ꞌadao habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa niau ḡouriꞌuma. Ebu ze Vaze Ubuganiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa boro zu agaḡa boro hune madu adureo ḡoze hina areꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma.
\v 31 Ebu bigoro ago boro zamaḡano aniꞌa ane tuḡure viga ḡehaḡa tuḡuziꞌuma, ebu zeḡeꞌa adure ḡonaga ꞌahaonoꞌo onamo adure ḡonaga ꞌomo, haba niduꞌa zamaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌoziꞌuma.”
\s1 Figi Ireḡa Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Mareko 13:28-31; Luka 21:29-33)
\p 
\v 32 “Figi ireḡa ḡianadu ꞌahi ederoꞌi. Ezaganiꞌa butiru itadu rouḡaniꞌa udufaꞌoga horoneꞌetene, zaꞌe edeḡa, irugu madaḡaniꞌa haniteha.
\v 33 Eꞌe teige, ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureranoga horonoꞌidene, Vaze Ubuganiꞌa zae ibihetao haniteha rae ederoꞌi.
\v 34 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, izidi egaꞌe mene hauḡiꞌuma, onamo ꞌahiguḡa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma.
\v 35 Adure zu rahaꞌe hauḡiꞌuma, rehano eḡe ḡoereꞌe mene hune hauḡiꞌuma.”
\s1 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa Ariteꞌe Madaḡa veize Ruhibe Radoꞌi
\r (Mareko 13:32-37; Luka 17:26-30, 34-36)
\p 
\v 36 “Rehano vazeni ꞌahoga zuni ꞌuguḡaniꞌa fureratiteꞌe madaḡaꞌe aḡuꞌa. Adureo tuḡure viga ebu Badiꞌa Ubuga zuni aḡuꞌa, rehano Moga daꞌo edeḡa.
\v 37 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe Noa madaḡa teigiꞌuma.
\v 38 Zobo boroꞌa ꞌizema zubuzogano, vaze niduꞌa iḡaiḡa haḡainuteꞌe teige ogaunu, gaginu zu hahurinu, onamo Noaꞌa ḡasi boro diuḡiro.
\v 39 Rehano ze naginiꞌa fureraꞌuma mene ederiro, onamo zobo boroꞌa zubuzadu hunuhune ḡouriro. Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe eꞌe madaḡa teigiꞌuma.
\v 40 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze aheuꞌa mebao gaue radiuꞌeteꞌea, ꞌahogaꞌe zamahanadu onamiꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe muhine iḡuniꞌuma.
\v 41 Roḡae aheuꞌe ꞌuvahu mirune radiuꞌeteꞌea, ꞌahogaꞌe zamahanadu onamiꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe muhine iḡuniꞌuma. \fig Roḡae aheuꞌa ꞌuvahu miruneꞌohe|src="41_Mat24:41_GrindingGrain" size="col" ref="24:41"\fig*
\p 
\v 42 Eꞌanoꞌo tohutohoꞌi, mazaḡa zaꞌe aḡuꞌa, noꞌe madaḡano zae Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ariꞌuma.
\v 43 ꞌAdi zamaroꞌi. Ḡonore vazeḡaniꞌa ohere noꞌe madaḡano aritaꞌaꞌe ne vazeḡaniꞌa ederifone, aniꞌe evate radiuꞌenaꞌa neḡa faine taufadu ḡonore vazeḡaniꞌa diuḡogaꞌe mene idarafo.
\v 44 Eꞌanoꞌo zae zuni ruhibe radoꞌi, mazaḡa Vaze Ubugaꞌe zaeꞌa mene zamareꞌeteꞌe madaḡano ariꞌuma.”
\s1 Tuḡure Azaḡa Aheu Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Luka 12:41-48)
\p 
\v 45 “Iniuꞌe vaze huhuzaḡa zu zamaḡa niduꞌa hina gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa? Tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe vaze ꞌuguḡa reine, zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa aniꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡano mae ohonadu ꞌahige rae niꞌuma, 'Tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa taufoꞌi. Ogomuze zuni mada idunane zenoꞌi.'
\v 46 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa ꞌouge gauine ebu zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa bare feuradu horonine, tuḡure vazeḡa aꞌe matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.
\v 47 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, aniꞌe zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa ane tohe niduꞌa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoniꞌuma.
\v 48 Rehano tuḡure vazeḡa aꞌe sauꞌa reine, ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige zamariꞌuma, 'Eḡe zuhiꞌaꞌe vesuꞌu faḡanobuꞌu ariꞌuma.'
\v 49 Ebu tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa bouziꞌuma zu gagone azaḡa teite ufeta ogau gage sautaꞌuma.
\v 50 Ebu aniꞌa mene zamareꞌeteꞌe zu mene edereꞌeteꞌe madaḡano zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa bare aradu,
\v 51 ani ahiri variꞌe tahitahiꞌuma ebu zama niduꞌa hina mene gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa habaꞌano ohonadu aduga boro haꞌuma. Eꞌea ani niaꞌuma zu ḡononeḡa atitiꞌuma.”
\c 25
\s1 Nogoba Gaubanana Hari Idaidaḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa bare reiro, “Eꞌe madaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe nogoba gaubanana teigiꞌuma. Ze ihureze madu hahu ohoze iziga hidoga veize onamiro.
\v 2 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano fuꞌoꞌe kauriḡa ebu fuꞌoꞌe huhuzaḡa.
\v 3 Nogoba kauriḡa fuꞌoꞌe ihureze odohiro, rehano ihure vuḡaꞌe mene meiro.
\v 4 U nogoba huhuzaḡa fuꞌoꞌe ihurezeta ihure vuḡa biozeo abe odohiro.
\v 5 Ebu hahu ohoze iziganiꞌa mene ḡarihe arirotene, ze ubumaze anozadu bazubazu uhiro.
\p 
\v 6 Ohere nemanema ze ago ꞌahoga igiro, 'Hahu ohoze iziganiꞌa feureha! Buanadu ani hidoꞌi!'
\v 7 ꞌOugirotene nogoba niduꞌa evatadu ihureze ruhibiro.
\v 8 Ebu nogoba kauriḡa fuꞌoꞌa nogoba huhuzaḡa fuꞌo umiziro, 'Za ihure vuḡa nuḡo eme rifoꞌi, mazaḡa eme ihureꞌe vidauꞌohe.'
\v 9 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeziro, 'Mene, 'ahiꞌe za zu emeḡe niduꞌa veize mene idaḡa. Ihure vuḡa seroneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa vaḡe onamadu zae veize nu hoitoꞌi.'
\v 10 Rehano ze ihureze vuḡa hoitoga uꞌa onamiroteꞌea, hahu ohoze iziganiꞌa feuriro. Ebu ihureze zu ihureze vuḡa ruhibiroteꞌe nogobaḡa fuꞌoꞌa ani teite mui habaꞌa diuḡiro ebu ibihetaḡaꞌe hararo.
\v 11 Vesuꞌu nogoba kauriḡa fuꞌoꞌa feuradu reiro, 'Vaze boro! Vaze boro! Ibiheta vavaofoꞌi!'
\v 12 Rehano aneꞌa naenaeziro, 'Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, e za aḡuꞌa.'
\p 
\v 13 Eꞌanoꞌo tohutohe radoꞌi, mazaḡa eḡeꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe zaꞌe aḡuꞌa.” \fig Nogoba gaubanana|src="lb00318b.tif" size="col" ref="25:1-13"\fig*
\s1 Tuḡure Azaḡa Uḡidu Hari Idaidaḡa
\r (Luka 19:11-27)
\p 
\v 14 “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe haba faḡa ragaveꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga heuḡa. Aniꞌa iḡunirotene, tuḡureḡa azaḡa ane ḡau niduꞌa zenadu faine taufoꞌi rae reiro.
\v 15 Zeḡe tibatiba inaraze idunaḡano, ꞌahogaꞌe hadi silivaḡa fuse\f + \fr 25:15 \fqa talanti. \ft Talanti tibaꞌe silivaḡa 34kg heuḡa. Aꞌe muri 16 gauḡa naeḡa heuḡa.\f* fuꞌo, ꞌahogaꞌe fuse aheu ebu ꞌahogaꞌe fuse tiba ziniro. Ebu aniꞌa haba faḡa ragaviro.
\p 
\v 16 Hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa fuꞌo meiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zogone onamadu eꞌe hadiḡa hina gauiro, ebu hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa fuꞌo ragate hidiro.
\v 17 Hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa aheu meiroteꞌe vazeḡa zuni ꞌouge haḡadu hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa aheu ragate hidiro.
\v 18 Rehano hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa tiba meiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe onamadu rahao idu huꞌiro, ebu zuhiꞌaḡa hadi eꞌea gure ꞌuꞌuru tiro.
\p 
\v 19 Mada faḡa ḡarugano tuḡure azaḡa zuhiꞌazeꞌa bariro. Ebu zeḡeꞌa ane hadi hina nougenouge gauiroteꞌe ederifine huziro.
\v 20 Hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa fuꞌo meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa hadi fuseḡa fuꞌo bare ragate hidirotaꞌaꞌe odohe aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaꞌa hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa fuꞌo iniro. Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa hadi eꞌe hina gauadu hadi fuseḡa fuꞌo ragate hidiro.'
\v 21 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa niro, 'Manoḡa tauḡi, ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa manoḡa zu zamaḡo niduꞌa hina gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa! Ḡaeꞌa gau komeꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina faine odohe gauiro ꞌahine, eḡeꞌa ḡau ḡehaḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma. Aroꞌi, zuhiꞌaḡo teite matuꞌihi.'
\v 22 Ebu hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa aheu meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaꞌa hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa aheu iniro. Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa hadi eꞌe hina gauadu hadi fuseḡa aheu ragate hidiro.'
\v 23 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa niro, 'Manoḡa tauḡi, ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa manoḡa zu zamaḡo niduꞌa hina gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa! Ḡaeꞌa gau komeꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina faine odohe gauiro ꞌahine, eḡeꞌa ḡau ḡehaḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma. Aroꞌi, zuhiꞌaḡo teite matuꞌihi.'
\p 
\v 24 Rehano hadi siliva fuseḡa tiba meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaꞌe vaze riḡa. E ederiro, vazeꞌa ḡoraroteꞌe ḡauḡa ḡaeꞌa hiriveꞌohe, ebu vazeꞌa feune ḡoraroteꞌe ezoneḡa ḡaeꞌa hirive nuꞌoneꞌohe.
\v 25 Eꞌanoꞌo e ḡa rihoꞌadu rahao gure tiro. Ḡae hadi ꞌahi bare moꞌi.'
\v 26 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa sauꞌa ebu tubuḡa! Ḡaꞌe vazeꞌa ḡoraroteꞌe ḡauḡa eḡeꞌa hiriveꞌohe ebu vazeꞌa feune ḡoraroteꞌe ezoneḡa eḡeꞌa hirive nuꞌoneꞌohe rae ederirohe?
\v 27 ꞌOugirotene, ḡa nougadu hadi tiꞌeteꞌe neḡano eḡe hadi mene tiro? ꞌOugifone, e bare aradu eḡe hadi ufeta ragate meifo.'
\p 
\v 28 Hena zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa tuḡure azaḡa ziro, 'Hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa tiba ani mazaonoꞌo bare madu hadi silivaḡa fuseḡa gaubanana meiroteꞌe vazeḡa hanoꞌi.
\v 29 Iniuꞌa nagini hidiroteꞌe faine odohe gauine, ani bare ufeta borofe hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa nagini hidiroteꞌe mene faine odohe gauine, ani mazao nagini komeꞌa zuni meiniꞌuma.
\v 30 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌadiꞌe eḡe veize mene faine gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahine, enona uzabo zamaḡano mae feunoꞌi. Eꞌea ani niaꞌuma ebu ḡonoga atitiꞌuma.'”
\s1 Badiꞌa Kota Ḡonaga
\p 
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa reiro, “Vaze Ubuganiꞌa niḡa mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa, tuḡure viga niduꞌa teite arine, aniꞌe ane ehoro habaꞌa, kini ehoro habaꞌa ḡihiꞌaḡano ehoriꞌuma.
\v 32 Aniꞌa habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa ane zamao nuꞌozadu mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa mamoeꞌe gouti mazaonoꞌo rovozeꞌeteꞌe teige, ze rovoziꞌuma.
\v 33 Ebu iniu vaze mamoe heuḡaꞌe ane edaꞌe moneo zu iniu vaze gouti heuḡaꞌe ane kauri moneo ohoziꞌuma.
\p 
\v 34 Ebu hena kinizeꞌa edaꞌe mone azaḡa ziꞌuma, 'Zaꞌe eḡe Mama mazaonoꞌo manohuga meiroteꞌe azaḡa. Aroꞌi ebu eḡeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano radoꞌi. Eꞌe habaꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ḡau niduꞌa haḡairoteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo ruhiniro.
\v 35 Mazaḡa e vinihirotene zaeꞌa ogomu inido, zu e irinehe moꞌohirotene zaeꞌa vu inido, ebu e iꞌudo vazeḡa reirotene zaeꞌa zae neo huhe zouhido.
\v 36 Dabuahe oꞌoꞌa reirotene zaeꞌa dabua inido, zu e ugihirotene zaeꞌa eḡe taufido, ebu e ḡuꞌa neḡano radirotene zaeꞌa ḡiahi ariro.'
\p 
\v 37 Ebu duduḡa azaḡaniꞌa naenaeniꞌuma, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme naniꞌa ḡaꞌe viniꞌiroteꞌe horo'adu ogomu ḡanido? Naniꞌa eme ḡaꞌe irigo moꞌoꞌiroteꞌe horoꞌadu vu ḡanido?
\v 38 Naniꞌa eme ḡaꞌe iꞌudo vazeḡa reiroteꞌe horoꞌadu neo huḡade zouꞌido? Naniꞌa eme dabuaḡo ꞌoꞌoꞌa reiroteꞌe horoꞌadu dabua ḡanido?
\v 39 Naniꞌa eme ḡa ugiꞌiroteꞌe ga ḡuꞌa neḡano radiroteꞌe horoꞌadu ḡa ḡiaꞌi amido?'
\v 40 Ebu kinizeꞌa naenaeziꞌuma, 'Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zaeꞌa eḡe nego nabudi ꞌahi boꞌaḡano ḡonaga vazeḡa ꞌahoga veize ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe eḡe veize haḡairoteꞌe heuḡa.'
\p 
\v 41 Ebu kinizeꞌa vaetadu kauri mone azaḡa ziꞌuma, 'Zaꞌe aduga tuḡutuḡu meiroteꞌe azaḡa, eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi, ebu Satani zu ane tuḡure viga niduꞌa veize ruhiniroteꞌe ire rogaḡa radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡa diuḡoꞌi.
\v 42 Mazaḡa e vinihirotene zaeꞌa ogomu mene inido, zu e irinehe moꞌohirotene zaeꞌa vu mene inido.
\v 43 E iꞌudo vazeḡa reirotene zaeꞌa neo mene huhe zouhido, zu e dabuahe oꞌoꞌa reirotene zaeꞌa dabua mene inido, ebu e ugihirotene zu ḡuꞌa neḡano radirotene, zaeꞌa e mene taufido.'
\p 
\v 44 ꞌOugadu zeꞌa naenaeniꞌuma, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, naniꞌa eme ḡaꞌe viniꞌiroteꞌe ga irigo moꞌoꞌiroteꞌe ga iꞌudo vazeḡa reiroteꞌe ga dabuaḡo ꞌoꞌoꞌa reiroteꞌe ga ugiꞌiroteꞌe ga ḡuꞌa neḡano radiroteꞌe horoꞌadu mene danaꞌido?'
\v 45 Ebu kinizeꞌa naenaeziꞌuma, 'Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, ꞌahi azaḡa boꞌaḡano ḡonaga vazeḡa ꞌahoga veize mene haḡairotaꞌaꞌe eḡe veize mene haḡairoteꞌe heuḡa.'
\v 46 Eꞌanoꞌo kauri mone azaḡaꞌe aduga tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma, u duduḡa azaḡaꞌe ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.”
\c 26
\s1 Iesu Manoga veize Ḡoꞌaniro
\r (Mareko 14:1-2; Luka 22:1-2; Ioane 11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ḡoere eꞌe niduꞌa rae hauḡirotene, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro,
\v 2 “Zaꞌe edeḡa, mada aheu enogano Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa meꞌuma ebu Vaze Ubugaꞌe satauronoga veize agire ꞌevora riꞌiniꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 3 Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa, niḡa Kaiafa neo nuꞌoraro.
\v 4 Ebu ze Iesu soꞌonadu obone teadu manoga veize ibiḡa ḡoꞌane vaḡiro.
\v 5 Rehano ze zeḡeꞌa bare reiro, “Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡanoꞌe mene idaḡa, mazaḡa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa utitofiꞌuma.”
\s1 Roḡae ꞌAhoganiꞌa Dehoro Hohoḡa Iesu rana Beuꞌiro
\r (Mareko 14:3-9; Ioane 12:1-8)
\p 
\v 6 Iesuꞌe Betania neḡano ibite referaꞌa meiroteꞌe vazeḡa, niḡa Simona neo radiunu.
\v 7 Aniꞌa ogomu fataḡa zamao tave ehoreꞌenaꞌa ogauꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa dehoro hohoḡa manoḡa naeḡa boroꞌe bioḡa komeꞌa manohuga iriꞌavonadu mae ariro, ebu Iesu vadinio beuꞌiro.
\v 8 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa eꞌe horonirotene, ze maḡune rudaro ebu niro, “Nougadu dehoro hohoḡa ꞌahiꞌe mode hauḡeha?
\v 9 Aꞌe hadi boro hina seronadu zahara azaḡa zinifo.”
\p 
\v 10 Iesuꞌa eꞌe horonadu ziro, “Za nougadu roḡae ꞌadi aduga hauꞌohe? Aniꞌe eḡe veize manohuga haḡaeha.
\v 11 Zahara azaḡaꞌe iḡaiḡa zae teite radiꞌuma, u eꞌe iḡaiḡa zae teite mene radiꞌuma.
\v 12 Aniꞌe eḡeꞌa rudanadu guriteꞌe madaḡa ruhiboga veize dehoro hohoḡa eḡe ahiri rana beuꞌeha.
\v 13 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, raha niduꞌa zamaḡano noꞌe habaꞌano hari manoḡa haramine, aniꞌa haḡateꞌe haḡaiḡa ꞌahi meꞌodadu ani zamariꞌuma.”
\s1 Iudaꞌa Iesu Revohaꞌuma rae Ḡoitoriro
\r (Mareko 14:10-11; Luka 22:3-6)
\p 
\v 14 Eꞌe enogano Iesu tahiꞌaḡa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga, Isakariota vazeḡa Iudaꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa vaḡe onamiro,
\v 15 ebu ḡadiziro, “E Iesu zae ꞌevoreo riꞌinine, za nagini iniꞌuma?” ꞌOugirotene ze hadi silivaḡa 30 meꞌodadu haro.
\v 16 Eꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo aniꞌa Iesu zeḡe ꞌevoreo riꞌinoga veize mada manoḡa ꞌahoga vaḡiro.
\s1 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa Ogomuḡa Aro
\r (Mareko 14:12-21; Luka 22:7-14, 21-23; Ioane 13:21-30)
\p 
\v 17 Isiti Oꞌoꞌa ꞌUvahuḡa Odoga Muiḡa zamaḡano mada ibiꞌaꞌe Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa. Eꞌe madaḡa meirotene, Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe aradu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa urao eme Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ogomuḡaꞌe nouma ruhibe tiꞌuma?”
\v 18 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Ne boro diuḡadu vaze ꞌahoga vaḡoꞌi ebu noꞌi, 'Ihore vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe: Eḡe mada ꞌai haniteha. E eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ḡae neo Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ogomuḡa au tiburaꞌuma.'”
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe Iesuꞌa ziroteꞌe idunaḡano Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ruhibe tiro.
\p 
\v 20 Ḡoravararotene, Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare teite ogomu fataḡa babaḡano ehoriro.
\v 21 Ebu ze ogauꞌeteꞌea Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe revoniꞌuma.”
\v 22 Ebu ze zamaze adudanadu zeḡezeḡeꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eꞌe mene, ineo?”
\v 23 Aneꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe teite idaḡa siuvao ꞌevoꞌa tare auꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa revoniꞌuma.
\v 24 Vaze Ubuga moneo Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌe idunaḡano Vaze Ubuganiꞌa rudaꞌuma. Rehano ani revohatiteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma. Aniꞌe mene furerafone ufeta manoḡa reifo.”
\v 25 Ebu ani revohatiteꞌe vazeḡa, Iudaꞌa niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eꞌe mene, ineo?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Aꞌe ḡae.”
\s1 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Ogomu Ḡonaga Aro
\r (Mareko 14:22-26; Luka 22:15-20; 1Korinto 11:23-25)
\p 
\v 26 Ze ogauꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, Iesuꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga madu kuraro ebu vahegadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziniro. Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “ꞌAdi madu anoꞌi. ꞌAdiꞌe eḡe ahiri.”
\v 27 Ebu aniꞌa vaini vuḡa bioḡa madu kuraroteꞌe ḡarugano ziniro. Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Zae niduꞌa, ꞌahi gagoꞌi.
\v 28 Vaini vuḡa bioḡa ꞌadiꞌe eḡe ru. Aꞌe eḡeꞌa vaze ḡehaḡa haḡaize sauꞌa rae modoga veize ruhe beꞌunadu ohoneꞌeteꞌe ḡoitore ḡoeꞌa.
\v 29 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, eꞌe vaini vuḡa mene bare gagiꞌuma, onamo eḡe Mamaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡano zae teite vaini vuḡa iziga gagiꞌuma.”
\v 30 Ebu ze bada ꞌahoga mae hauḡadu Olivi Maḡa onamiro.
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniꞌuma rae Reiro
\r (Mareko 14:27-31; Luka 22:31-34; Ioane 13:36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Izidi ohere zae niduꞌa eḡe muhihe feraꞌuma. Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,
\q1 'Badiꞌaꞌa mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mau runiꞌuma,
\q2 ebu mamoeḡaꞌe ferau ḡouriꞌuma.'\x + \xo 26:31 \xt Zekaria 13:7\x*
\m 
\v 32 Rehano eḡeꞌa runeonoꞌo bare ḡaboditeꞌe enogano zae zamao Galilea habaꞌa onamiꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 33 Peteroꞌa Iesu niro, “Vaze niduꞌa ferau muhiꞌiꞌuma rehano, eꞌe mene hune ferau muhiꞌiꞌuma!”
\v 34 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ḡaꞌohe, izidi ohere ꞌizema kokorokuꞌa uganogano ḡaeꞌa ḡae uḡidu eḡe oꞌohiꞌuma.”
\v 35 Rehano Peteroꞌa niro, “E mene oꞌoꞌiꞌuma. Ḡae teite rudaune zuni idaḡa!” Ebu ane tahiꞌaḡa niduꞌa zuni ꞌouge reiro.
\s1 Getesemane Habaꞌano Kuraro
\r (Mareko 14:32-42; Luka 22:39-46)
\p 
\v 36 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite haba ꞌahoga, niḡa Getesemane onamadu ziro, “ꞌAda ehore radoꞌi, u eꞌe kuranoga veize ꞌomo onamiꞌuma.”
\v 37 Ebu aniꞌe Petero ebu Zebedeo ubuga aheu, Iakobo zu Ioane tutuze onamiro. Ani zamaḡa ḡadahe ariro zu adudaro.
\v 38 ꞌOugadu aniꞌa ziro, “Zamahe are rudauꞌohe. Zaꞌe ꞌada radadu eḡe teite evate radoꞌi.”
\v 39 Ebu ani tahiḡa faḡa onamiro zu rahao ḡuḡuradu kuraro, “Eḡe Mama, ḡa idaḡa roꞌidene, eḡe mazaonoꞌo bio aduga ꞌadi mae vaḡinoꞌi. Rehano eḡe mene urao, ḡae urao daꞌo haḡaoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 40 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe bare arirotene, ze bazeꞌeteꞌe horoziro. Ebu aniꞌa Petero niro, “Za mada tahiḡa zuni eḡe teite evate radoga mene idaḡahe?
\v 41 Sataniꞌa tuhuzadu zaeꞌa mene uitifine tohutohoꞌi zu kuranoꞌi. Zamazeꞌe urateꞌohe, rehano ahirizeꞌe taoḡa.”
\p 
\v 42 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare onamadu ḡae aheuḡano kuraro, “Eḡe Mama, e bio ꞌahi hube hune gage huniꞌuma roꞌidene, ḡae ura haḡaoꞌi.”
\v 43 Aniꞌa bare arirotene, ze bare bazeꞌeteꞌe horoziro, mazaḡa ubumazeꞌa ufeta anoziro.
\p 
\v 44 Aniꞌa ze muhizadu bare onamiro ebu ibite kuraroteꞌe teige ḡae uḡiduḡano bare kuraro.
\v 45 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe bare aradu ziro, “Za ꞌize bazeꞌehe zu ahirize ohoneꞌehe? Ḡiꞌanoꞌi, madaḡa ꞌai maha, ebu Vaze Ubugaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniꞌuma.
\v 46 Iḡunadu onamihi. Ḡianoꞌi, eḡe revoniteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌai feureha.”
\s1 Iesu Obone Tiro
\r (Mareko 14:43-50; Luka 22:47-53; Ioane 18:3-12)
\p 
\v 47 Iesuꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga, Iudaꞌa feuriro. Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡa ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa benisi zu somori boro madu Iuda teite ariro.
\v 48 Ebu Iesu revoharoteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aneꞌa nougenouge haḡaiteꞌe moneo ibite ihoziro, “Eḡeꞌa furaꞌiniteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iesu. Ani obone toꞌi.”
\v 49 Ebu aniꞌa zogone Iesu vaḡe onamadu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa! Manoḡahe?” Ebu aniꞌa furaꞌiniro.
\v 50 Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe vaze, ḡa ꞌahao nagini haḡaiteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaoꞌi.”
\p Ebu Iuda teite ariroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa onamadu Iesu obone tiro.
\v 51 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu ḡati vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa benisiḡa ahase bunadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa tuḡure vazeḡa udirotene teḡaḡa variꞌe butiro.
\v 52 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa niro, “Benisiḡo bare iḡuꞌano ofoꞌi! Benisi hina vaze matihi raꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡe zuni benisi uꞌano rudaꞌuma.
\v 53 Eḡeꞌa Mamahe uminine, aneꞌa tuḡure viga ḡehaḡa bagaḡa zogone tuḡuzadu emeḡe biriꞌuma. Za eḡeꞌa ꞌouge uminoga idaḡa rae mene zamareꞌehe?
\v 54 Rehano e ꞌougine, Buka Zaḡoḡano eḡe mazao ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureraꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa mene hudaꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 55 Ebu Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ziro, “Zaꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa obone tiꞌeteꞌe teige, benisi ebu somori boro madu eḡe obohe touga veize arahe? Mada niduꞌa eꞌe kuru neḡa habaꞌano ihore radiunu. Eꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe mene obohe tiro.
\v 56 Rehano peroveta azaḡaniꞌa mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudafine ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureraneha.” ꞌOugirotene ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa niduꞌaꞌe Iesu muhine feraro.
\s1 Iesuꞌe Kotao Ohoniro
\r (Mareko 14:53-65; Luka 22:54-55, 63-71; Ioane 18:12-14, 19-24)
\p 
\v 57 Ebu Iesu obone tiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa Kaiafa vaḡe tutune onamiro. Eꞌea Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa nuꞌoranadu radiunu.
\v 58 U Peteroꞌe faḡanonoꞌo Iesu hegotadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ne habaꞌano feuriro. Ebu naginiꞌa fureratiteꞌe ḡianoga veize ne habaꞌa diuḡadu eꞌe neḡa ḡianeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite ehoriro.
\p 
\v 59 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo boro azaḡaniꞌa Iesu manoga veize ani moneo ḡuriro ḡoeꞌaḡoeꞌa vaḡiro.
\v 60 Ebu vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa aradu Iesu moneo ḡuriro ḡoeꞌa rae fureniro, rehano ze ani veꞌoḡaꞌe mene horoniro. Ḡonagano vaze aheuꞌa iḡune edaro.
\v 61 Ebu ze ꞌahige rae fureniro, “Vaze ꞌadaꞌa raenaꞌa, 'Eḡeꞌa Badiꞌa kuru neḡa fahadu mada uḡidu zamaḡano bare ogoranogaꞌe idaḡa,' rae reiro.”
\v 62 ꞌOuge reirotene, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa edau iḡunadu Iesu niro, “Zeꞌa ḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureneꞌohe. Ḡa zeḡe ḡoere mene naenaeniꞌumahe?”
\v 63 Rehano Iesuꞌe sifu radiro. Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa niro, “E ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa niḡano riḡa ḡadimuꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe Keriso, Badiꞌa Ubuga ga mene? Efoꞌi.”
\v 64 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe, ḡaeꞌa eꞌe Keriso rae raha. Rehano eḡeꞌa zae niduꞌa ziꞌohe, zama moneo Vaze Ubugaꞌe Gigiꞌa Boro Badiꞌaḡa edaꞌe moneo ehoradu zuhiꞌaziteꞌe zu adureo ḡoze hina ariteꞌe horoniꞌuma.”
\p 
\v 65 ꞌOuge reirotene, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa dabuaḡa zegadu ziro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe Badiꞌa rae sausauneha! Eme aniꞌe veꞌoḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa bare vaḡiꞌumahe? Izidi aniꞌa Badiꞌa rae sausaunateꞌe zae niduꞌa egeha.
\v 66 Zaꞌe nouge rae zamareꞌohe?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Ani runeo tuḡuniꞌuma!”
\v 67 Ebu zeꞌa Iesu iraḡa rana soꞌabide vaniro zu ꞌevoreze hina bouniro. Vaze nuꞌa ubumaḡa dabua hina ꞌuadu faꞌone arahiro,
\v 68 “Keriso, efoꞌi. Iniuꞌa faꞌoꞌeha?”
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniro
\r (Mareko 14:66-72; Luka 22:56-62; Ioane 18:15-18, 25-27)
\p 
\v 69 Ebu Peteroꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ne habaꞌano ehore radiroteꞌea, tuḡure roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ane uꞌa aradu niro, “Ḡae zuni Galilea vazeḡa Iesu teite radiunu.”
\v 70 Rehano Peteroꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa zamao oꞌoniro, “E ḡaꞌa nagini raꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.”
\p 
\v 71 Ebu Peteroꞌa ne ḡabiriḡa ibihetaḡa uꞌa onamirotene, tuḡure roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa horonadu eꞌea radiunuteꞌe azaḡa ziro, “ꞌAdiꞌe Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu teite radiunu.”
\v 72 Ebu Peteroꞌa bare oꞌonadu ḡoere rinede tiro, “Eꞌe vaze aꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa!”
\p 
\v 73 Mada tahiḡa enogano eꞌea edau radiunuteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Petero vaḡe aradu niro, “Hube hune ḡa zu Iesu duḡuru boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga, mazaḡa ḡae ago iraḡaꞌe Galilea habaꞌa ago iraḡa.”
\v 74 Ebu ani ḡoere rinede teadu reiro, “E ḡuririne aduga hidiꞌuma! E vaze aꞌe aḡuꞌa!”
\p Ani Ꞌouge reirotene, kokorokuꞌa ugaro.
\v 75 Ebu Peteroꞌe Iesuꞌa ꞌahige rae niroteꞌe zamariro, “Kokorokuꞌa ꞌizema uganogano ḡaeꞌa eḡe ḡae uḡidu oꞌohiꞌuma.” Ebu aniꞌa ne enogano buanadu niau rudaro.
\c 27
\s1 Iesuꞌe Pilato Vaḡe Tutune Onamiro
\r (Mareko 15:1; Luka 23:1-2; Ioane 18:28-32)
\p 
\v 1 Oherebau uzeuze dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa nuꞌoranadu Iesu manoga veize ḡoere idaniro.
\v 2 Ze ani autadu Roma gavana vazeḡa Pilato vaḡe tutune onamiro ebu ane ꞌevora riꞌiniro.
\s1 Iudaꞌa Ane Bare Bodaniro
\r (Apostolo 1:18-19)
\p 
\v 3 Iesu revoharoteꞌe vazeḡa Iudaꞌa Iesuꞌe runeo tuḡuniꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa igirotene, ani haḡaiḡa sauꞌa uꞌano aneꞌa bare zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro. Eꞌanoꞌo siliva hadiḡa 30 madu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboro bare ziniro.
\v 4 Ebu aneꞌa ziro, “E haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeha, mazaḡa eḡeꞌa haḡai sauꞌa oꞌoꞌa vazeḡa revohanadu ani runeo tuḡuneha.” ꞌOugadu zeḡeꞌa niro, “Aꞌe emeḡeꞌa mene haḡaeha, rehano ḡaeꞌa bare haḡaeha. Ḡae edeḡano haḡaoꞌi.”
\v 5 ꞌOugirotene, Iudaꞌa kuru neḡa zamaḡano hadiḡa feuniro ebu onamadu aneꞌa bare bodane runiro.
\p 
\v 6 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa hadiḡa madu reiro, “Hadi ꞌadiꞌe vaze matihi radu haroteꞌe hadiḡa ꞌahine, kuru neḡa hadiḡa teite tibune tougaꞌe mene idaḡa.”
\v 7 Zeḡeꞌa ꞌouge ḡoꞌaniroteꞌe enogano, eꞌe hadiḡa hina ḡoḡore haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa haba ꞌahoga hoitadu eꞌe habaꞌano avoꞌa azaḡa guriꞌuma rae reiro.
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo haba aꞌe Ru Habaꞌa rae hunadu izidi zuni deꞌuge rae huneꞌohe.
\v 9 ꞌOugadu Badiꞌaꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Ieremiaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaro, “Zeḡeꞌa siliva hadiḡa 30 meiro. Aꞌe Isaraela azaḡaniꞌa vaze eꞌe naeḡa rae ohoniroteꞌe hadiḡa.
\v 10 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ihiroteꞌe teige, zeꞌa hadi eꞌe hina ḡoḡore haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa haba hoitiro.”\x + \xo 27:9-10 \xt Zekaria 11:12-13; Ieremia 19:1-13, 32:6-9 \x*
\s1 Iesuꞌe Pilato zamao Kotaniro
\r (Mareko 15:2-5; Luka 23:3-5; Ioane 18:33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Ebu Iesuꞌe Roma gavana vazeḡa Pilato zamao edau radiro. Ebu Pilatoꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa kinihe?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe, ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare eꞌe kini rae raha.”
\v 12 Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa Iesuꞌe veꞌoḡa rae riḡa ḡoerirotene, Iesuꞌe mene naenaeziro.
\v 13 Hena Pilatoꞌa ḡadiniro, “Zeꞌa ḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ḡehaḡa rae fureneꞌohe. Ḡa mene igiꞌehe?”
\v 14 Rehano Iesuꞌa zeḡe ḡoere tiba zuni mene naenaeziro. ꞌOugadu Pilatoꞌa zaguzagau huniro.
\s1 Iesu Runeo Tuḡuniꞌuma Reiro
\r (Mareko 15:6-15; Luka 23:13-25; Ioane 18:39-19:16)
\p 
\v 15 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡano Roma gavana vazeḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡaniꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe ḡuꞌa vazeḡa ꞌahoga tuḡune bunido.
\v 16 Eꞌe madaḡano ḡuꞌa neḡano vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Barabasiꞌa radiunu. Vaze niduꞌa ani ederiro.
\v 17 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa nuꞌorarotene, Pilatoꞌa ḡadiziro, “Za uraꞌe eḡeꞌa iniu tuḡune buniꞌuma, Barabasi ga Keriso raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa Iesu?”
\v 18 Mazaḡa Pilatoꞌe zeꞌa Iesu ahiahiniroteꞌe uꞌano, ani riꞌinirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.
\p 
\v 19 Pilatoꞌa kota habaꞌano ehorinuteꞌe zamaḡano inuganiꞌa ani veize ḡoere tuḡuriro, “Ḡa veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa vazeḡa eꞌe mazao haḡai sauꞌa ꞌahoga ago haḡaoꞌi. Eꞌe ohoḡore ohere iḡunao ani uꞌano zamaheꞌa ufeta adudaneha.”
\p 
\v 20 Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa Barabasi tuḡune bunadu Iesu manoga veize vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Pilato uminoga tuḡutuḡuziro.
\v 21 Pilatoꞌa ḡadiziro, “Vaze aheu boꞌaḡano zaꞌe eḡeꞌa iniu tuḡune bunoga urateꞌohe?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Barabasi!”
\v 22 Ebu Pilatoꞌa ḡadiziro, “Tena e Keriso raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa Iesu mazaoꞌe nougiꞌuma?” Zeḡe niduꞌa niro, “Aniꞌe Satauronoꞌi!”
\v 23 Pilatoꞌa ḡadiziro, “Nougadu? Ani haḡai sauꞌa nagiga haḡairo?” Rehano zeḡeꞌa ufeta ḡihau huaro, “Satauronoꞌi!”
\p 
\v 24 Pilatoꞌe Iesu veize gauni ꞌahoga haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa reirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro. Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ufeta maḡune haraeꞌeteꞌe horonirotene, zeḡe ubumao vu tahiḡa madu ꞌevoꞌa vuzuꞌiro ebu ziro, “E vaze ꞌahaꞌa rudatiteꞌe moneo veꞌoḡa ꞌahoga mene haḡaeha. Zae daꞌo eꞌe naeḡa moꞌi.”
\v 25 ꞌOugadu vaze niduꞌa naenaeniro, “Ani rudaune, eꞌe naeḡaꞌe emeḡe zu marigafeꞌa meꞌuma!”
\v 26 Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌe zeḡe veize Barabasi ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo tuḡune buniro, rehano Iesuꞌe masiniroteꞌe enogano satauronoga veize uti azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniro.
\s1 Uti Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Ḡirihoharo
\r (Mareko 15:16-20; Ioane 19:2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Gavana uti azaḡa nuꞌa Iesuꞌe gavana ne zamaḡa tutune onamiro, ebu uti azaḡa niduꞌa ani zamao huze nuꞌoziro.
\v 28 Ebu ze Iesu dabua fuhiꞌohanadu dabua kanaḡa duhuḡa hune vidoharo.
\v 29 Ebu ire ezaga meigameiga ḡurunadu kini vadiga adiriḡa teige vadigano redoharo, zu Gubu somoriḡa edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌano obonoharo. Ebu obenaze hina ani mazao ḡuḡureꞌenaꞌa ḡirihoharo, “Iuda azaḡa kini, nigunihi!”
\v 30 Ebu ze ani rana soꞌabide vaniro zu Gubu somoriḡa eꞌe madu vadiga rana barebare bouniro.
\v 31 Ḡirihohau hauḡirotene, ani vidoharoteꞌe dabuaḡa fuhiꞌadu ane dabua bare vidoharo. Ebu satauronoga radu tutune onamiro.
\s1 Iesu Satauroniro
\r (Mareko 15:21-32; Luka 23:26-43; Ioane 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu tutune onamiroteꞌe zamaḡano Kurene vazeḡa ꞌahoga, niḡa Simona hidiro, ebu aniꞌa Iesu satauro herate onamoga veize tuḡutuḡuniro.
\v 33 Ebu ze Gologota rae huneꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano feuriro (Gologota hugaꞌe Vadini Isiga Haba'a).
\v 34 Eꞌea ze vaini vuḡa ḡau ꞌahoga ḡiḡiꞌa bagaḡa teite mirunadu gagoharo. Rehano aneꞌa tahiḡa gage nuradu gagoga mene uratiro.
\p 
\v 35 Zeḡeꞌa Iesu satauroniroteꞌe ḡarugano kaḡusi arahoḡa arahadu Iesu dabua ḡahugotitiro.
\v 36 Ebu eꞌea ze ehoradu Iesu ḡiane radiro.
\v 37 Ze Iesu haḡai sauꞌaꞌe nagini rae ihozifine ane satauro hitagano ꞌahige mirihadu tiro, “ꞌADIꞌE IESU, IUDA AZAḠ KINI.”
\v 38 Ebu ḡonore azaḡa aheu zuni ani teite satauroziro. ꞌAhogaꞌe ane edaꞌe moneo zu ꞌahogaꞌe ane kauri moneo ikokoziro.
\p 
\v 39 Ebu uhiḡano vitau onamiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa vadinize miruneꞌenaꞌa, Iesu rae sausauniro,
\v 40 “Ḡaꞌe kuru neḡa fahadu mada uḡidu zamaḡano bare ohoniꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡa. Ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare ḡaboꞌoꞌi! Ḡa Badiꞌa Ubuga roꞌidene, satauronoꞌo buau ovaoꞌi!”
\v 41 Eꞌe teige, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa zuni ḡirihohauꞌenaꞌa ḡoeriro,
\v 42 “Aniꞌa vaze nunu ḡaboziro, rehano ani aneꞌa bare ḡabonogaꞌe mene idaḡa! Aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa kini, eꞌanoꞌo izidi hune satauronoꞌo bua ovaoꞌi, ꞌougine eme ani mazao fiꞌuma!
\v 43 Aniꞌe Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa uratine izidi ani ḡaboniꞌuma, mazaḡa aneꞌa raenaꞌa, 'E Badiꞌa Ubuga,' rae reiro.”
\v 44 Zeḡe teige, Iesu teite idaḡa satauroziroteꞌe ḡonore azaḡaniꞌa zuni ani rae sausauniro.
\s1 Iesu Rune
\r (Mareko 15:33-41; Luka 23:44-49; Ioane 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 45 Madai kirikiri meirotene, haba niduꞌa uzaboꞌa ꞌuiro, onamo ḡorava mone mada uḡidu.
\v 46 Ḡorava madaḡa uḡidu meirotene, Iesuꞌa ḡihau huaro, “Eli, Eli, lama sabatani?” Ḡoere eꞌe hugaꞌe, “Eḡe Badiꞌa, eḡe Badiꞌa, ḡa nougadu eḡe modeha?”\x + \xo 27:46 \xt Salamo 22:1\x*
\v 47 Eꞌea edau radiroteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano nuꞌe ḡoere eꞌe egadu reiro, “Aniꞌa Elia huneꞌohe.”
\v 48 Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa zogone dure onamadu vu romane zouneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa meiro, ebu vaini vuḡa ḡiḡiꞌa iriꞌavonadu Gubu somoriḡa rana tiro, ebu Iesu gagoharo.
\v 49 Rehano vaze nuꞌe reiro, “Ani modoꞌi. Eliaꞌa ovadu ḡaboniꞌuma ga mene, ḡianihi.”
\p 
\v 50 Ebu Iesuꞌa agoḡa boro hina bare ḡihau huanadu iriga riꞌiro.
\v 51 Eꞌe madaḡano kuru neḡano Haba Zaḡoḡa Hune ꞌueꞌeteꞌe dabuaḡaniꞌa hitaganonoꞌo ꞌuꞌuḡa ḡuzu zigau ꞌaꞌadaro. Ebu rahaꞌa hagariro zu vatavaꞌa ꞌaꞌadanadu bohatu ḡouriro.
\v 52 Ebu rune iduḡa ꞌaꞌadanadu Badiꞌa mone azaḡa ḡehaḡa ahirizeꞌa ḡabode iḡune ḡouriro.
\v 53 Ze iduzeonoꞌo buaro, ebu Iesuꞌa bare ḡabodiroteꞌe enogano Ierusalema onamadu vaze ḡehaḡa zamao fureraro. \fig Haba Zaḡoḡa Hune ꞌueꞌeteꞌe dabuaḡaniꞌa zigau ꞌaꞌadaro|src="41_Mat27:51_TempleCurtainTorn" size="col" ref="27:51"\fig*
\p 
\v 54 Uti vazeḡa boro zu ane teite Iesu ḡiane radiroteꞌe uti azaḡaꞌe rahaꞌa hagariroteꞌe zu naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe horonirotene, rihau rudanadu reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe hube hune Badiꞌa Ubuga!”
\v 55 Eꞌea roḡae ḡehaḡaniꞌa zuni faḡanonoꞌo ehamu radiro. Zeꞌe Iesu dananoga veize Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo hegote ariro.
\v 56 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano Magadala roḡaeḡa Maria, ebu Iakobo zu Iosefa vize Maria, ebu Zebedeo ubugaubuga Iakobo zu Ioane vizeꞌa radiunu.
\s1 Iesu Guriro
\r (Mareko 15:42-47; Luka 23:50-56; Ioane 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Ḡoravararotene, maꞌora vazeḡa, niḡa Iosefaꞌa ariro. Aniꞌe Arimate vazeḡa zu Iesu tahiꞌa ꞌahoga.
\v 58 Aniꞌa Pilato vaḡe onamadu Iesu ahiri mouga veize uminiro, ebu Pilatoꞌa ḡoere tuḡuradu Iesu ahiri haro.
\v 59 ꞌOugadu Iosefaꞌa Iesu ahiri madu dabua deheḡa manoḡa hina ꞌumiro.
\v 60 Ebu vatava huꞌiroteꞌe iduḡa, Iosefa ane rune iduḡa iziga zamaḡano Iesu ahiri tiro. Ebu hadi boro hina ibihetaḡano kiune ꞌuadu mode onamiro.
\v 61 U Magadala roḡaeḡa Maria zu Maria ꞌahogaꞌe iduḡa zama ḡoha ehore radiro.
\s1 Uti Azaḡaniꞌa Idu Habaꞌa Ḡiane Radiro
\p 
\v 62 Irarirotene, aꞌe Bana Madaḡa. Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Pilato vaḡe onamiro.
\v 63 Ebu ze Pilato niro, “Vaze boro, ḡuriro vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa ꞌize ḡabode radiroteꞌe zamaḡano reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa emeꞌa zamareꞌohe. Aniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'E mada uḡiduḡano bare ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma.'
\v 64 Eꞌanoꞌo mada uḡidu zamaḡano uti azaḡaniꞌa ani idu faine ḡianoga veize eme umiꞌeꞌohe. Mene ꞌougine, ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa aradu ani ahiri ḡonotaꞌuma ebu vaze zinaꞌa, 'Aniꞌe bare ḡabode iḡuneha,' rae reꞌuma. ꞌOugine zeꞌa vaze ufeta soꞌoziꞌuma. Aꞌe ibite soꞌozirotaꞌaꞌe vitiniꞌuma.”
\v 65 Pilatoꞌa naenaeziro, “Uti azaḡa nu tutuze onamadu zae edeḡano iduḡa faine ḡiane radoꞌi.”
\v 66 ꞌOugirotene, ze uti azaḡa teite onamadu iduḡa ibiheta hadiḡa boro faifaine hararo, ebu vazeꞌa mene vavaꞌifine gudune ꞌahoga tiro, ebu uti azaḡaꞌe iduḡa ḡiane radiro.
\c 28
\s1 Iesuꞌa Bare Ḡabodiro
\r (Mareko 16:1-8; Luka 24:1-12; Ioane 20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Bana Madaḡa ḡarugano fura oherebau uzeuze Magadala roḡaeḡa Maria zu Maria ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu idu ḡianoga radu onamiro.
\v 2 Eꞌe madaḡano tabara habaꞌa borofe hagariro, ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ovadu idu uhiḡa onamiro, ebu hadiḡa boro kiune vaḡinadu eꞌe rana ehoriro.
\v 3 Ani iraḡaꞌe viriꞌa fuꞌuradu vazavazaheꞌeteꞌe teigiro ebu dabuaḡaꞌe ḡoze teige ꞌuraro.
\v 4 Idu ḡianeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ani horonadu rihau rudaro ꞌahine, rereraro ebu rune azaḡa teigiro.
\p 
\v 5 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa roḡae aheu ziro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. Eḡe edeḡa, zaꞌe satauroniroteꞌe vazeḡa Iesu vaḡeꞌohe.
\v 6 Aniꞌe ꞌahao oꞌoꞌa, rehano aniꞌa reiroteꞌe teige bare ḡabodeha. Aroꞌi ebu aniꞌa bazateꞌe habaꞌa ḡianoꞌi.
\v 7 Ebu za ḡarihe onamadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ꞌahige zoꞌi, 'Aniꞌe rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodeha. Aniꞌe zae zamao Galilea habaꞌa ibite onamiꞌuma ebu eꞌea za ani horoniꞌuma.' Eḡeꞌa zeateꞌe ḡoeꞌa faine ihozoꞌi.”
\p 
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo roḡaeroḡaeꞌe rihozeta zu matuꞌuzeta iduonoꞌo ḡarihe iḡunadu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa zouga veize zeḡe vaḡe dure onamiro.
\v 9 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa tabara zeḡe mazao fureranadu ziro, “Zaꞌe manoḡahe?” ꞌOuge reirotene, ze ani uhiḡa onamiro zu odaḡa obonadu ani mazao kuraro.
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. Onamadu eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa ꞌahige rae zoꞌi, 'Galilea habaꞌa onamoꞌi.' Eꞌea ze eḡe horohiꞌuma.”
\s1 Iesu Iduḡa Ḡianiroteꞌe Uti Azaḡaniꞌa Hari Meꞌodiro
\p 
\v 11 Roḡaeroḡaeꞌa onamiroteꞌea, Iesu idu ḡiane radiroteꞌe uti azaḡa boꞌaḡano nuꞌa ne boro diuḡadu naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe hariḡa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa meꞌodoziniro.
\v 12 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa vaze boroboro teite nuꞌoranadu ḡoꞌaniro, ebu iduḡa ḡiane radiroteꞌe uti azaḡa hadi boro zenadu,
\v 13 ꞌahige rae ziro, “Zaꞌe ꞌahige rae roꞌi, 'Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ohere aradu eme bazuꞌenona ani ahiri ḡonotu feraneha.'
\v 14 ꞌAhi hariḡa gavana vazeḡaniꞌa igine, emeḡeꞌa zae veize ani mazao faine ḡoeriꞌuma ebu zaꞌe aduga ꞌahoga mene hidiꞌuma.”
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo iduḡa ḡiane radiroteꞌe uti azaḡaniꞌa hadi madu zeḡeꞌa ziroteꞌe idunaḡano ḡoeriro. Ebu eꞌe hariḡaniꞌa Iuda azaḡa mazao bororaro zu izidi madaḡano zuni vazeꞌa ꞌouge raꞌohe.
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Haḡae Huniteꞌe Gauḡa Ihoziro
\r (Mareko 16:14-18; Luka 24:36-49; Ioane 20:19-23; Apostolo 1:6-8)
\p 
\v 16 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana tiba fareꞌa Galilea habaꞌa onamadu aniꞌa ihoziroteꞌe maḡano feuriro.
\v 17 Feurirotene, ze ani horonadu ani mazao kuraro. Rehano nuꞌe zamaze ꞌadaꞌadaziro.
\v 18 Ebu Iesuꞌa zeḡe vaḡe aradu ziro, “Adure zu raha gigiꞌaḡa niduꞌaꞌe eḡe iniro.
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe onamadu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa rouga veize zamazoꞌi. Moga, Ubuga zu Vine Zaḡoḡa niḡano babatisozoꞌi,
\v 20 ebu eḡeꞌa haḡaoꞌi rae ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa zeḡeꞌa hegotoga veize ihozoꞌi. Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa iḡaiḡa zae teite radiuꞌohe zu radiꞌuma onamo mada ḡonaga.” 
